\id EZK
\h Ḥizqiyal 
\toc1 Ḥizqiyal 
\toc2 Ḥizqiyal 
\toc3 Ḥiz. 
\mt1 Ḥizqiyal  
\c 1
\s1 Aḍhar n uɛuǧi n SIDI  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss třatin, deg \+bdit uyur\+bdit* wiss arebɛa, deg wass wiss xemsa n uyur\bd*, umi d ayi tuɣa di řwesṭ n ayt n lmenfa ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur, imsar belli arezmen ijenwan uca ẓriɣ iweḥḥan n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Izhd. 137:1\x*  
\v 2 \bd Deg wass wiss xemsa n uyur - tuɣa d aseggʷas wiss xemsa n lmenfa n ujeǧid Yuyakin -\bd*  
\v 3 yusa-dd wawař n SIDI nican ɣar Ḥizqiyal, mmis n Buzi, akehhan, di temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen, ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur. Tuɣa din xas afus n SIDI.   
\m
\v 4 Ẓriɣ, uca xzar, yusa-dd usemmiḍ n tḥaryaḍt zi ccamal, ijj n useynu d ameqqran, d ict n tmessi tᵉttceɛɛeř, inneḍ as-dd \add i useynu\add* ijj n uwesseg. Zi řwesṭ nnes iban-dd \add ca\add* am wuzzař ittwessgen, zi řwesṭ n tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Uf. 9:24\x*  
\v 5 Zi řwesṭ nnes \add tban-dd\add* ṣṣifet n arebɛa n imuddaren. Ammu dd-ḍharen yina: tuɣa \add marra\add* ɣarsen ṣṣifet n bnadem.  
\v 6 Kuř ijj ɣares arebɛa n wudmawen u kuř ijj ɣares arebɛa n wafriwen. \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Ḥiz. 10:14\x*  
\v 7 Iḍaren nsen tuɣa aten nican u tiřeqqa n iḍaren nsen am třeqqa n iḍaren n uɛejmi uca ttissiqent \add třeqqat n iḍaren nsen\add* am wudem n nnḥas ittwassuydan.\f ◼ \fr 1:7 \ft \+fk aɛejmi\ft  - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  
\v 8 Sadu afriwen nsen ɣar arebɛa n iɣezdisen nsen \add ɣarsen\add* ifassen n bnadem. Arebɛa \add n imuddaren\add* ɣarsen udmawen d wafriwen. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Ḥiz. 10:8\x*  
\v 9 Tuɣa afriwen nsen munen ijj ak-d wenneɣni. Nitni war nnqeřben ca xmi gguren. Gguren nitni, kuř ijj \add zzaysen iggur\add* nican ɣar zzat.  
\v 10 Arwas n wudmawen nsen \add tuɣa am\add* wudem n bnadem u ɣar uɣezdis afusi n arebɛa \add n imuddaren nni\add* \add am\add* wudem n weyrad u ɣar uɣezdis azeřmaḍ n arebɛa \add n imuddaren nni\add* \add am\add* wudem n ufunas uca arebɛa \add n imuddaren nni\add* ɣarsen ɛawed udem n ugider. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Ḥiz. 10:14; Asa. 4:7\x*  
\v 11 Udmawen nsen d wafriwen nsen ttwamsebḍan ɣar tiwa. Tnayen \add n wafriwen\add* n kuř ijjen ttmunan ak-d wenneɣni, u tnayen dřin arrimat nsen.  
\v 12 Nitni uyuren, kuř ijj nican ɣar zzat. Mani ma tuɣa ixs Arruḥ ad yuyur, gguren nitni. Nitni war ttneqřiben ca xmi gguren.  
\v 13 X warwas n imuddaren \add nni\add*: aqa banen-dd am řefḥem itteḥduduqen icemmḍen, am yiṣefḍawen. Tuɣa \add timessi\add* tᵉttraḥ tᵉttas-dd jar imuddaren uca timessi tᵉttissiq u zi tmessi tteffɣen-dd wassamen. \x ◘ \xo 1:13 \xt Ḥiz. 10:2\x*  
\v 14 Imuddaren tuɣa ttazzřen, dekkwařen-dd, ittban am wassamen.   
\m
\v 15 \add Řami\add* ẓriɣ imuddaren \add nni\add*, xzar ict n tjarrart \add tbedd\add* x temmurt zzat i imuddaren, ɣar \add kuř ijj zi\add* arebɛa n wudmawen.  
\v 16 Tajarrarin d twaggit nsen banent-i-dd am texrisulit u ɣarsen ṣṣifet d ict ɣar arebɛa \add n imuddaren\add*. Mammec dd-ḍharent u mammec ttwaggent tuɣa axmi ict n tjarrart \add tuɣa nican\add* di tjarrart \add nneɣni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Ḥiz. 10:9, 10\x*  
\v 17 Xmi gguren, gguren ɣar arebɛa n iɣezdisen nsen. Nitni war ttneqřiben ca xmi gguren.  
\v 18 Yantat nsen tuɣa aten uɛřant u ssagʷadent u yantat nsen ccurent s tiṭṭawin i d asent-i-dd innḍen, ɣar arebɛa \add n imuddaren nni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Ḥiz. 10:12\x*  
\v 19 Xmi gguren imuddaren, ggurent uřa d tjarrarin nni ɣar zzat nsen akidsen, u xmi ttwassgeɛɛden imuddaren zi temmurt, ttwassgeɛɛdent uřa d tijarrarin. \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt Ḥiz. 10:16\x*  
\v 20 Ař mani ixs Arruḥ ad yuyur, din gguren nitni, mani ixs Arruḥ ad iraḥ, uca tijarrarin ɣar zzat nsen ttwassgeɛɛdent, maɣar Arruḥ n imuddaren tuɣa di tjarrarin.  
\v 21 Xmi gguren nitni, ggurent uřa d nitenti, u xmi ttbeddan nitni, beddent uřa d nitenti u xmi ttwassgeɛɛden nitni, ttwassgeɛɛdent uřa d tijarrarin akidsen, maɣar Arruḥ n imuddaren tuɣa di tjarrarin.  
\v 22 Sennej i izeǧifen n umuddar tuɣa din min yarewsen deg ict n řqubbet, tban-dd am \add yict n řqubbet\add* issaggʷaden n wejris nni ittwabezzɛen sennej i izeǧifen nsen.  
\v 23 Sadu řqubbet tuɣa afriwen nsen seggmen, sswiẓẓaḍen ijj ɣar wenneɣni. Kuř ijj ɣares tnayen maḥend ad zzaysen issduriy ixef nnes ɣar uɣezdis-s, uca kuř ijj ɣares \add ɛawed\add* tnayen \add nneɣni\add* maḥend ad zzaysen issduriy ixef nnes ɣar uɣezdis nni, \add tuɣa d man aya i\add* arrimat nsen. \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Ḥiz. 1:11\x*  
\v 24 Xmi gguren, sřiɣ i řḥess n wafriwen nsen am zzhir n řebḥar, am tmijja n Umzemmar x kuřci, aqa řḥess d ameqqran am řḥess n řɛeskar. Řami bedden, ssehwan afriwen nsen.  
\v 25 Tuɣa din ict n tmijja sennej i řqubbet nni tuɣa sennej i izeǧifen nsen. Řami \add xenni\add* bedden nitni, ssehwan afriwen nsen.  
\v 26 Sennej i řqubbet nni tuɣa x izeǧifen nsen iban-dd \add ca\add* am yijj n řɛarc s wudem n weẓru n ṣaffir aziza u sennej qaɛ x min ittbanen am řɛarc, \add iqqim\add* xas sennej min ittbanen am ṣṣifet n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 1:26 \xt Dan. 7:9\x*  
\v 27 Uca ẓriɣ \add aqa ṣsifet\add* tᵉttban am wuzzař ittwessgen, tban-dd am tmessi ɣar daxeř nnes u deg wenneḍ nnes. Zi tejɛinnatin nnes ař sennej u zi min yarwesen di tejɛinnatin nnes ař wadday, ẓriɣ \add wenni\add* dd-ittbanen am tmessi uca inneḍ as-dd ijj n uwesseg.  
\v 28 Am mammec dd-tᵉttban tesřit n wenẓar deg iseynuten deg ijj n wass n wenẓar ijehden, ammu tuɣa ccuf n uwesseg nni i d \add as\add* dd-innḍen. Wanita d udem n waddud n uɛuǧi n SIDI. \add Řami\add* \add t\add* ẓriɣ, wḍiɣ s uɣembub inu \add ɣar temmurt\add* uca sřiɣ tmijja nni \add kidi\add* issawařen. \x ◘ \xo 1:28 \xt Dan. 10:9\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Tařaɣit n Arebbi x Ḥizqiyal  
\m
\v 1 Inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, kkar x iḍaren nnec uca Necc ad kik ssiwřeɣ.”  
\v 2 Řami akidi issiweř, yudef-dd dayi Arruḥ uca issekkar-dd ayi x iḍaren inu u necc sřiɣ i tmijja n Wenni kidi issawařen. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Ḥiz. 3:24; Dan. 10:10\x*  
\v 3 Netta inna ayi:  
\b  
\m “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, Necc sekkeɣ cek ɣar ayt n Israil, ɣar řegnus iɣewwɣen, inni xafi iɣewwɣen. Nitni d řejdud nsen ɛeddan xafi ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Irm. 3:25\x*  
\v 4 Nitni d arraw n wudem iqesḥen d wuř izelgen. Necc sekkeɣ cek ɣarsen, ittxeṣṣa ac ad asen tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI!’  
\v 5 Ma ad \add ac\add* sřen niɣ ad semḥen di man aya, minzi nitni d ict n taddart iɣewwɣen, nitni ad ssnen belli tuɣa anabi di řwesṭ nsen. \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Ḥiz. 33:33\x*  
\v 6 Uca cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, war zzaysen tteggʷed u war tteggʷed uřa zeg wawařen nsen. Waxxa aqa din ɣarek tizeggʷura d isennanen u waxxa zeddɣent ɣarek tɣarḍmiwin, war tteggʷed ca zeg wawařen nsen u war zzaysen ttnexřiɛ, minzi nitni d ict n taddart iɣewwɣen. \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Irm. 1:8, 17; Ḥiz. 3:9; Lk. 12:4; 1 Bṭ. 3:1\x*  
\v 7 Ad kidsen tessiwřed s wawařen inu, ma ad sřen niɣ ad semḥen di man aya, minzi nitni aqa ttɣewwɣen.  
\v 8 \add Maca\add* cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, seř min d ac ɣa iniɣ, war ttɣewwiɣ am taddart nni iɣewwɣen. Arzem aqemmum nnec nican uca ecc min d ac ɣa wceɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Asa. 10:9\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Uca ẓriɣ, xzar, ijj n ufus isswiẓẓeḍ-dd ɣari, u xzar, dayes ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen. \x ◘ \xo 2:9 \xt Asa. 10:8-11\x*  
\v 10 Netta ibezzeɛ i-t zzati. Tuɣa yura zi sennej d wadday uca ttwarin dayes izřan n wecḍan d usqinnef d uweḥweḥ n tamara.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\m
\v 1 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, min tᵉttwařid \add danita\add*, ecc i-t! Ecc adlis-a ittwannḍen uca uyur, siweř ak-d taddart n Israil.” \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Irm. 15:16; 2:8; Asa. 10:8-11\x*  
\v 2 Necc arzmeɣ aqemmum inu u Netta issecc ayi adlis nni ittwannḍen.  
\v 3 Inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ɛřef aɛeddis nnec, ccur takrict nnec s wedlis ittwannḍen nni i d ac ɣa wceɣ.” \add Xenni\add* cciɣ u tuɣa-t d \add a\add*miẓid deg uqemmum inu am tamment. \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Izhd. 19:11; 119:103; Asa. 10:10\x*   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, uyur, adef ɣar taddart n Israil uca siweř awařen inu akidsen. \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Irm. 1:17\x*  
\v 5 Minzi war dd-tᵉttwassekked ca ɣar ijj n řgens s ijj n yiřes iwɛar u s ijj n wawař iqseḥ, maca ɣar taddart n Israil,  
\v 6 war iǧi ɣar řegnus aṭṭas s ijj n yiřes iwɛar niɣ s ijj n wawař iqseḥ, i zi war tzemmared ad tfehmed awařen nsen. Mařa sekkeɣ cek ɣarsen nitni, s tidett ad ac sřen.  
\v 7 \add Maca\add* taddart n Israil war ixs ad ɣarek iseř, minzi war xsen ad dd-sřen ɣari, minzi marra taddart n Israil, aqa nitni \add ɣarsen\add* azeǧif iqseḥ u \add ɣarsen\add* uř yezleg.  
\v 8 Xzar, Necc ggiɣ udem nnec iqseḥ am wudmawen nsen, u tanyart nnec ggiɣ tt teqseḥ am tenyarin nsen. \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt Irm. 1:18; Mixa 3:8\x*  
\v 9 Necc ggiɣ tanyart nnec am yijj n umesmir i iǧan iqesḥen x ict n txedmect n weẓru. War zzaysen tteggʷed ca u war ttnexřiɛ ca zeg wudmawen nsen, minzi nitni d ict n taddart iɣewwɣen.” \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Irm. 1:8, 17; 5:3; Ḥiz. 2:6; 1 Bṭ. 3:14\x*   
\m
\v 10 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ḥḍa marra awařen inu nni i ɣa ssiwřeɣ akidek deg wuř nnec uca seř ɣarsen s imezzuɣen nnec.  
\v 11 Uyur, adef ɣar ayt n lmenfa ɣar tarwa n řgens nnec uca siweř akidsen, ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI inu, SIDI!’, ma ad sřen niɣ ad semḥen di man aya.” \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Ḥiz. 2:5, 7\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed ayi Arruḥ uca sřiɣ awarni ayi ict n tmijja teddardiḥ aṭṭas, teqqar: “Ad ittwabarek uɛuǧi n SIDI zeg wemcan \add n tzeddiɣt\add* nnes!” \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Ḥiz. 8:3\x*  
\v 13 Sřiɣ i řḥess n wafriwen n imuddaren nni iřeqqfen ijj i wenneɣni uřa i řḥess n tjarrarin zzat nsen u i řḥess n ijj n udardiḥ imɣar.  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed ayi Arruḥ uca iksi ayi. Necc uyureɣ, d amarzag, itteḥduduq buḥbeř inu \add dayi\add* u afus n SIDI tuɣa idqeř xafi.  
\v 15 \add Ammu i\add* dd-usiɣ ɣar ayt n lmenfa di Tal-Aviv, inni izeddɣen ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur. Necc qqimeɣ din mani tuɣa zeddɣen, \add wah,\add* qqimeɣ din sebɛa n wussan ttbehteɣ řami d ayi tuɣa jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Ayub 2:13\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ḥizqiyal ittwařeqqem d aɛessas x Israil  
\m
\v 16 Imsar awarni řami ɛdun sebɛa n wussan, aqa yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI. Inna:  
\v 17 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, Necc ggiɣ cek d aɛessas x taddart n Israil. Xmi ɣa tesřed i yijj n wawař zeg uqemmum inu, ittxeṣṣa cek ad asen tɛeřmed zzayi. \x ◘ \xo 3:17 \xt Ica. 62:6; Ḥiz. 33:7; 1 Tim. 3:1\x*  
\v 18 Xmi ɣa iniɣ i uɛeffan ‘S tidett ad temmted!’ uca cek war d as teɛřimed ca u war tessiwřed ḥima ad tɛeřmed aɛeffan di ssibbet n webrid nnes aɛeffan maḥend ad t teḥḍid ḥima ad iqqim ad iddar, \add xenni\add* ad immet uɛeffan nni di řɣecc nnes, maca idammen nnes ad ten ttareɣ zeg ufus nnec. \x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt Ḥiz. 33:8\x*  
\v 19 Maca mařa tɛeřmed i uɛeffan u netta war ibeɛɛed ca x tuɛeffna nnes u x webrid nnes iɛeffnen, \add xenni\add* netta ad immet di řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, \add maca\add* řeɛmar nnec ad injem.”   
\m
\v 20 “Mařa amsegged ibeɛɛed x tsegda nnes uca igga řmuɛṣiyyet xmi ɣa ssarseɣ ict n ssibbet zzates ařami ɣa ixḍa, \add xenni\add* ad immet. Minzi cek war d as teɛřimed, ad immet di ddenb nnes uca timegga iseggden i yegga war daysent idaren \add ɛad\add*. \add Maca\add* idammen nnes ad ten ttareɣ zeg ifassen nnec. \x ◘ \xo 3:20 \xt Ḥiz. 18:24; 33:12, 13\x*  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* mařa tɛeřmed i umsegged, ḥima war ixeṭṭi umsegged u netta war ixḍi, \add xenni\add* ad iqqim iddar s tidett minzi tuɣa ittwaɛřem, u cek tfekked řeɛmar nnec.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aḍhar wiss tnayen n uɛuǧi n SIDI  
\m
\v 22 Yusa-dd din ufus n SIDI xafi uca inna ayi: “Kkar, ffeɣ ɣar řewḍa \add n teɣzurt\add*, ad kidek ssiwřeɣ dinni.”  
\v 23 Kkareɣ uca ffɣeɣ ɣar řewḍa \add n teɣzurt\add*, xzar, aɛuǧi n SIDI tuɣa ittbedda dinni am uɛuǧi i ẓriɣ ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur uca wḍiɣ x uɣembub inu \add ɣar temmurt\add*. \x ◘ \xo 3:23 \xt Ḥiz. 1:3\x*  
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* yudef dayi Arruḥ uca issekkar ayi x iḍaren inu uca issiweř akidi. Netta inna ayi: “Uyur, belleɛ ixef nnec daxeř di taddart nnec. \f ◼ \fr 3:24 \ft \+fk daxeř di taddart nnec\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘di řwest n taddart nnec’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 3:24 \xt Ḥiz. 2:2\x*  
\v 25 U cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, xzar, ad ac ggen iseɣwan u ad cek carfen zzaysen. War tᵉtteffeɣ ca ḥima ad tadfed jar asen.  
\v 26 Ad ssřesqeɣ iřes nnec ɣar waneɣ nnec. Ad tdewřed d azinun uca war tᵉttiřid d aryaz jar asen wenni ten i ɣa iwebbxen, minzi nitni d ict n taddart tɣewweɣ. \x ◘ \xo 3:26 \xt Ḥiz. 2:5\x*  
\v 27 \add Maca\add* Necc, xmi kik i ɣa ssiwřeɣ, ad arzmeɣ aqemmum nnec \add ɛawed\add* uca ad asen tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI! Wi ittesřan, ad iseř, uca wi isemmḥen di man aya, \add waxxa\add* ad dayes ismeḥ!’, minzi nitni d ict n taddart tɣewweɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 3:27 \xt Ḥiz. 2:5, 7\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Arcam n uqewwar n řɛeskar n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ksi ict n luṣa n třaxt uca sars i-tt zzat i wudem nnec uca arcem xas tandint n Urcalim.  
\v 2 Qewwar as uca bna xas ijj n lbaraj uca egg xas acbar, egg xas řemrageḥ n řɛeskar uca wwet xas deg wenneḍ nnes řeqcuɛ n wedham. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt 2 Ij. 25:1\x*  
\v 3 Uca cek, ksi ict n marmita n wuzzař uca egg i-tt am yijj n řḥiḍ n wuzzař jar cek d tendint. Arr udem nnec xas maḥend ad tᵉttwaḥṣar u cek ad tt teḥṣared: man aya ad tiři d řeɛřamet i taddart n Israil.  
\v 4 Uca cek, ad tezzřed x uɣezdis nnec azeřmaḍ uca ad xas tegged řmuɛṣiyyet n taddart n Israil. Anect n ussan nni di xasen i ɣa tezzřed, ad tarbud řmuɛṣiyyet nsen.  
\v 5 Maɣar Necc ad xak ggeɣ \add lɛadad n\add* iseggʷusa n řmuɛṣiyyet nsen am lɛadad n wussan: \bd teřt-mya u-tesɛin n wussan\bd* ad tarbud \bd řmuɛṣiyyet n taddart n Israil\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 4:5 \xt Řxř. 14:34\x*  
\v 6 \add Xmi\add* i ɣa tkemmřed \add ussan nni\add*, ad tezzřed ɛawed x uɣezdis nnec afusi uca ad tarbud \bd řmuɛṣiyyet n taddart n Yahuda\bd*, \bd arebɛin n wussan\bd*. Ijj n wass i yijj n useggʷas, am mammec i d ac umureɣ. \f ◼ \fr 4:6 \ft \+fk am mammec i d ac umureɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘am mammec d ac wciɣ’.\f*  
\v 7 Ad teqqimed tᵉttarred udem nnec ɣar řeḥṣaret n Urcalim uca ad tɛarrid aɣiř nnec, ad tnebbid ḍidd nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Ica. \x*  
\v 8 Xzar, Necc ad xak ggeɣ tisɣunin ařami war tzemmared ad tennqeřbed zeg ijj n uɣezdis ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni ař ɣa tkemmřed ussan n řeḥṣaret nnec.”   
\m
\v 9 “Ksi irden, imendi, ibawen, řeɛdes, tafsawt d karṣana uca egg i-ten di tebqect uca egg zzaysen aɣrum i yixef nnec. Ad tecced aya am mecḥař lɛadad n wussan nni i ɣa tezzřed x uɣezdis nnec, teřt-mya u-tesɛin n wussan. \f ◼ \fr 4:9 \ft \+fk karṣana\ft  - niɣ ‘dduxn’ niɣ ‘jawars’.\f*  
\v 10 Macca nni i ɣa tecced ad tᵉttwawzen: ɛicrin ciqlu i yijj n wass. Ad tt tecced di tsaɛɛetin ittwaggen.  
\v 11 Ad teswed aman s řeɛbar: ict n tsittut zeg ijj n uhinu. Ad tt teswed zi řweqt ař řweqt \add nneɣni\add*. \f ◼ \fr 4:11 \ft \+fk ict n tsittut zeg ijj n uhinu\ft  - ɛřaḥař azyen litru.\f*  
\v 12 Ad tecced ict n txebbazt n imendi uca ad tt tᵉssenggʷed zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen x iẓẓan i dd-iffɣen zi bnadem.”   
\m
\v 13 Inna SIDI: “Ammu i ɣa ccen ayt n Israil aɣrum nsen ixemjen jar řegnus mani ten ɣar i ɣa ssuffɣeɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 4:13 \xt Ḥuc. 9:3\x*  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ: “\add A,\add* Sidi inu, SIDI, xzar, řeɛmar inu war ittwassexmej ɛemmarṣ \add s macca war iḥřin\add*. Zi temẓi inu ař řexxu necc war cciɣ řxecbet niɣ min imezzqen u ɛemmarṣ war yudif weysum n jjɛifect ɣar uqemmum inu.”  
\v 15 Uca Netta inna ayi: “Xzar, ad ac wciɣ řeɣbar n ifunasen deg wemcan n ubarruḍ n bnadem. Sewjed xas aɣrum nnec.”   
\m
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, xzar, ad arẓeɣ řeɛweč n weɣrum di Urcalim uca nitni ad ccen aɣrum s řewzen s unexřiɛ uca s arjef ad swen aman s řeɛbar,\f ◼ \fr 4:16 \ft \+fk řeɛweč n weɣrum\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘aɛmud n weɣrum’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:16 \xt Lawi 26:26; Ica. 3:1; Ḥiz. 5:16; 14:13\x*  
\v 17 minzi ad asen ittxeṣṣa weɣrum d waman. Nitni ad xzaren ayawya s arjef uca ad dewřen arṣuḍen di řmuɛṣiyyet nsen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\m
\v 1 “Uca cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ksi ijj n řmus iqḍeɛ, ksi ijj řmus n uḥeffaf uca sekk i-t x uzeǧif nnec u x tmart nnec. \add Xenni\add* ad teksid ijj n řmizan uca \add acuwwaf\add* ad ten tebḍid. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt 2 Ṣm. 10:4\x*  
\v 2 \bd Ict n ttuřut\bd* ad tt tesscemḍed di řwesṭ n tendint awarni řami i ɣa kemmřen wussan n řeḥṣaret \add uca\add* ad teksid \bd ict n ttuřut\bd* \add nneɣni\add*, ad tewted s ssif nnec deg wenneḍ nnes uca \bd ict n ttuřut\bd* \add nneɣni\add* ad tt tzuzzared deg usemmiḍ u Necc ad jebdeɣ ssif awarni as. \x ◘ \xo 5:2 \xt Lawi 26:33; Zak. 13:8\x*  
\v 3 Ssenni ad teksid \bd cwayt \+bdit n iẓeṭṭan\+bdit*\bd* uca ad ten tcedded deg ibeḥruren \add n upartessu\add* nnec. \f ◼ \fr 5:3 \ft \+fk ssenni\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘zi Babil’ mani tuɣa zeddɣen Wudayen awařni řami ten yiwi Nabuxadnaṣṣar di tmeḥbast ɣar Babil.\f*  
\v 4 Ad \bd zzayes\bd* teksid \bd ɛad cwayt \+bdit n iẓeṭṭan\+bdit*\bd* uca ad ten tenḍared di řwest n tmessi uca ad ten tesscemḍed s tmessi. Ssenni ad teffeɣ tmessi x marra taddart n Israil.”   
\m
\v 5 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Ta d Urcalim i ẓẓuɣ di řwesṭ n řegnus, ak-d temmura i d as dd-innḍen.  
\v 6 \add Maca\add* nettat tɣewweɣ x lfarayiḍ inu mahu řegnus, uřa x tweṣṣa inu mahu timmura i d as dd-innḍen, minzi nitni nḍaren lfarayiḍ inu u tiweṣṣa inu war tent ḍfaren.”  
\v 7 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Minzi kenniw teggim mahu řegnus i d awem dd-innḍen, war tuyurem di tweṣṣa inu u war teggim lfarayiḍ inu, ɛad war teggim ɛlaḥsab lfarayiḍ n řegnus i d awem dd-innḍen’, \x ◘ \xo 5:7 \xt Lawi 18:24, 28\x*  
\v 8 s uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, uřa d Necc ad xam qeřbeɣ u ad ggeɣ řeḥkamat di řwesṭ nnem zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus.  
\v 9 Ad zzayem ggeɣ am mammec ɛemmarṣ war ggiɣ u war tteggeɣ ɛemmarṣ ɛad zi ssa d tsawent, zi ssibbet n marra jjɛayef nnem.  
\v 10 S uya ibabaten ad ccen arraw di řwesṭ nnem uca arraw ad ccen ibabaten nsen. Necc ad am ggeɣ řeḥkamat u marra min zzayem iqqimen ad t zuzzareɣ ɣar marra tiɣemmura n usemmiḍ.’” \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Lawi 26:29; Aɛwd. 28:53; 2 Ij. 6:29; Igjd. 4:10\x*   
\m
\v 11 “S uya, s tidett am ddareɣ Necc, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: \add S tidett\add*, uřa d Necc ad qeḍɛeɣ, war zziǧizeɣ, war areḥḥmeɣ, umi tessxemjed Zzawect inu Iqeddsen s marra nnɛawat nnem n l’aṣnam u s marra jjɛayef nnem! \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Ḥiz. 7:4\x*  
\v 12 \bd Ict n ttuřut\bd* \add n imezdaɣ\add* nnem ad temmet s ṭṭaɛun u s řaẓ di řwesṭ nnem, uca \bd ict n ttuřut\bd* \add nneɣni\add* ad tewḍa s ssif deg wenneḍ nnem, u \add ɛad\add* \bd ict n ttuřut\bd* ad tt zuzzareɣ ɣar marra tiɣemmura n usemmiḍ u awarni asen ad dd-jebdeɣ ssif. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Irm. 15:2\x*  
\v 13 Aɣḍab inu ad ijjiwen ař uneggar uca ad xasen ssarseɣ asɛar inu. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ssfewwjeɣ ixef inu u nitni ad ssnen, aqa Necc, SIDI, ssiwřeɣ di tusmi inu \add iqeddsen\add*, xmi ɣa kemmřeɣ asɛar inu xasen.  
\v 14 Ad cem arreɣ d řxirbet d ict n řqecɛet n ustehzi jar řegnus i d am dd-innḍen, zzat i tiṭṭawin n kuř ijj nni i ɣa iɛdun.  
\v 15 Ad tedweř \add Urcalim\add* i ustehzi d řḥegra, i \add umedya n\add* useqseḥ d usiggʷed i řegnus i d as dd-innḍen, xmi d as i ɣa qḍeɣ řeḥkamat s weɣḍab u s wesɛar u s tiyitta iḥman. Necc, SIDI, aqa ssiwřeɣ! \x ◘ \xo 5:15 \xt Aɛwd. 28:37\x*  
\v 16 Xmi ten ɣa wteɣ s fřitcat n řaẓ nni dd ɣa yawyen areddeǧ, tinni ɣa wteɣ ḥima ad kenniw sshellkeɣ, \add xenni\add* ad xawem arniɣ řaẓ u ad arẓeɣ řeɛweč n weɣrum \add nwem\add*. \x ◘ \xo 5:16 \xt Lawi 26:26; 2 Ij. 6:25; Ica. 3:1; Ḥiz. 4:16; 14:13\x*  
\v 17 Ad xawem sekkeɣ řaẓ d řewḥuc iwɛaren nni i ɣa ikksen tarwa nnem. Ṭṭaɛun d usizzeř n idammen ad kken xam u Necc ad xam ssekkeɣ ssif. Necc, SIDI, aqa ssiwřeɣ!” \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Lawi 26:22\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Awař ḍidd i idurar n Israil  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, arr udem nnec ɣar idurar n Israil uca nabb xasen \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt Ḥiz. 36:1\x*  
\v 3 uca ini: ‘\add A\add* idurar n Israil, sřem i wawař n Sidi inu, SIDI! Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, i idurar u i tewririn, i tɣezratin u i teɣzurtin: Xzar, Necc ad xawem ssekkeɣ ssif uca řegɛudi nwem \add mani tᵉttwehhabem ddbayeḥ nwem\add* ad tent areddǧeɣ.  
\v 4 Ad ttwaredǧen iɛalṭaren nwem u ipilaren n arebbi n tfuct nwem ad ttwarẓen u Necc ad nḍareɣ inni ittwassnuqben zzat i wudem n imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nwem\add*.  
\v 5 Ad ggeɣ řxecbat n ayt n Israil zzat i imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nsen\add* uca ad zuzzareɣ iɣsan nwem ɣar min dd-innḍen i iɛalṭaren nwem.  
\v 6 Di marra imucan mani tzeddɣem ad ttwareddǧent tneddam uca řegɛudi ad tent jjen, ařami iɛalṭaren nwem ad iřin d řxarbet d ttwajjen, uca imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nwem\add* ad ttwarẓen u ipilaren nwem n arebbi n tfuct ad ttwaqessen u timegga nwem ad ttwamḥant.  
\v 7 Inni ittwanɣen ad \add din\add* iřin di řwesṭ nwem, uca \add ammu\add* i ɣa tessnem aqa Necc d SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 8 “Ad ggeɣ aqa inni ittwassnejmen zi ssif jar řegnus ad qqimen ddaren umi kenniw ɣa zuzzareɣ x temmura.  
\v 9 Inni ittwanejmen ad xafi ɛeqřen jar regnus mani ttwaneddhen d imeḥbas, minzi Necc arẓiɣ uř nsen nni xafi ittaggʷejen, iccuren s farq-ccɣeř uca uřa d tiṭṭawin nsen nni iḍfaren awarni i imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nsen\add* ccurent s farq-ccɣeř. Nitni ad ɛiffen ixef nsen zi ssibbet n tmegga iɛeffnen nni ggin s marra jjaɛayef nsen.  
\v 10 Nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI. Necc war nniɣ amenni waha aqa Necc ad daysen ggeɣ řɣar-a.”   
\m
\v 11 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Wwet s ufus nnec uca darrec s uḍar nnec uca ini: ‘Ay!’ x marra nnɛawat tiɛeffanin n taddart n Israil, maɣar nitni ad wḍan s ssif, s řaẓ u s ṭṭaɛun! \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt Ḥiz. 21:22\x*  
\v 12 Wi iǧan yiggʷej ad immet s ṭṭaɛun u wi iǧan yudes ad iwḍa s ssif u wi iqqimen u aqa ittwaḥṣar ad immet s řaẓ, \add ammu\add* ad daysen kemmřeɣ asɛar inu.  
\v 13 Ittxeṣṣa ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, xmi inni zzaysen ittwanɣen ad \add din\add* iřin jar imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nsen\add* deg wenneḍ n iɛalṭaren nsen x kuř tawrirt tuɛřa, x marra tiqqicatin n idurar, sadu kuř tacejjart tazizawt u sadu kuř tacejjart n yigg s waṭṭas n tefray, \add deg\add* wemcan mani nnumen ssewjaden ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i marra imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nsen\add*. \f ◼ \fr 6:13 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  
\v 14 Ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd nsen uca ad ggeɣ tammurt d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen, ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen mahu řexřa n Dabla, di marra imucan mani zeddɣen. Uca nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Aneggaru ad dd-yas!  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, i temmurt n Israil:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Aneggar, yusa-dd uneggar\qt*  
\m \qt x arebɛa n iɣezdisen n temmurt.\qt*   
\m
\v 3 \qt Řexxu yusa-dd xam uneggar nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi ad ɣarem dd-sekkeɣ aɣḍab inu\qt*  
\m \qt u ad xam ḥekmeɣ am yibriden nnem\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad xam ggeɣ marra jjɛayef nnem.\qt*   
\m
\v 4 \qt War d am zziǧizent tiṭṭawin inu\qt*  
\m \qt u war areḥḥmeɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi ad arreɣ ibriden nnem\qt*  
\m \qt x uzeǧif nnem\qt*  
\m \qt u jjɛayef nnem ad cem řeqfent\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ nnem.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Ammu i ɣa\+tl* tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:4 \xt Ḥiz. 5:11; 8:18\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Ijj n řɣar, ijj n řɣar ifarzen,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ad dd-yas.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Yusa-dd uneggar,\qt*  
\m \qt aneggar yusa-dd,\qt*  
\m \qt ifaq-dd ḍidd nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ad dd-yas!\qt*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Tusa-dd ɣarek tqedduḥt,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a\+tl* amezduɣ n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt tasaɛɛet tusa-dd,\qt*  
\m \qt ass n uxarweḍ iqarreb-dd\qt*  
\m \qt u war \+tl din\+tl* asřiwřew\qt*  
\m \qt zeg idurar.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 7:7 \ft \+fk tasaɛɛet\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řweqt’.\f*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Řexxu deɣya ad xam zeǧɛeɣ asɛar inu\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad dayem kemmřeɣ aɣḍab inu.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad xam ḥekmeɣ anect n ibriden nnem\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad xam ssiwḍeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt marra jjɛayef nnem.\qt*   
\m
\v 9 \qt War zziǧizeɣ u war areḥḥmeɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad ɣarem dd-arreɣ\qt*  
\m \qt min tessdaheǧed,\qt*  
\m \qt u jjɛayef nnem ad iřint di řwesṭ nnem\qt*  
\m \qt u kenniw ad tessnem\qt*  
\m \qt belli aqa Necc d SIDI\qt*  
\m \qt wenni kenniw iccaten.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 \qt ‘Xzar, ass, xzar,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa da tiweḍ-dd \+tl tqedduḥt\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt teqḍa tqedduḥt,\qt*  
\m \qt tnewwar taɣɣarct,\qt*  
\m \qt tessendi nnfaxet.\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Igeɛɛed lɛunf am uzeǧaḍ n řɣar.\qt*  
\m \qt War zzaysen iqqim uřa d ijj,\qt*  
\m \qt walu n řɣaci nsen inhewřen,\qt*  
\m \qt walu n ddriz nsen\qt*  
\m \qt u walu n usemɣar ad ɣarsen iqqim ɛad.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Tusa-dd tsaɛɛet, ixecced wass.\qt*  
\m \qt Ejj wenni isɣin war ifarreḥ\qt*  
\m \qt u ejj wenni izznuzan war ittecḍin,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi řḥaduq n weɣḍab\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl aqa-t\+tl* x marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen.\qt*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Minzi wenni izznuzan\qt*  
\m \qt war dd-iddikkwiř\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar min immenzen,\qt*  
\m \qt waxxa nitni qqimen ddaren,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi war ibeṭṭiř řewḥiy\qt*  
\m \qt x marra řɣaci inhewřen n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt uca uřa d ijj war izemmar s řmuɛṣiyyet nnes\qt*  
\m \qt ad iqqim ittᵉṭṭef di tudart nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 14 \qt Nitni suḍen s jjehd \+tl di řbuq\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt uca sswejden marra řeḥwayej,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* uřa d ijj war itteffeɣ ɣar umenɣi,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi řḥaduq n weɣḍab inu\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl aqa-t\+tl* x marra řɣaci inhewřen n temmurt.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 \qt ‘Zi barra ssif\qt*  
\m \qt u zi daxeř ṭṭaɛun d řaẓ.\qt*  
\m \qt Wi iǧan deg iyyar ad immet s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt wi iǧan di tendint ad t yecc řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun.\qt*   
\m
\v 16 \qt Wi zzaysen yarewřen, \+tl wah\+tl* ad nejmen,\qt*  
\m \qt maca ad iřin x idurar\qt*  
\m \qt am idbiren zi teɣzurin,\qt*  
\m \qt ad nnezbaren marra,\qt*  
\m \qt kuř ijj x řmuɛṣiyyet nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Marra ifassen ad heyyfen,\qt*  
\m \qt u marra ifadden ad dewřen d aman.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:17 \xt Ica. 13:7; Irm. 6:24\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 \qt ‘Ad beysen s txuncay n \+tl wecḍan\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt arjef ad ten issduriy\qt*  
\m \qt x marra udmawen \+tl ad yiři\+tl* řeḥya\qt*  
\m \qt u x marra izeǧifen nsen tuqeccart.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:18 \xt Ica. 15:2, 3; Irm. 48:37\x*   
\m
\v 19 \qt Ad nḍaren nnuqart nsen deg ibriden\qt*  
\m \qt u ureɣ nsen ad yiři am ca n řḥajjet texmej.\qt*  
\m \qt Nnuqart nsen d wureɣ nsen\qt*  
\m \qt war zemmaren ad ten fekken\qt*  
\m \qt deg wass n uduqqez \+tl n ufugem\+tl* n SIDI.\qt*  
\m \qt War zemmaren ad zzaysen ssjiwnen\qt*  
\m \qt řeɛmar nsen\qt*  
\m \qt niɣ ad zzaysen ccuren takrict nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi aya tuɣa d ssibbet n uneqraḍ\qt*  
\m \qt i dd-yiwyen řmuɛṣiyyet nsen.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:19 \xt Awřn. 11:4; Ṣaf. 1:18\x*   
\m
\v 20 \qt Aẓri n telwizt igga i-t d lɛaḍama yuɛřan,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* nitni ggin dayes\qt*  
\m \qt řexyařat n nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam\qt*  
\m \qt u řexyařat n jjɛayef nsen.\qt*  
\m \qt X uya arriɣ \+tl talwizt\+tl* d taxmuji i nitni.\qt*   
\m
\v 21 \qt Necc ad tt wceɣ d tucceffra\qt*  
\m \qt deg ufus n ibarraniyyen\qt*  
\m \qt uca \+tl ad tt wceɣ\+tl* d takeccaḍt\qt*  
\m \qt i iɛeffanen n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt uca nitni ad ssɛiǧten \+tl talwizt\+tl*.\qt*   
\m
\v 22 \qt Necc ad xas ssenqeřbeɣ udem inu\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad ssɛiǧten tazeddiɣt inu innufaren,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar iceffaren ad din adfen\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ssɛiǧten \+tl marra\+tl*.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 23 \qt ‘Sewjed ssnesřet,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi tammurt teccur s usizzeř n idammen\qt*  
\m \qt u tandint teccur s lɛunf.\qt*   
\m
\v 24 \qt Necc ad awyeɣ řegnus iɛeffanen qaɛ,\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad ṭṭfen tudrin nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ssbedden nnfaxet n ayt n jjehd,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ttwassɛiǧtent\qt*  
\m \qt Tzawiyyin nsen Iqeddsen.\qt*   
\m
\v 25 \qt Ad dd-yas unexřiɛ d ameqqran.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad arzun řehna,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* war ittiři.\qt*   
\m
\v 26 \qt Aqa ad dd-yas uceřwaw awarni i uceřwaw,\qt*  
\m \qt ad yiři řhard awarni i řhard.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad arzun řewḥiy n unabi,\qt*  
\m \qt waxxa teqḍa Ccariɛa n ukehhan\qt*  
\m \qt d ccwar n imɣaren\qt*   
\m
\v 27 \qt Ajeǧid ad icḍen,\qt*  
\m \qt řḥakem ad yarḍ anexřiɛ\qt*  
\m \qt u ifassen n řgens\qt*  
\m \qt ad qarrmen s tiggʷudi.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc ad zzaysen ggeɣ am webrid nsen\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad xasen ḥekmeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt am lfarayiḍ nsen.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Ammu\+tl* i ɣa ssnen aqa Necc d SIDI.’”\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Aɛbed n l’aṣnam di Zzawect Tameqqrant di Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss setta, deg uyur wiss setta, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss xemsa n uyur\bd*, \add umi\add* tuɣa qqimeɣ di tudart inu u imɣaren n Yahuda tuɣa qqimen zzat i wudem inu, \add xenni\add* imsar aqa iwḍa-dd xafi din ufus n Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 2 Necc ẓriɣ, uca xzar, tuɣa din wenni ṣsifet nnes yarwesen deg wudem n tmessi. Zi tejɛinnatin nnes ɣar wadday aqa iban-dd am tmessi u zi tejɛinnatin nnes ař sennej \add tuɣa\add* axmi teẓrid tissiqt, tban-dd am wuzzař ittwessgen.  
\v 3 Isswiẓẓeḍ-dd min yarwesen deg ijj n ufus uca Netta iṭṭef ayi-dd ɣar ict n tzarezt n uzeǧif inu, uca Arruḥ issgeɛɛed ayi jar ujenna d temmurt, indeh ayi di iweḥḥan n AREBBI ɣar Urcalim, ɣar wadaf \add n tewwart\add* n řemraḥ n daxeř nni ixezzaren ɣar ccamal, mani iǧa řkursi n řexyař n l’aṣnam n tusmi nni issekkaran tusmi. \x ◘ \xo 8:3 \xt Dan. 5:5\x*  
\v 4 U xzar, din i iǧa uɛuǧi n AREBBI n Israil, ittban-dd am mammec \add t\add* ẓriɣ di řewḍa n teɣzurt. \x ◘ \xo 8:4 \xt Ḥiz. 3:23\x*  
\v 5 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, sgeɛɛed řexxu tamuɣři nnec ɣar ccamal!” Uca ssgeɛɛdeɣ tamuɣři inu jjihet n ccamal, u xzar, ibedd \add din\add* řexyař nni n ṣṣanam n tusmi ɣar ccamal n Tewwart n Uɛalṭar deg wadaf.  
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ma tᵉttwařid min tteggen nitni, jjɛayef timeqqranin nni tᵉttegg taddart n Israil danita, ařami ittxeṣṣa ad aggʷejeɣ x Zzawect inu Iqeddsen. Ad tẓared ɛad jjɛayef timeqqranin \add x tina\add*.”   
\m
\v 7 Netta yiwyi ayi ɣar wadaf n řemraḥ. \add Umi\add* ẓriɣ, xzar, aqa din ijj n weḥfur di řḥiḍ.  
\v 8 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ɣaz xenni řḥiḍ.” Necc ɣziɣ řḥiḍ uca xzar, aqa din ijj n wadaf.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Adef, uca xzar jjɛayef timeqqranin nni tteggen danita.”  
\v 10 Udfeɣ uca ẓriɣ, xzar, aqa din ɛřam kuř ineqqacen n imuddaren ittbuɛen, n řmař amengus u n marra imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam\add* n taddart n Israil ttwaneqcen di řḥid deg wenneḍ. \x ◘ \xo 8:10 \xt Ica. 66:17\x*  
\v 11 Aqa sebɛin n yeryazen zeg imɣaren n taddart n Israil, ak-d Yazanyahu, mmis n Cafan, di řwest nsen, bedden zzatsen u kuř ijj s řmejmar nnes n řebxur deg ufus nnes uca tuři tejnewt teccur s arriḥet n řebxur. \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt Ica. 66:17\x*  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ma teẓrid min tteggen imɣaren n Israil di taǧest, kuř ijj deg wexxam n řexyař nnes ineqcen, maɣar qqaren: SIDI war d aneɣ iẓri, SIDI yejja tammurt.” \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Ḥiz. 9:9\x*  
\v 13 Netta inna ayi: “Ad tẓared ɛad jjɛayef timeqqranin \add x tina\add* nni tteggen nitni.”   
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* indeh ayi ɣar wadaf n tewwart n Taddart n SIDI, wenni iǧan ɣar ccamal, u xzar, qqiment din temɣarin ttrunt di Tammuz. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Uf. 38:8\x*  
\v 15 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ma teẓrid aya! Ad tẓared ɛad jjɛayef mɣarent x tina.”   
\m
\v 16 Uca yiwyi ayi ɣar řemraḥ n daxeř n Taddart n SIDI, uca xzar, ɣar tewwart n Zzawect n SIDI, jar wesqif d uɛalṭar, aqa din ɛřaḥař xemsa u-ɛicrin n yeryazen. Iɛurar nsen dewřen ɣar Zzawect n SIDI u udmawen nsen ɣar ccarq, uca nitni sejden ɣar ccarq i tfuct.  
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ma teẓrid aya? Ma aqa drust i taddart n Yahuda maḥend ad ggen jjɛayef-a timeqqranin nni tteggen danita? Maɣar nitni ccuren tammurt s lɛunf uca qqimen dewřen-dd ɣari ḥima ad ayi sɛaren. Xzar, tteggen \add ɛad\add* taseṭṭa \add ittwaqeḍɛen\add* ɣar wenzaren nsen!  
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* uřa d Necc ad ggeɣ s wesɛar. War dayi izziǧiz ḥed u war areḥḥmeɣ. Waxxa nitni sɣuyyun s tmijja ijehden deg imezzuɣen inu, Necc war dd ɣarsen ttesřiɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 8:18 \xt Awřn. 1:28; Ica. 1:15; Irm. 11:11; Ḥiz. 5:11; 7:4\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Řḥukm x Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa deg imezzuɣen inu s tmijja tejhed, inna: “Ejj imeḥḍayen n tendint ad dd-qarrben, kuř ijj s řesnaḥ nnes n ureddeǧ deg ufus nnes.”  
\v 2 Uca xzar, setta n yeryazen usin-dd zeg webrid zi Tewwart Yuɛřan nni ixezzaren ɣar ccamal u kuř ijj ɣares řesnaḥ nnes i uteḥḥi deg ufus nnes. Di řwesṭ nsen tuɣa din ijj n weryaz, tuɣa yarḍ řeqṭen, yiwi tadwat n umarir ɣar webyas nnes. Udfen nitni uca ggin ad bedden ɣar uɛalṭar n nnḥas.  
\v 3 Aɛuǧi n AREBBI n Israil issgeɛɛed ixef nnes zi sennej n ukirub nni x iǧan, yuyur ɣar tnebdat n Taddart uca Netta iřaɣa-dd i weryaz nni yarḍen řeqṭen d wenni \add yiwyen\add* tadwat n umarir ɣar webyas nnes. \f ◼ \fr 9:3 \ft \+fk akirub\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  
\v 4 Inna as SIDI: “Cuqq di řwesṭ n tendint, di řwesṭ n Urcalim, uca egg kruz \add d řeɛřamet\add* x tenyarin n yeryazen nni ittnixsisen d ttweɛɛḍen x ssibbet n marra jjɛayef nni ittwaggen di řwesṭ nnes.”  
\v 5 Umi sřiɣ, inna i inneɣni: “Cuqqem di tendint awarni as, nɣem, war zziǧizem u war areḥḥmem!  
\v 6 Nɣem iwessura, iḥuḍriyyen, tiɛezriyin, iḥenjiren d temɣarin ař ɣa ttwahellken qaɛ, maca war tthadam uřa d ijj xas kruc \add d řeɛřamet\add*. Bdam zi Zzawect inu Iqeddsen.” Uca nitni bdan zeg iwessura nni iǧan zzat i Taddart.  
\v 7 Uca Netta inna asen: “Sxemjem Taddart uca ccurem řemraḥat s \add řxecbat n\add* yinni ittwanɣen. Ffɣem!” Ffɣen nitni uca nɣin \add iwdan\add* di tendint.   
\m
\v 8 Řami ten nɣin uca qqimeɣ necc, imsar aqa necc wḍiɣ x uɣembub inu \add ɣar temmurt\add* uca nniɣ: “Ax, Sidi inu, SIDI, ma ad tareddǧed řexxu min iqqimen n Israil umi ɣa tzeǧɛed asɛar nnec x Urcalim?”  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Řmuɛṣiyyet n taddart n Israil d Yahuda temɣar aṭṭas u tammurt teccur s idammen u tendint teccur s usfarɣ n řḥeqq, minzi nitni qqaren: ‘SIDI ismeḥ di temmurt uca SIDI war iẓarr!’  
\v 10 \add S uya\add* uřa d Necc ad ggeɣ ammu. Tiṭṭ inu war tsemmeḥ u Necc war ttḥinniɣ. Necc ad ssenqeřbeɣ abrid nsen x uzeǧif nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Ḥiz. 5:11; 7:4; 8:18\x*   
\m
\v 11 Uca xzar, aryaz nni yarḍen řeqṭen, wenni dd-yiwyen ɣar webyas nnes tadwat \add n umarir\add*, aqa yarra-dd řexbar, inna: “Ggiɣ am mammec i d ayi tumured.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\m
\v 1 \add Awarni aya\add* ẓriɣ, xzar, sennej i řqubbet, sennej i uzeǧif n ikiruben, \add tuɣa din ca\add* am weẓru n ṣaffir, min dd-ittbanen am wudem n min yarwesen deg ijj n řɛarc, \add u\add* sennej i nitni iḍhar-dd Netta.  
\v 2 Uca issiweř ak-d weryaz nni yarḍen arrud n řeqṭen, inna: “Adef-dd ɣar daxeř jar tjarrarin ittennḍen, ař sadu i ikiruben, uca ccur ifassen nnec s řefḥem itteḥduduqen zi jar ikiruben uca zeǧeɛ i-t x tendint!” Uca yudef-dd \add jar asent\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin inu. \f ◼ \fr 10:2 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat inni ɣarsen ṣulṭa tameqqrant.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt Ḥiz. 1:13\x*   
\m
\v 3 Ikiruben tuɣa bedden ɣar uɣezdis afusi n Taddart umi dd-yadef weryaz ɣar daxeř uca aseynu iccur řemraḥ n daxeř.  
\v 4 Aɛuǧi n SIDI issgeɛɛed ixef nnes zi sennej n uxirub, \add iɛdu\add* x tnebdat n tewwart n Taddart uca tᵉttwaccur Taddart s useynu u řemraḥ n zzat tuɣa iccur s tessiqt n uɛuǧi n SIDI.  
\v 5 Drizz n wafriwen ittwaseř-dd ař daxeř di řemraḥ n barra, am tmijja n Arebbi, Amzemmar x kuřci, xmi issawař.   
\m
\v 6 Imsar awarni řami yumur Netta i weryaz nni yarḍen řeqṭen, inna: “Ksi timessi zi jar tjarrarin ittenḍen, zi jar ikiruben!”, aqa wanita yudef-dd uca ibedd zzat i tjarrart ittenḍen.  
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* isswiẓẓeḍ ijj n ukirub afus nnes zi jar ikiruben ɣar tmessi nni tuɣa jar asen, iksi zzayes uca issars i-tt deg ifassen n wenni yarḍen řeqṭen. Wanita iksi tt uca iffeɣ.  
\v 8 Sadu wafriwen n ikiruben ittwaẓar ca am ṣṣifet n ufus n bnadem.   
\m
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ẓriɣ, xzar, aqa din arebɛa n tjarrarin ɣar uɣezdis n ikiruben, ict n tjarrart ɣar uɣezdis n ijj n ukirub. Udem n tjarrarin am wudem n weẓru n texrisulit. \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Ḥiz. 1:16\x*  
\v 10 X mammec dd-ḍharen, aqa arebɛa ɣarsen ṣṣifet d icten, axmi ict n tjarrart \add tᵉttřiq nican\add* di řwesṭ n tjarrart \add nneɣni\add*.  
\v 11 Xmi gguren, gguren ɣar arebɛa n iɣezdisen \add nsen\add*. Nitni war ttneqřiben ca xmi gguren, minzi amcan mani tarra \add tjarrart\add* n zzat azeǧif nnes, aqa ḍfaren tt-i-dd. Nitni war nnqeřben ca xmi gguren.  
\v 12 Marra arrimet nsen: iɛurar nsen, ifassen nsen d wafriwen nsen, uca uřa d tijarrarin nsen ccuren s tiṭṭawin deg wenneḍ nsen ɣar \add marra\add* arebɛa \add imuddaren\add* nni, \add wah ɛad\add* tijarrarin nsen.  
\v 13 Sřiɣ \add ict n tmijja\add* aqa tᵉttřaɣa asent i tjarrarin: ‘Tajarrart n ddewran!’  
\v 14 Kuř ijj ɣares arebɛa n wudmawen: udem amezwaru \add tuɣa\add* d udem n ukirub, u udem wiss tnayen d udem n bnadem, u \add udem\add* wiss třata d udem n weyrad, u \add udem\add* wiss arebɛa d udem n ugider.   
\m
\v 15 Ssgeɛɛden ikiruben ixef nsen. Wa d simant n umuddar i ẓriɣ ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur.  
\v 16 Umi uyuren ikiruben, uyurent uřa d tijarrarin ɣar uɣezdis nsen, umi ssgeɛɛden ikiruben afriwen nsen maḥend ad ssgeɛɛden ixef nsen zi temmurt, war qnunnyent tjarrarin nni ařami aggʷejent x uɣezdis nsen. \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Ḥiz. 1:19\x*  
\v 17 Umi bedden nitni, beddent uřa d nitenti, umi ssgeɛɛden nitni ixef nsen, ssgeɛɛdent uřa d nitenti ixef nsent, minzi buḥbeř n imuddaren \add tuɣa-t\add* daysent. \x ◘ \xo 10:17 \xt Ḥiz. 1:20\x*   
\m
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ uɛuǧi n SIDI zi sennej n tnebdat n Taddart uca ibedd sennej i ikiruben.  
\v 19 Ikiruben ssgeɛɛden afriwen nsen uca, umi dd-ffɣen, ssgeɛɛden ixef nsen zi temmurt zzat i tiṭṭawin inu uca uřa d tijarrarin ɣar uɣezdis nsen. Nitni qqimen bedden ɣar wadaf n Tewwart n Ccarq n Taddart n SIDI uca aɛuǧi n AREBBI \add tuɣa-t\add* xasen zi sennej.  
\v 20 Wa d amuddar i ẓriɣ sadu AREBBI n Israil ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur. \add Xenni\add* ssneɣ belli tuɣa aten d ikiruben. \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Ḥiz. 1:3\x*  
\v 21 Kuř ijj ɣares arebɛa n wudmawen u kuř ijj ɣares arebɛa n wafriwen u sadu afriwen nsen aqa din min yarwesen deg ifassen n iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 10:21 \xt Ḥiz. 1:6, 8; 10:8, 14\x*  
\v 22 Udmawen nsen am wudmawen nni ẓriɣ ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur, mammec dd-banen \add wudmawen nni\add*, uřa d nitni s yixef nsen. Nitni gguren kuř ijj nican ɣar zzat nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Řḥukm x řḥukkam  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed ayi Arruḥ \add ɛawed\add* uca indeh ayi ɣar Tewwart n Ccarq n Taddart n SIDI nni iǧan ɣar ccarq, u xzar, ɣar wadaf n tewwart \add aqa din\add* xemsa u-ɛicrin n yeryazen u di řwesṭ nsen ẓriɣ Yazanya\add hu\add*, mmis n Ɛazur, u Falaṭya, mmis n Banaya, řḥukkam n řgens.  
\v 2 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ina d iryazen nni ittxarriṣen di ddeǧ, tticen ccwar aɛeffan di tendint-a,  
\v 3 qqaren: ‘War bennam ɛad tudrin deg wussan-a! Tanita d marmita uca neccin d aysum!’”\f ◼ \fr 11:3 \ft \+fk Tanita\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘tandint-a’.\f*   
\m
\v 4 “S uya nabb xasen, nabb, \add cek\add*, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem!”  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* iwḍa-dd Arruḥ n SIDI xafi uca Netta inna ayi: “Ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI! Ammu i tessiwřem kenniw, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, maɣar Necc ssneɣ řeḥwayej nni ittgeɛɛaden ɣar buḥbeř nwem.  
\v 6 Tarnim \add řxecbat n\add* yinni ittwanɣen nwem di tendint-a uca teccurem ibriden nnes s \add řxecbat n\add* yinni ittwanɣen!’”   
\m
\v 7 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Inni zzaywem ittwanɣen, inni tessarsem di řwesṭ nnes, aqa aten d aysum u nettat d marmita, \add maca\add* Necc ad kenniw ssuffɣeɣ zi řwesṭ nnes. \f ◼ \fr 11:7 \ft \+fk dayes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘di řwest nnes’.\f*  
\v 8 Ssif tᵉtteggʷdem, d ssif ad xawem dd-ssekkeɣ, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 9 Necc ad kenniw nedheɣ zi řwest nnes uca ad wceɣ kenniw deg ufus n ibarraniyyen uca ad ggeɣ řeḥkamat jar awem.  
\v 10 S ssif ad tewḍam. Di temmurt n Israil ad xawem ḥekmeɣ uca ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.  
\v 11 Tandint-a war d awem tᵉttiři d marmita u kenniw war dayes tᵉttiřim d aysum. Necc ad xawem ḥekmeɣ di temmurt n Israil.  
\v 12 Kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, minzi war tuyurem di tweṣṣa inu u war teggim ɛlaḥsab lfarayiḍ inu, \add maca\add* teggim am mammec lfarayiḍ n řegnus i d awem dd-ittennḍen.’”   
\m
\v 13 Řami tuɣa ttnabbiɣ, imsar aqa Falaṭya, mmis n Banaya, immut. \add Xenni\add* wḍiɣ ɣar temmurt s uɣembub inu uca řaɣiɣ s tmijja ijehden, nniɣ: “A, Sidi inu, SIDI, ma ad teqḍid min iqqimen zi Israil?”   
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 15 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, aqa d aytmac, aytmac, iryazen nni \add iǧan\add* d imefdiyyen nwem d marra taddart n Israil, aqa-ten marra d inni i d asen nnan imezdaɣ n Urcalim: ‘Aggʷejem x SIDI, tammurt-a temmewc aneɣ d tasɣart!’”  
\v 16 “S uya ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Waxxa Necc ssiggʷejeɣ ten jar řegnus, waxxa Necc bezzɛeɣ ten x temmura, s marra aya ad asen iřiɣ \add ɛad\add* cwayt d Zzawect Iqeddsen di temmura mani ɣa yawḍen.’”  
\v 17 “S uya ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Necc ggur ad kenniw ssmuneɣ zi řegnus, ad kenniw ssmuneɣ zi temmura mani ɣa tᵉttwabezzɛem u Necc ad awem wceɣ tammurt n Israil.  
\v 18 Nitni ad din awḍen u ad zzayes kksen marra nnɛawat nnes n l’aṣnam d marra jjɛayef nnes.  
\v 19 Necc ad asen wceɣ ijj n wuř d ijj n buḥbeř n jdid di daxeř nwem. Ad kkseɣ uř n weẓru zi arrimet nsen u ad asen wceɣ uř n weysum, \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Irm. 32:39; Ḥiz. 36:26\x*  
\v 20 ḥima ad uyuren di tweṣṣa inu u ad ḥḍan lfarayiḍ inu u ad \add zzaysent\add* ggen. Ad iřin d řgens inu u Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nsen. \x ◘ \xo 11:20 \xt Irm. 24:7; 30:22; 31:1; 32:38\x*  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* \add inni\add* uř \add nsen\add* ad iḍfar uř n nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam d jjɛayef nsen, Necc ad ggeɣ ibriden nsen x uzeǧif nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 11:21 \xt Ḥiz. 9:10\x*   
\m
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* ssgeɛɛden ikiruben afriwen nsen u tijarrarin \add tuɣa\add* zzatsen uca aɛuǧi n AREBBI n Israil \add tuɣa-t\add* xasen sennej nsen. \f ◼ \fr 11:22 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  
\v 23 \add Xas uca\add* igeɛɛed uɛuǧi n SIDI zi řwesṭ n tendint uca \add iqqim\add* ittbedda x wedrar nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar ccarq n tendint.  
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed ayi-dd Arruḥ uca yiwi ayi deg ijj n řewḥiy s Arruḥ n AREBBI ɣar \add temmurt\add* n Ikaldaniyyen ɣar ayt n lmenfa. \add Awarni man aya\add* igeɛɛed zzayi řewḥiy i ẓriɣ,  
\v 25 u nniɣ i ayt n lmenfa marra min tuɣa d ayi isscen SIDI.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Arcam n tmeḥbast  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, cek tzeddɣed deg ict n taddart iɣewwɣen, maɣar nitni ɣarsen tiṭṭawin maḥend ad ttwařan, \add maca\add* war ttwiřin, uřa d imejjanen maḥend ad sřen, \add maca\add* war ttesřin, minzi nitni d ict n taddart iɣewwɣen. \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt Ica. 6:9, 10; Irm. 5:21; Ḥiz. 2:3-8; 3:26, 27\x*  
\v 3 Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, sewjed řeḥwayej i lmenfa uca uyur di lmenfa zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen. Ad tuyured di lmenfa zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen zeg wemcan nnec ɣar ijj n wemcan nneɣni. Ad taɣ ad neɛmen aqa aten d ict n taddart iɣewwɣen.  
\v 4 Ad tessuffɣed řeḥwayec nnec deg uziř zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen am řeḥwayec i lmenfa, ad teffɣed di tmeddit zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, amecnaw \add iwdan\add* inni igguren di lmenfa.  
\v 5 Egg anuqqib di řḥiḍ zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen uca suffeɣ \add marra aya\add* zzayes.  
\v 6 Zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen ad tawyed \add aya\add* x tɣarḍin nnec, di tbambast ad tessuffɣed \add aya\add*. Ad teffared udem nnec, \add ařami\add* war tẓarred tammurt, minzi ggiɣ cek d řeɛřamet n řeɛjeb i taddart n Israil.”  
\v 7 Necc ggiɣ am mammec i d ayi iweṣṣa. S uziř ssuffɣeɣ řeḥwayec inu am řeḥwayec i lmenfa. Ɣar tmeddit ɣziɣ s ufus inu x řḥiḍ u di ǧiřet ssuffɣeɣ \add marra\add* ɣar barra uca iwyeɣ t x tɣarḍin \add inu\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen.   
\m
\v 8 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI x tuffut, inna:  
\v 9 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ma war d ac tenna taddart n Israil, taddart iɣewwɣen \add nni\add*: ‘Min tᵉttegged?’  
\v 10 Ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI! Řḥukm issaggʷaden wanita \add ad yiři x\add* řḥakem di Urcalim u x marra taddart n Israil, inni izeddɣen jar asen.’  
\v 11 Ini: ‘Necc d řeɛřamet n řeɛjeb i kenniw. Am mammec ggiɣ necc, ammu i ɣa ggen daysen, ad ttwanedhen di lmenfa, di tmeḥbast.  
\v 12 Řḥakem nni \add iǧan\add* di řwesṭ nsen, ad yarbu \add řeḥwayec\add* x teɣruḍt nnes di ǧiřet uca ad iffeɣ. Nitni ad ɣzan x řḥiḍ maḥend ad zzayes t ssuffɣen. Netta ad ideř aɣembub nnes ařami ɣa iqqim war izemmar ad iẓar \add ɛad\add* tammurt s tiṭṭ\add awin\add* \add nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt 2 Ij. 25:4\x*  
\v 13 Necc ad xasen bezzɛeɣ tracca inu ařami ɣa idweř d ameḥbus di řfex inu uca ad t awyeɣ ɣar Babil, \add ɣar\add* temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen. Netta \add maca\add* war tt iẓarr, \add maca waxxa amenni\add* ad din immet. \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt Ḥiz. 17:20\x*  
\v 14 Marra inni d as dd-innḍen maḥend ad t ɛawnen d marra bandiyyat n řɛeskar nnes, ad ten bezzɛeɣ i marra tiɣemmura n usemmiḍ uca ad jebdeɣ ssif awarni asen. \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Ḥiz. 5:10, 12\x*  
\v 15 \add Ammu i\add* ɣa ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, xmi ten ɣa bezzɛeɣ jar řegnus uca ad ten zuzzareɣ di temmura.  
\v 16 Maca ad zzaysen jjeɣ ca n yeryazen \add inni inejmen\add* zi ssif, zi řaẓ u zi ṭṭaɛun, ḥima ad ɛawden i řegnus mani ɣa yawḍen, x marra jjɛayef nsen nni ggin. \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 17 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 18 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ad tecced aɣrum nnec s tarjiji uca ad teswed aman nnec s warjef d wecḍan.  
\v 19 Ad tinid i řgens n temmurt: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, x imezdaɣ n Urcalim \add i yeǧan\add* x wudem n temmurt n Israil: Nitni ad ccen aɣrum nsen s wecḍan u ad swen aman nsen s wejɛar, minzi marra aɛemmar nnes ad ittwakkes zi temmurt zi ssibbet n lɛunf n marra inni dayes izeddɣen. \x ◘ \xo 12:19 \xt Ḥiz. 4:16\x*  
\v 20 Tineddam izeddɣen ad dewřent d řxirbet uca tammurt ad tᵉttwareddeǧ. Ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řḥukm aqa iqarreb-dd  
\m
\v 21 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 22 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, man amedya nni ɣarwem din di temmurt n Israil, umi teqqarem: ‘Ɛeddun wussan uca war dd-iffiɣ ura d ijj n řewḥiy’?”   
\m
\v 23 “S uya ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Necc ad ssbeddeɣ amedya-ya, ařami ɣa qqimen war qqaren ɛad man aya am umedya di Israil.’”  
\m “S uya siweř akidsen \add ammu\add*: ‘Aqa iwḍen-dd ussan \add nni\add*, uca uřa d aseqfeř n kuř řewḥiy!’  
\v 24 Minzi war ittiři ɛad řewḥiy war iǧin uřa d tagezzant s wawařen imiziḍen di taddart n Israil.  
\v 25 Minzi Necc, SIDI, ad ssiwřeɣ. Awař i ɣa ssiwřeɣ, ad yiři, war ittɛeṭṭař ɛad, minzi deg wussan nwem, \add a\add* taddart iɣewwɣen, ad ssiwřeɣ ijj n wawař uca ad t ggeɣ, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\m
\v 26 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 27 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, xzar, inni n taddart n Israil, inni iqqaren: ‘Řewḥiy nni ittwařa aqa-t i \add yijj n řweqt awarni\add* i waṭṭas n wussan, ittnabba x \add wussan n\add* zzmanat iggʷejen aṭṭas.’”  
\v 28 “S uya ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: War ittɛeṭṭař ɛad uřa d ijj zeg wawařen inu. Awař i nniɣ, ad yiři, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Awař ḍidd i inabiyyen issxarriqen  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, nabb ḍidd i inabiyyen n Israil inni ittnebban, uca ini i yinni ittnebban ɣar \add meẓri\add* n wuř nsen: ‘Srem i wawař n SIDI!  
\v 3 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Uct x inabiyyen ibuḥařiyyen nni igguren awarni i buḥbeř n yixef nsen u awarni min war ẓrin!  
\v 4 \add A\add* Israil, inabiyyen nwem dewřen am yiceɛbawen jar řxirbat.  
\v 5 War tuřyem ɣar tizzeyyin \add di řeḥyuḍ n tendint\add* niɣ tebnam řḥiḍ i taddart n Israil, ḥima ad teqqimem tᵉttbeddam deg umenɣi deg wass n SIDI.  
\v 6 Nitni ttwařin min war iǧin, uca \add ssawařen\add* tagezzant issxarriqen, aqa inni iqqaren: SIDI iqqar!, waxxa SIDI war ten issekk ca, \add ɛad\add* sittimen belli awař ad iffeɣ.  
\v 7 Ma kenniw war teẓrim \add xenni\add* iweḥḥan war iǧin, niɣ war tessiwiřem kenniw tagezzant issxarriqen umi teqqarem: SIDI iqqar!, \add waxxa\add* Necc war ssiwiřeɣ ca?’”   
\m
\v 8 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Minzi tessawařem řbaṭeř u tᵉttwařam \add iweḥḥan\add* issxarriqen, s uya, xzar, Necc aqa ayi xawem, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 9 Ad yiři ufus inu ḍidd i inabiyyen nni ittwařan řbaṭeř u ttgezzanen s ixarriqen. Nitni war ttɣimin ca deg wegraw n řgens inu u war ttwazemmimen ca di lista n taddart n Israil u war dd-ttasen x wudem n temmurt n Israil. Kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc, Sidi, d SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 10 “Minzi, \add wah,\add* minzi nitni ttɣarran řgens inu, qqaren: ‘Řehna!’ am war iǧi řehna, \add ammu\add* i ɣa ibna \add řgens\add* ijj n řḥiḍ ittenhezzan. Uca xzarem, \add xenni\add* ttřeḥḥafen as \add ɛawed\add* s jjar.  
\v 11 Ini i yinni ittřeḥḥafen \add řḥiḍ\add* s jjar, belli ad iwḍa. Ad dd-yas wenẓar ijehden uca kenniw, \add a\add* ibquqen imeqqranen n tebruri, ad tewḍam, uca isemmiḍen n tḥaryaḍt ad dd-ffɣen s jjehd.  
\v 12 Uca xzar, xmi iwḍa řḥiḍ, ma war d awem qqaren: ‘Mani iǧa jjar i zi d as třeḥḥfem?’”   
\m
\v 13 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Deg wesɛar inu ad t arẓeɣ s isemmiḍen n tḥaryaḍt u s weɣḍab inu ad yiři wenẓar ijehden aṭṭas u s wesɛar inu \add ad wḍan\add* ibquqen imeqqranen n tebruri ařami ɣa iqḍa. \x ◘ \xo 13:13 \xt Asa.16:21\x*  
\v 14 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ɣeḍřeɣ řḥiḍ nni třeḥḥfem s jjar ifesyen u Necc ad t mmenḍareɣ ɣar temmurt ařami ɣa ittwaɛarra dsas nnes. Ad tewḍa tendint u kenniw ad tᵉttwahellkem di řwesṭ nnes uca ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.  
\v 15 Ad nḍareɣ asɛar inu x řḥiḍ u x yinni t idřin s jjar uca ad awem iniɣ: War din iǧi \add ɛad\add* řḥiḍ uřa d yinni d as iřeḥḥfen,  
\v 16 inabiyyen n Israil nni inebban x Urcalim uca twařin ijj n řewḥiy n řehna i nettat am war iǧi řehna!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Awař ḍidd i tnabbiyin issxarriqen  
\m
\v 17 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, arr udem nnec ɣar yessis n řgens nnec, tinni ittnebban zeg wuř n yixef nsent, u nebba xasent,  
\v 18 ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Uct \add x temɣarin\add* nni ittxeyyaḍen řecfen x marra řemfaṣeř n ifassen inu uca tteggent iřeḥḥaf x uzeǧif n umeqqran d umeẓyan maḥend ad gmarent řeɛmur! Ma texsent ad tegmarent řeɛmur n řgens inu u ad teḥḍant tudart n yixef nkent?  
\v 19 Ma texsent ad ayi tessfesdent ɣar řgens inu di ṭṭweɛ n ca n wurawen n imendi d ca n iřeqqwaz n weɣrum, maḥend ad tenɣent řeɛmur, nni war iɛeddeř ad mmten u maḥend ad teḥḍant tudart n řeɛmur nni war iɛeddeř ad qqimen ddaren, s ixarriqen nkent ɣar řgens inu nni issḥessan ɣar uxarriq?’” \x ◘ \xo 13:19 \xt Mixa 3:5\x*   
\m
\v 20 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, ad arreɣ řecfen nkent i zi tyemmarent din, ad ḍwen ak-d řeɛmur. Ad ten qeřɛeɣ zeg iɣaǧen nkent uca ad deřqeɣ i řeɛmur i tyemmarent, \add ad ggeɣ\add* řeɛmur ad ḍwen.  
\v 21 Ad carrgeɣ iřeḥḥafen nkent uca ad ssnejmeɣ řgens inu zeg ifassen nkent ařami nitni war ttiřin ɛad d takeccaḍt deg ifassen nkent. \add Xenni\add* kennint ad tessnent belli Necc d SIDI,  
\v 22 minzi kennint tessxeyyqent uř n umsegged s ixarriqen, umi Necc simant inu war dayes ggiɣ řeḥriq u minzi kennint tessjehdent ifassen n iɛeffanen ařami aɛeffan war dd-idwiř zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan maḥend ad iqqim iddar.”   
\m
\v 23 “S uya war tẓarrem ɛad \add iweḥḥan\add* war iǧin u war tᵉtteggem ɛad s tgezzant. Necc ad ssnejmeɣ řgens inu zeg ufus nwem u kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Awař ḍidd i yenni iɛebbden l’aṣnam  
\m
\v 1 Usin-dd ɣari \bd yeryazen zeg imɣaren n Israil\bd* uca qqimen zzati. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt Ḥiz. 20:1\x*  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 3 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, iryazen-a ssgeɛɛden imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam nsen\add* deg wuř nsen uca ggin taɛenkrift i dd-yiwyen řmuɛṣiyyet nsen nican zzat i yixef nsen. Ma Necc ad ten jjeɣ ɛad ad ttaren ccwar zzayi?”  
\v 4 “S uya, cek, siweř akidsen uca ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Kuř aryaz zi taddart n Israil nni issgeɛɛden imeyḍa n l’aṣnam deg wuř nnes uca igga taɛenkrift i dd-yiwyen řmuɛṣiyyet nnes nican zzat i wudem nnes uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-yas ɣar unabi, Necc, SIDI, ad xas dd-yarr, mařa ittas-dd, anect \add řqedd n\add* ubarru n imeyḍa nnes n l’aṣnam,  
\v 5 ḥima ammu i ɣa řeqfeɣ taddart n Israil deg wuř nsen, maɣar aggʷejen xafi marra zi ssibbet n imeyḍa nsen n l’aṣnam.’”   
\m
\v 6 “S uya, ini i taddart n Israil: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Dewřem-dd uca qeřbem x imeyḍa nwem n l’aṣnam uca arrem iɣembab nwem x marra jjɛayef nwem.’  
\v 7 Minzi i kuř aryaz zi taddart n Israil u zi ibarrani\add yyen\add* nni izeddɣen di Israil - wenni i ɣa yaggʷejen zi ḍeffar inu u ittejja ad dd-adfen imeyḍa n l’aṣnam ɣar wuř nnes uca igga taɛenkrift i dd-ittawyen řmuɛṣiyyet nnes nican zzat i wudem nnes uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-yas ɣar unabi, maḥend ad yarzu zzayes ccwar - aqa Necc d SIDI ad xas dd-arreɣ.  
\v 8 Necc ad arreɣ udem inu ḍidd i weryaz nni uca ad t ssjɛareɣ ařami \add i ɣa idweř\add* d ict n řeɛřamet d ijj n umedya. Necc ad t qeḍɛeɣ zi řwesṭ n řgens inu u kenniw ad tessnem aqa Necc d SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 14:8 \xt Aɛwd. 28:37; Ḥiz. 5:15\x*   
\m
\v 9 “‘Xmi ijj n unabi ijja ixef nnes ad as ɣarren uca issiweř ijj n wawař, \add xenni\add* Necc, SIDI, ad ɣarreɣ anabi nni uca ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd nnes uca ad t teḥḥiɣ zi řwest n řgens inu n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 14:9 \xt Ḥiz. 13:1, 2, 9\x*  
\v 10 Nitni ad arbun řmuɛṣiyyet nsen. Anect n řmuɛṣiyyet n yinni yarezzun ccwar, ammu i ɣa tiři řmuɛṣiyyet n unabi \add nni\add*,  
\v 11 ḥima taddart n Israil war tᵉttweddar \add ɛad\add* zi ḍeffar inu u nitni war ssxemmajen \add ɛad\add* ixef nsen s marra ixeṭṭan nsen. \add Xenni\add* ad ayi iřin d řgens u Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nsen!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Třata n imseggaden d arebɛa n řeḥkamat  
\m
\v 12 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 13 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, mařa texḍa ict n temmurt akidi am tᵉttegg s řɣedran ameqqran, \add xenni\add* Necc ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd nnes. Ad arẓeɣ řeɛweč n weɣrum nnes u ad ssekkeɣ dayes řaẓ u ammu i ɣa teḥḥiɣ am bnadem am řmař. \x ◘ \xo 14:13 \xt Lawi 26:26; Ḥiz. 4:16; 5:16\x*  
\v 14 Mařa tuɣa aten di řwest nnes třata n yeryazen-a, Nuḥ d Daniyil d Ayub, ad fekken nitni mɣir řeɛmar \add n yixef nsen\add* s tsegda nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 14:14 \xt Irm. 15:1\x*   
\m
\v 15 “Mařa ggiɣ ad ẓwan imuddaren n řexřa x temmurt uca ad zzayes keccḍen iḥenjiren, ařami tedweř d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen, ařami war yeǧi wi ssenni i ɣa yeɛdun zi ssibbet n řewḥuc iwɛaren,  
\v 16 \add waxxa tuɣa\add* třata n yeryazen nni di řwesṭ nnes, s tidett am ddareɣ Necc, issawař Sidi inu, SIDI, war zemmaren nitni ad fekken iḥenjiren niɣ tiḥenjirin, ad fekken mɣir ixef nsen, \add maca\add* tammurt ad tedweř d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen.”   
\m
\v 17 “Niɣ ad ssiwḍeɣ ssif x temmurt nni, ad iniɣ: ‘Ssif, ekk x temmurt!’, ařami zzayes i ɣa qeḍɛeɣ bnadem d řmař,  
\v 18 s tidett am ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, waxxa \add tuɣa\add* třata n yeryazen nni di řwesṭ nnes, war zemmaren nitni ad fekken iḥenjiren niɣ tiḥenjirin, ad fekken mɣir ixef nsen.”   
\m
\v 19 “Niɣ ad ssekkeɣ ṭṭaɛun ɣar temmurt nni uca ad ssfarɣeɣ asɛar inu \add ixeǧḍen\add* s idammen ařami zzayes i ɣa qeḍɛeɣ bnadem d řmař,  
\v 20 \add s tidett am\add* ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, \add waxxa tuɣa\add* Nuḥ d Daniyal d Ayub di řwesṭ nnes, war zemmaren nitni ad fekken iḥenjiren niɣ tiḥenjirin, ad fekken mɣir ixef nsen s tsegda nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 14:20 \xt Irm. 15:1\x*   
\m
\v 21 “Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Mahu xmi ɣa ssekkeɣ ḍidd i Urcalim arebɛa n řeḥkamat inu iqesḥen \add marra\add*: ssif d řaẓ d řmař n řexřa d ṭṭaɛun, maḥend ad zzayes qeḍɛeɣ bnadem d řmař!  
\v 22 Uca xzar, ad dayes qqimen \add ɛad\add* inni innejmen u nitni ad ttwanedhen barra, \add am\add* iḥenjiren \add am\add* tḥenjirin. Xzar, ad ɣarwem dd-ffɣen uca kenniw ad tẓarem abrid nsen d řexdayem nsen uca kenniw ad ttwassfewwjem x řɣar nni ssiwḍeɣ x Urcalim, \add wah,\add* x marra min xas ssiwḍeɣ.  
\v 23 Nitni ad kenniw ssfewwjen xmi ɣa tẓarem abrid nsen d řexdayem nsen uca kenniw ad tessnem belli marra min dayes ggiɣ, war t ggiɣ břa ssibbet, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Tazayart n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, min iɛna ukeccuḍ n tzayart ktar zeg ukeccuḍ \add nneɣni\add*, \add ktar zeg\add* ukeccuḍ nni din \add iǧan\add* jar tcejjura n wezɣar? \f ◼ \fr 15:2 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  
\v 3 Ma izemmar \add bnadem\add* ad zzayes iksi akeccuḍ maḥend ad zzayes igg ict n řqecɛet ineffɛen i řxedmet? Ma ittwakksi zzayes ict n řewted ḥima ad dayes tayřed ca n řqecɛet?  
\v 4 Xzar, ad immewc d macca i tmessi. Timessi ad tecc tnayen n ṭṭrufa nnes u aɣezdis n řwest ittwacemḍ. Ma ad iṣřeḥ \add ukeccuḍ nni ɛad\add* i yict n řqecɛet i řxedmet?  
\v 5 Xzar, umi tuɣa \add ɛad\add* imun, war zzayes tᵉttwagg ict n řqecɛet i řxedmet. Mecḥař qell ɛad umi t tecca timessi, icmeḍ \add ukeccuḍ\add*. Ma ad zzayes ggen ɛad ca n řqecɛet i řxedmet?”   
\m
\v 6 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Mammec i wciɣ akeccuḍ n tzayart jar ukeccuḍ n wezɣar i timessi, ḥima ad ittwacc, ammu i ɣa sellmeɣ uřa d imezdaɣ n Urcalim \add i tmessi\add*!  
\v 7 Maɣar Necc ad arreɣ udem inu ḍidd nsen. \add Xmi\add* i ɣa xsen ad dd-ffɣen zi tmessi, ad ten tessecmeḍ tmessi u kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, umi ggiɣ udem inu ḍidd nsen.  
\v 8 Ad arreɣ tammurt d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen, minzi nitni ɣdaren ayi s ict řeɣdaret iqesḥen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Řeɣdar n Urcalim i SIDI AREBBI  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, scen i Urcalim jjɛayef nnes,  
\v 3 uca ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, i Urcalim: X ř’aṣeř nnem d wexřaq nnem aqa cem zi temmurt n ayt n Kenɛan. Tuɣa babam d Amuri u yemmam d Taḥittit.  
\v 4 \add Ɣar\add* třařit nnem, deg wass nni di dd-tᵉttwaxeřqed, war d am qessen taɛebbut niɣ ssirden cem s waman, ḥima ad cem ssizdegen. War cem meǧḥen s tmeǧaḥt niɣ cem ssennḍen s teḥřucin.  
\v 5 Tuɣa war txezzar i cem uřa d ict n tiṭṭ, ḥima ad am yegg ca zi ddegga, ḥima ad am tezziǧez, \add maca\add* temmenḍared x wudem n yeyyar s řḥegra n řeɛmar nnem deg wass nni di dd-tᵉttwaxeřqed.’”   
\m
\v 6 “\add Umi\add* ẓwiɣ zzatek, ẓriɣ cem tᵉttneqřabed deg idammen nnem. Necc nniɣ am umi cem tuɣa deg idammen nnem: ‘Ddar!’, \add wah,\add* Necc nniɣ am umi tuɣa cem deg idammen nnem: ‘Ddar!’  
\v 7 Arniɣ dayek ařami tfeyyḍed am uɣemmuy n yeyyar. Cem teymid, temɣared uca tiwḍed ad tiřid tecnid aṭṭas. Idmaren nnem jemden u ucuwwaf nnem imɣar, \add maca\add* tuɣa cem d taɛaryant d taqeddidt.  
\v 8 \add Umi\add* ẓwiɣ zzatem, ẓriɣ cem uca xzar, ussan nnem \add iwḍen\add*, ussan n tayri. Necc sswiẓẓḍeɣ afriw\add en\add* inu xam uca dřiɣ tuɛɛaryent nnem. Jjuǧeɣ ict n tjaǧit di ṭṭweɛ nnem uca udfeɣ ɣar Řɛahd akidem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, uca \add ammu i\add* tdewřed inu. \x ◘ \xo 16:8 \xt Amz. 22:16; 24:7\x*  
\v 9 Ssirdeɣ cem s waman uca sřiřeɣ idammen nnem zzayem uca dehneɣ cem s zzect.  
\v 10 Necc ssyarḍeɣ cem s warruḍ n uburḍa s tintat ifarzen uca ssɣuneɣ cem s tsiřa n teřmect n ddenfiř uca ssbeyseɣ cem s řeqṭen azdad uca dřiɣ cem s řehrir.  
\v 11 Qqneɣ cem s řehzuṭ uca ggiɣ am tmeqyasin ɣar ifassen nnem d ict n tseddect deg yiri nnem.  
\v 12 Ggiɣ taxadent di tinzart nnem d texrazin deg imejjan nnem d ttaj icnan x uzeǧif nnem.  
\v 13 \add Ammu i\add* tᵉttwazehhjed s wureɣ d nnuqart uca arruḍ nnem tuɣa-t s řeqten azdad d řehrir d uburḍar s tintat ifarzen. Cem tuɣa teccid aren azdad d tamment d zzect. Tuɣa cem tecnid aṭṭas uca tfeřḥed ařami tdewřed tessdahjed tagelda.  
\v 14 Iffeɣ zzayek ijj n yisem jar řegnus zi ssibbet n waẓri nnem, minzi tuɣa aẓri nnem nican zeg ucewwar inu i xam ssarseɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\m
\v 15 “\add Maca\add* tᵉttiqqed deg weẓri \add n yixef\add* nnem uca tessefsed ixef nem \add am tᵉttiqqed\add* deg yisem nnem uca tfarrɣed farq-ccɣeř nnem x marra wi yeɛdun: i wanita tuɣa aẓri nnem.  
\v 16 Teksid ca zeg warruḍ nnem, teggid řegɛudi s tintat aṭṭas i yixef nnem uca tesseffsᵉded ixef nnem din. Am man aya ɛemmarṣ war imsar u ɛemmarṣ war ittiři ɛad.  
\v 17 Teksid řehzuṭ n wureɣ inu d nnuqart inu nni d ac wciɣ uca teggid zi man aya řexyařat n yeryazen i yixef nnem uca tessefsᵉded ixef nnem zzaysen.  
\v 18 Teksid arruḍ n uburḍar s tintat ifarzen uca třeḥḥfed asen \add zzayes\add* uca tessarsed zzect inu d řebxur inu zzatsen.  
\v 19 Aɣrum inu nni d am wciɣ, waren azdad d zzect d tamment i zi cem ssecceɣ, aqa tessarsed aya d arriḥet ittfuḥen zzatsen, \add ammu i\add* imsar, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.   
\m
\v 20 Iḥenjiren nnem d yessim nni dd-turwed i Necc, aqa teksid ten uca tqeddmed ten d macca i nitni. Ma \add xenni\add* farq-ccɣeř nnem d drust waha,  
\v 21 ařami tɣarṣed i iḥenjiren inu uca tezzenzed ten umi ten tessekked x tmessi? \x ◘ \xo 16:21 \xt Ica. 57:5\x*  
\v 22 Ɣar marra jjɛayef nnem d farq-ccɣeř nnem war tidared deg wussan n temẓi nnem umi tuɣa cem d taɛaryant, tᵉttwaɛarrid \add u\add* tᵉttneqřabed deg idammen nnem.  
\v 23 Awarni marra řɣar i teggid - ay, ayehhat xam, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI - imsar  
\v 24 aqa cek tebnid i yixef nnem ict n řgeɛɛdet uca teggid i yixef nnem di marra azzay ict n řgeɛɛdet \add ḥima ad din wehhben tiɣarṣa\add*.  
\v 25 Di marra azeǧif n webrid tebnid řegɛudi i yixef nnem. Tjeyyḥed aẓri nnem s ijj n nnɛi n webrid uca tesswiẓẓḍed iḍaren nnem i kuř ijj wi yeɛdun uca tarnid aṭṭas di farq-ccɣeř nnem.  
\v 26 Tessfesded ixef nnem uřa s ayt n Miṣra, jjiran nnem nni iqqbubbuzen s weysum \add nsen\add*. Tarnid ammu aṭṭas di farq-ccɣeř nnem maḥend ad ayi tesɛared.  
\v 27 Xzar, xenni Necc sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd nnem uca ssneqṣeɣ tasɣart nnem i d am dd-ittasen uca sellmeɣ cem ɣar meẓri n yinni cem icarrhen, \add ɣar\add* yessis n Ifilisṭiniyyen, tinni ttseḍḥant zeg webrid nnem ifeḍḥen. \x ◘ \xo 16:27 \xt 2 Im. 28:18\x*  
\v 28 Tessefsᵉded ixef nnem ak-d ayt n Accur, umi war tejjiwned. Tessefsᵉded ixef nnem akidsen, \add maca\add* war tufid ajiwen.  
\v 29 Tarnid aṭṭas di farq-ccɣeř nnem ař di temmurt n isebbaben, \add tammurt n\add* Ikaldaniyyen, uca uřa s uya war tejjiwned.  
\v 30 Mecḥař ihřec wuř nnem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, aqa teggid marra aya, řxedmet n ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř iɣewwɣen,  
\v 31 umi tebnid ict n řgeɛɛdet ɣar uzeǧif n kuř abrid, teggid ict n řgeɛɛdet \add i tewhibt n tɣarṣa\add* di kuř azzay, břa ma teǧid \add d tidett\add* d tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř umi tesseḥqared řexřaṣ \add nnem n farq-ccɣeř\add*.  
\v 32 \add A cem,\add* tamɣart izennan, tenni itteṭṭfen ibarraniyyen deg wemcan n weryaz nnes.  
\v 33 I marra timɣarin n farq-ccɣeř wcin asent řmunet, \add maca\add* cem tewcid timewca i marra inni cem ittexsen uca \add ammu i\add* ten tesseɣwid s farq-ccɣeř nnem, maḥend ad ɣarem dd-asen zi marra iɣezdisen.  
\v 34 Ammu, s farq-ccɣeř nnem, ad kidem imsar řɛeks n min imsaren i temɣarin \add nneɣni\add*, minzi war cem ḍeffaren ca maḥend ad zzayem ggen s farq-ccɣeř \add nsen\add*. Mařa cem tewcid asen řexřaṣ n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, war tᵉṭṭfed ca řexřaṣ n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, \add xenni\add* aqa cem tdewřed d řɛeks zzaysen.”   
\m
\v 35 “S uya, \add a\add* tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř, seř i wawař n SIDI.  
\v 36 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Minzi tessfarrɣed nnḥas nnem \add ittwařeḥḥfen s ddra\add* u tessɛarrid řeḥya nnem s farq-ccɣeř nnem ak-d yinni i cem ittexsen u ak-d marra imeyḍa nnem n l’aṣnam n jjɛayef nnem, u umi d asen tewcid idammen n iḥenjiren nnem,  
\v 37 xzar, s uya ad ssmuneɣ marra inni tuɣa cem ittexsen nni tuɣa i d am itteɛjiben u marra inni texsed \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra inni tcarhed. Necc ad ten dd-ssmuneɣ xam zi marra iɣezdisen uca ad ssɛarriɣ řeḥya nnem, \add ař\add* i ɣa ẓaren marra řeḥya nnem.  
\v 38 Necc ad xam carrɛeɣ ɛlaḥsab lfarayiḍ i tinni izennan d tinni issizzřen idammen uca ad cem sellmeɣ ɣar \add ijj n usizzeř n\add* idammen i dd-iffɣen zeg wesɛar d tusmi.  
\v 39 Necc ad wceɣ cem deg ufus nsen uca nitni ad arẓen řgeɛɛdet nnem uca ad areddǧen řegɛudi nnem uca ad am kksen arruḍ nnem, ad awyen řehzuṭ nnem uca ad cem jjen d taɛaryant d taqeddidt.  
\v 40 Awarni aya ad xam ssiwḍen ijj n wegraw \add d ameqqran\add* uca ad cem arejmen uca ad cem qessen s řesyuf nsen.  
\v 41 Nitni ad sscemḍen tudrin nnem s tmessi uca ad xam dd-ssehwan řeḥkamat zzat i tiṭṭawin n waṭṭas n temɣarin. Necc ad ggeɣ ad tessbedded zi farq-ccɣeř nnem, war tbeṭṭid ɛad řexřaṣ n farq-ccɣeř. \x ◘ \xo 16:41 \xt 2 Ij. 25:9; Irm. 52:13\x*  
\v 42 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ssarseɣ asɛar inu xam uca tusmi inu \add iqeddsen\add* ad xam tbeɛɛed u Necc ad dewřeɣ areyyḥeɣ, war ttɛessibeɣ ɛad.  
\v 43 Minzi war tidared deg wussan n temẓi nnem, umi d ayi tesɛared s marra aya, aqa da Necc ɛawed ad awyeɣ abrid nnem x yixef nnem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI. Ɛemmarṣ ad ggeɣ řefḍiḥet sennej i marra jjɛayef nnem \add umi Necc war cem ttɛiqibeɣ ca\add*.’”\f ◼ \fr 16:43 \ft \+bd afessar\+bd* - xzar Lawi 19:29.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 16:43 \xt Ḥiz. 9:10; 11:21; Lawi 19:29\x*   
\m
\v 44 “Xzar, marra wenni issawařen s wawařen iweznen, ad xam issawař awař-a, ad yini: ‘Am yemmas, am yeǧis!’  
\v 45 Aqa cem d yeǧis n yemmam nni iɛiffen aryaz nnes d iḥenjiren nnes u cem d učmas n suyᵉtmam nni iɛiffen zeg yeryazen nsent d iḥenjiren nsent. Tuɣa yemmam d Taḥittit u babam d Amuri.  
\v 46 Učmam tameqqrant aqa-tt Samarya, nettat d yessis nnes zeddɣen ɣar uẓermaḍ nnem, u učmam tenni d tameẓyant zzayem, tzeddeɣ ɣar yefus nnem, aqa-tt d Sadum d yessis.  
\v 47 Cem war teggured deg ibriden nsent u war teggid am jjɛayef nsent. \add Maca\add* axmi mammec ddegga tuɣa drust \add waha\add*, tfesded marra ibriden nnem ktar zzaysent.  
\v 48 S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Aqa Sadum, učmam ak-d yessis, ɛemmarṣ war teggi am teggid cem d yessim.  
\v 49 Xzar, ta d řmuɛṣiyyet n učmam Sadum: nnfaxet, tyawant n weɣrum d ict n tudart di řhudnet břa amnus, \add ammu i\add* iǧa umeddur nnes u n yessis, \add maca\add* afus n wenni ittwaḥṣaren u n umezřuḍ war d as tessejhed.  
\v 50 Nitenti nnefxent uca ggint jjɛifect zzat i wudem inu. Umi ẓriɣ aya, nḍareɣ tent. \x ◘ \xo 16:50 \xt Amz. 19:24\x*  
\v 51 \add Maca\add* Samarya war txeṭṭi uřa deg wezyen n ddnub nnem uca cem teggid jjɛayef ktar zzayes. S marra jjɛayef i teggid, tarred suyᵉtmam banent seggdent.  
\v 52 \add Xenni\add* cem ɛawed, ksi řefḍiḥet nnem, minzi tewtid x suyᵉtmam. Umi teggid ddnub d jjɛifect ktar zzaysent, banent nitenti seggdent xam. Seḍḥa u ksi řefḍiḥet nnem, minzi tarrid suyᵉtmam banent seggdent.  
\v 53 Xmi ɣa beṭṭřeɣ tameḥbast nsent, tameḥbast n Sadum d yessis, uřa d tameḥbast n Samarya d yessis, \add xenni\add* ad beṭṭřeɣ \add ɛawed\add* tameḥbast nnem di řwesṭ nsent,  
\v 54 ḥima ad teksid řefḍiḥet nnem uca ad tseḍḥid zi marra min teggid, řami cem tent tessfewwjed.  
\v 55 Mařa suyᵉtmam, Sadum d yessis, ad dd-dewřent ɣar umeddur nsent amezwaru, uca uřa d Samarya d yessis ad dd-dewřent ɣar umeddur nsent amezwaru, \add xenni\add* ad dd-tdewřed uřa d cem d yessmam ɣar umeddur nkent amezwaru.  
\v 56 Deg wass n nnfaxet nnem war ittwaseř ca zeg uqemmum nnem x \add min imsaren i\add* učmam Sadum,  
\v 57 qbeř ma iɛarra tuɛeffna nnem, am mammec \add i imsar\add* di řweqt n řḥegra s ufus n yessis n Aram d marra inni d as dd-innḍen, yessis n Ifilisṭiniyyen nni cem isseḥqaren ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnem. \x ◘ \xo 16:57 \xt Ica. 9:10-16\x*  
\v 58 Řefḍayeḥ nnem d jjɛayef nnem ad tent teksid!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 59 “Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Necc ad zzayem ggeɣ am mammec teggid cem umi tesseḥqared tajaǧit s treẓẓit n Řɛahd.  
\v 60 \add Maca ɛad\add* ad ɛeqřeɣ x Řɛahd inu akidem deg wussan n temẓi nnem uca ad ggeɣ ijj n Řɛahd i řebda i cem.  
\v 61 Xenni ad tidared deg ibriden nnem uca ad tseḍḥid xmi ɣa tawyed suyᵉtmam nni mɣarent zzayem, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d tinni timaẓuẓin xam. Necc ad am tent wciɣ d yessim, \add maca\add* war iǧi s webrid n řɛahd nnem.  
\v 62 \add Maca\add* Necc ad ggeɣ Řɛahd inu akidem uca ad tessned, aqa Necc d SIDI,  
\v 63 ḥima ad tidared dayes uca ad tseḍḥid uca war tarezzmed ɛemmarṣ ɛad aqemmum nnem zi ssibbet n řefḍiḥet nnem, xmi ɣa ggeɣ aṣřaḥ i cem x marra min teggid!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Řɣedran n Ṣidqiya  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ɛawed ict n ṭḥajit n twafit u ewc ijj n umedya i taddart n Israil  
\v 3 uca ini:  
\b  
\m ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI!  
\m \qt Agider d ameqqran s wafriwen arezmen,\qt*  
\m \qt daysen řewtad iziraren ccuren\qt*  
\m \qt s warric d tintat ifarzen,\qt*  
\m \qt yusa-dd ɣar idurar n Lubnan\qt*  
\m \qt uca ikkes tuccent n tcejjart n tengelt.\qt*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Azeǧif n řefruɛ nnes issendayen ikkes i-t,\qt*  
\m \qt uca yiwyi t ɣar ict n temmurt n ttijara\qt*  
\m \qt uca issars i-t\qt*  
\m \qt deg ict n tendint n isebbaben.\qt*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Iksi zi zzariɛet n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt uca igga i-tt deg ijj n yeyyar \+tl icna\+tl* i wezraɛ.\qt*  
\m \qt Iksi tt, iẓẓu tt\qt*  
\m \qt am tcejjart n uṣefṣaf ɣar waman aṭṭas.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Teɣmi-dd \+tl zzariɛet\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt uca tedweř d tazayart\qt*  
\m \qt s řefruɛ wessɛen\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d trunku d aquḍaḍ\qt*  
\m \qt nni zi dewřent tseḍwin \+tl ɣar ugider\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl am\+tl* tuɣa iẓewran nnes qqimen sadu nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Ammu i tedweř d ict n tzayart\qt*  
\m \qt nni issuffɣen tiseḍwin\qt*  
\m \qt uca tegga ad ssendyen ifetwan.\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \qt Tuɣa ɛawed ijj n ugider ameqqran nneɣni\qt*  
\m \qt s wafriwen imɣaren d waṭṭas n arric\qt*  
\m \qt uca xzar, tazayart tarra iẓewran nnes ɣares\qt*  
\m \qt uca tesswiẓẓeḍ tiseḍwin nnes ɣares\qt*  
\m \qt zeg iyyar mani tᵉttwaẓẓu\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima agider ad as issessu.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Tuɣa tᵉttwaẓẓu deg ijj n yeyyar isbeḥ\qt*  
\m \qt zzat i waman aṭṭas\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad tessuffeɣ tiseḍwin\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tewc řɣiǧet,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad tedweř d tazayart teccur.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Ini \add xenni\add*:  
\m ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt Ma ad iffeɣ man aya mliḥ?\qt*  
\m \qt Ma war ittekkes \+tl ugider ameqqran\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt iẓewran nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad iqḍeɛ řɣiǧet nnes\qt*  
\m \qt ařami i ɣa taẓeɣ?\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Wah\+tl* ad taẓeɣ s marra tifray\qt*  
\m \qt nni ɣares iɣemmyen,\qt*  
\m \qt war ittwaḥdij \+tl ɛad\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt uɣiř ijehden niɣ řɣaci aṭṭas\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad tt ssgeɛɛden zeg iẓewran nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 10 \qt Xzar, waxxa ẓẓun tt,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* ma \+tl xenni\+tl* ad tefřeḥ?\qt*  
\m \qt Ma war tᵉttiẓeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt xmi tt ɣa iřqef usemmiḍ n řɣarb?\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Wah\+tl*, ad taẓeɣ x iɛurar n řeɛraṣi\qt*  
\m \qt mani dd-tɣemmi.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 12 “Ini řexxu i taddart iɣewwɣen: ‘Ma war tessinem min ɛnant tmesřayin-a?’ Ini: ‘Xzar, ajeǧid n Babil yusa-dd ɣar Urcalim uca iṭṭef ajeǧid nnes d řḥukkam nnes uca yiwyi ten ɣares di Babil.  
\v 13 Iṭṭef \add ɛawed ijjen\add* zi zzariɛet igellden uca igga akides ijj n řɛahd uca yarra i-t ad iwc tajaǧit u ayt n jjehd di temmurt, aqa ikkes i-ten,  
\v 14 ḥima ad tiři tgeldit twaḍeɛ u war tessgiɛɛid ixef nnes u ḥima ad teḥḍa řɛahd nnes, ad teqqim tᵉttbedda.  
\v 15 \add Maca\add* netta iɣewweɣ xas, issekk ireqqasen nnes ɣar Miṣra, maḥend ad as wcen iysan d \add ijj n ubarru n\add* řgens. Ma ad iffeɣ aya mliḥ? Ma izemmar ad yarweř wenni iggin aya? Ma izemmar wenni yarẓin řɛahd ad yarweř?’” \x ◘ \xo 17:15 \xt Irm. 37:5\x*   
\m
\v 16 “S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Deg wemcan \add mani izeddeɣ\add* ujeǧid nni t iggin d ajeǧid, wenni zi isseḥqar netta tajaǧit \add i d as ijjuǧ\add*, d wenni zi yarẓ řɛahd \add i kides igga\add*, \add aqa din\add* ɣares, di řwest n Babil, ad immet!  
\v 17 War izemmar firɛun s ijj n řɛeskar ameqqran d ijj n wegraw imɣar ad yegg uřa d ict n řḥajjet di ṭṭweɛ nnes deg umenɣi, xmi ɣa ssgeɛɛden ijj n řḥiḍ uca xmi ɣa bnan ijj n wecbar maḥend ad nɣen aṭṭas n iwdan. \f ◼ \fr 17:17 \ft \+fk iwdan\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmur’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 17:17 \xt 2 Ij. 25:1; Ica. 29:3; Ḥiz. 4:2\x*  
\v 18 Aqa isseḥqar tajaǧit umi yarẓa řɛahd i x iwca afus nnes. \add Minzi\add* netta igga marra man aya, war ittrakkwař.’”   
\m
\v 19 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, tajaǧit i d ayi \add ijjuǧ\add* uca \add xenni\add* isseḥqar i-tt, uřa d řɛahd i kidi igga uca \add xenni\add* yarẓa i-t, ad ten-i-dd arreɣ x uzeǧif nnes!  
\v 20 Ad xas bezzɛeɣ tracca inu maḥend ad yiři icarf di řfex inu. Ad t awyeɣ ɣar Babil uca ad xas carrɛeɣ din zi ssibbet n řeɣdaret nnes i zi d ayi iɣdar. \x ◘ \xo 17:20 \xt Irm. 4:12; 25:31; Ḥiz. 12:13; 32:3\x*  
\v 21 Marra inni zzayes yarewřen \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra řɛeskar nnes, ad wḍan s ssif, uca inni iqqimen ad ttwazeǧɛen ɣar marra tiɣemmura n usemmiḍ. \add Xenni\add* kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc, SIDI, ssiwřeɣ.’” \x ◘ \xo 17:21 \xt Ḥiz. 5:10, 12; 12:14; 16:40\x*   
\m
\v 22 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Necc ad kkseɣ \add ijj n ufetwi n\add* tuccent n tcejjart n tengelt yuɛřan uca ad t ẓẓuɣ. Zeg uzeǧif ak-d tseḍwin nnes ad qeřɛeɣ ict n tseṭṭa tarhef uca ad tt ẓẓuɣ x ijj n wedrar yuɛřan.  
\v 23 Ad tt ẓẓuɣ x wedrar yuɛřan qaɛ di Israil. Tanita ad tawi tiseḍwin uca ad tarr řɣiǧet, ad tedweř d tacejjart n tengelt ijehden. Ɛřam kuř ijḍaḍ s ɛřam kuř afriwen ad zedɣen sadu nnes, \add wah,\add* di tiři nnes ad zedɣen nitni,  
\v 24 uca ad ssnen marra ticejjura n yeyyar, aqa Necc, SIDI, ssehwiɣ tacejjart yuɛřan uca ssgeɛɛdeɣ tacejjart taquḍaḍt u ssiẓɣeɣ tacejjart tazeyzat uca arriɣ tacejjart yuẓɣen ad tnewwar. Necc, SIDI, ssiwřeɣ uca ad t ggeɣ.’” \f ◼ \fr 17:24 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Ddenb n tbabat d tmemmit  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “Min kenniw yuɣin ařami i ɣa tiwyem awař-a ɣar wudem n temmurt n Israil uca teqqarem: ‘Ibabaten ccin aḍiř asemmaɣ uca tiɣmas n warraw dewřent ḥarecwent’? \x ◘ \xo 18:2 \xt Irm. 31:29\x*  
\v 3 S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘\add Uct xawem\add* mařa ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad tawyem awař-a di Israil!  
\v 4 Xzar, marra řeɛmur inu, am řeɛmar n babas uřa d řeɛmar n mmis inu. Řeɛmar nni ixḍan, ad immet.’”   
\m
\v 5 “Mařa ca n yijjen d amsegged \add i yeǧa\add*, ittegg řḥeqq d min iseggden:  
\v 6 war ittett \add ddbayeḥ\add* x idurar, war issgiɛɛid tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam\add* n taddart n Israil, war issexmij tamɣart n jjar nnes u war dd-ittqarrib ɣar temɣart nni iɛezzřen \add umi xas idammen\add*, \x ◘ \xo 18:6 \xt Lawi 15:19, 20 ; Ica. 57:7; 65:7\x*  
\v 7 war iḥeṣṣar uřa d ijj, ittarra-dd ddiyyet i bu-amarwas, war ittkeccaḍ, wenni iǧuẓen ittic as weɣrum nnes u wenni d aɛaryan issdduri i-t s warruḍ, \x ◘ \xo 18:7 \xt Uf. 22:21, 26; Lawi 19:13; 25:14; Aɛwd. 15:7; 24:12; Ica. 58:7; Mt. 25:3\x*  
\v 8 netta war yareṭṭeř s arriba niɣ ad iksi arbeḥ, afus nnes itteggʷej x min war iseggden, netta iḥekkem nican jar weryaz d ijj n weryaz \add nneɣni\add*, \x ◘ \xo 18:8 \xt Uf. 22:25; Lawi 25:35, 36\x*  
\v 9 iggur di tweṣṣa inu uca iḥeṭṭa lfarayiḍ inu umi ɣa yegg s řaman, \add xenni\add* aqa netta d amsegged, ad iddar s tidett!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 10 Mařa yejj-dd mmis d aceffar, wenni issizzařen idammen d wenni itteggen icten zi tmesřayin-a,  
\v 11 \add waxxa\add* netta \add s yixef nnes am babas\add* war ittegg timesřayin-a, \add maca\add* mmis wanita ittett \add tiwhibin\add* x idurar, issexmej tamɣart n jjar nnes,  
\v 12 iḥeṣṣar řmeskin d umezřuḍ, ittkeccaḍ, war dd-yarri ddiyyet, issgeɛɛad tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar imeyḍa n l’aṣnam, ittegg ict n jjɛifect,  
\v 13 yareṭṭeř s arriba, ittᵉṭṭef arbeḥ, ma \add xenni\add* ad iqqim \add mmis\add* wanita iddar? War ittɣimi iddar umi igga marra jjɛayef nni. Ad ittwaneɣ nican, idammen nnes ad xas iřin.”   
\m
\v 14 “Xzar, \add mařa\add* ad dd-yejj mmis nni ittwařa marra ddnub nni ittegg babas uca ixezzar \add waha\add* \add am\add* netta \add s yixef nnes\add* war ittegg timesřayin nni,  
\v 15 \add ixs ad yini\add* war ittett x idurar, war issgiɛɛid tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam\add* n taddart n Israil, war issexmij tamɣart n jjar nnes,  
\v 16 war iḥeṣṣar uřa d ijj, war imenneɛ ddiyyet, war ittkeccaḍ, ittic aɣrum nnes i wenni iǧuẓen, issdurruy i uɛaryan s warruḍ,  
\v 17 ittaggʷej s ufus nnes x umezřuḍ, war ikessi arriba d warbeḥ, ittegg s tsegda uca iḥeṭṭa tiweṣṣa inu, aqa mmis wanita war ittmetti zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet n babas, ad iddar s tidett.  
\v 18 Babas ad immet di řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, x umi igga bezzez \add x iwdan\add* s řexcunet, ikecceḍ agřa uca igga min war iḥřin di řwesṭ n řgens nnes.”   
\m
\v 19 “\add Maca\add* kenniw teqqarem: ‘Mayemmi mmis war ikessi řmuɛṣiyyet n babas? \add Minzi\add* mmis tuɣa ittegg řḥeqq d tsegda uca iḥḍa marra tiweṣṣa inu uca igga i-tent, netta ad iqqim iddar s tidett. \x ◘ \xo 18:19 \xt Aɛwd. 24:16; 2 Ij. 14:6; 2 Im. 25:4\x*  
\v 20 Řeɛmar nni ixḍan, ad immet. Mmis war ikessi ca řmuɛṣiyyet n babas uca babas war ikessi ca řmuɛṣiyyet n mmis. Tasegda n umsegged ad tiři x yixef nnes u tuɛeffna n uɛeffan ad tiři x yixef nnes.  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* mařa aɛeffan idweř-dd zi ddnub nni igga, ad iḥḍa marra tiweṣṣa inu uca ad yegg řḥeqq d tsegda, \add xenni\add* ad iqqim iddar s tidett, war ittmetti ca.  
\v 22 Marra iɛeddiyen nnes nni igga, war d as ttwaḥessben ca. S tsegda nnes nni igga, ad iddar.  
\v 23 Ma ad arḍiɣ s tidett řmewt n iɛeffanen?’, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI. ‘Ma netta war \add ittɣimi\add* iddar xmi dd ɣa idweř? \x ◘ \xo 18:23 \xt Ḥiz. 33:11\x*  
\v 24 \add Maca\add* mařa amsegged iḥeyyed x tsegda nnes uca ad igg ddeǧ ɛlaḥsab marra jjɛayef nni ittegg uɛeffan, ad igg \add amenni\add* uřa d netta, ma \add xenni\add* ad iqqim iddar? War tᵉttwaɛqiř \add ɛad\add* marra tasegda nni igga. S řeɣdaret nnes i zi iɣdar u s ddnub nnes i zi iddenb, s yina ad immet.’”   
\m
\v 25 “Teqqarem \add ɛawed\add*: ‘Abrid n Sidi war iǧi ca nican!’. Sřem, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, ma abrid inu war iǧi nican? Ma war ǧin \add s tidett\add* aqa ibriden nwem war seggmen? \x ◘ \xo 18:25 \xt Ḥiz. 33:17, 20\x*  
\v 26 Mařa iḥeyyed umsegged x tsegda nnes uca ittegg ddeǧ u s man aya ad immet, \add xenni\add* ad immet di ddeǧ nnes nni igga.  
\v 27 \add Maca\add* mařa idweř-dd uɛeffan zi tmegga nnes tiɛeffanin nni igga uca ad igg řḥeqq d tsegda, \add xenni\add* ad yarr řeɛmar nnes ad iqqim iddar.  
\v 28 Idweř ittwařa uca idweř-dd zi marra iɛeddiyen nnes nni igga. Ad iddar s tidett, war ittmetti ca.  
\v 29 Inni zi taddart n Israil yarennan qqaren: ‘Abrid n Sidi war iseggem!’ Ma ibriden inu war seggmen, \add a\add* taddart n Israil? \add D tidett\add* ma war ǧin ibriden nwem war seggmen?”  
\v 30 “S uya Necc ad xawem carrɛeɣ, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, kuř ijj anect ibriden nnes, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI. Ɛeqbem, dewřem-dd zi marra iɛeddiyen nwem, \add xenni\add* war tᵉttiři řmuɛṣiyyet nwem d taɛenkrift i dd-yiwyen řmuɛṣiyyet i kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 18:30 \xt Mt. 3:2\x*  
\v 31 Nḍarem řmuɛṣiyyet nwem i zi tɛeddam. Ggem uř \add nwem\add* d amaynu u buḥbeř \add nwem\add* d amaynu. Maɣar i ɣa temmtem, \add a\add* taddart n Israil? \x ◘ \xo 18:31 \xt Irm. 32:39; Ḥiz. 11:19; 36:26\x*  
\v 32 Minzi Necc war arḍiɣ di řmewt n wenni ittxeṣṣa ad immut, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, dewřem-dd uca ddarem.” \x ◘ \xo 18:32 \xt Ḥiz. 33:11\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 Izři n wecḍan x řḥukkam n Israil  
\m
\v 1 “Cek \add xenni\add*, sgeɛɛed ijj n yeẓri n wecḍan  
\m x řḥukkam n Israil  
\v 2 uca ini:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Mammec tuɣa tezzeř yemmatwem\qt*  
\m \qt am teyradt tezzeř jar teyradin!\qt*  
\m \qt Tessyem imeẓyanen nnes\qt*  
\m \qt jar wayraden imeẓyanen!\qt*   
\m
\v 3 \qt Nettat tesyem ijj zeg imeẓyanen nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Wanita idweř d ayrad ameẓyan,\qt*  
\m \qt iřmed ad icarreg taymart nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ɛad\+tl* iwdan icca i-ten\qt*.   
\m
\v 4 \qt \+tl Řami\+tl* sřin řegnus man aya,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥebbsen t deg \+tl weḥfur n\+tl* turṣuḍi nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt uca iwyen t s tsennarin \+tl deg wenzar nnes\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar temmurt n Miṣra.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:4 \xt 2 Ij. 23:33; Irm. 22:11\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 \qt ‘\+tl Umi\+tl* teẓra aqa řayas nnes iruḥ, ibḍeř,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl xenni\+tl* teksi ijjen zeg imeẓyanen nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt uca igga i-t d ayrad ameẓyan.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Wanita tuɣa iggur jar wayraden,\qt*  
\m \qt uca idweř d ayrad d ameẓyan,\qt*  
\m \qt iřmed ad icarreg taymart nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ɛad\+tl* iwdan icca i-ten.\qt*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Netta iɣṣeb tijjař nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt yareddeǧ tineddam nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami tsusem temmurt d marra min dayes\qt*  
\m \qt zi ssibbet n řḥess n uzehhar nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt \+tl Xenni\+tl* ssbedden xas řegnus\qt*  
\m \qt zi temmura i d as dd-innḍen\qt*  
\m \qt uca bezzɛen xas tracca nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ṭṭfen t deg \+tl weḥfur nsen n\+tl* turṣuḍi.\qt*   
\m
\v 9 \qt Nitni bellɛen xas deg ijj n řeqfez\qt*  
\m \qt s tsennarin \+tl deg wenzaren nnes\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad t awyen ɣar ujeǧid n Babil.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni iwyen t di lqelɛat,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami war ittwaseř \+tl ɛad\+tl* tmijja nnes\qt*  
\m \qt x idurar n Israil.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt 2 Im. 36:6\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 \qt ‘Tuɣa yemmac am tzayart\qt*  
\m \qt di řweqt n arraḥet nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt tᵉttwaẓẓu ɣar waman aṭṭas.\qt*  
\m \qt Tuɣa s řɣiǧet u s waṭṭas n tseḍwin,\qt*  
\m \qt zi ssibbet n waṭṭas n waman.\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Tuɣa ɣares tiseḍwin ijehden\qt*  
\m \qt am izeǧaḍ n řḥukkam.\qt*  
\m \qt Trunku \+tl n yijjen\+tl* zzayes\qt*  
\m \qt igeɛɛed jar iseynuten,\qt*  
\m \qt uca s řuɛřa nnes ittwaẓar nican,\qt*  
\m \qt s waṭṭas n řefruɛ nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt \+tl Maca tazayart\+tl* tᵉttwaqřeɛ\qt*  
\m \qt s \+tl ijj n uduqqez n\+tl* wesɛar,\qt*  
\m \qt temmenḍar ɣar temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt uca asemmiḍ zi ccarq yuẓeɣ řɣiǧet nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Arẓen uca uẓɣen řefruɛ nnes ijehden,\qt*  
\m \qt timessi tecca i-ten.\qt*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Řexxu ẓẓun t di  řexřa,\qt*  
\m \qt deg ict n temmurt yuẓɣen d iffuden.\qt*   
\m
\v 14 \qt Teffeɣ-dd tmessi zeg ict n tseṭṭa\qt*  
\m \qt zi jar tzermin nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt tecca řɣiǧet nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami war ɣares teqqim ɛad tseṭṭa ijehden\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl uřa d\+tl* azeǧaḍ maḥend ad iḥkem.’”\qt*  
\b  
\m Wa d ijj n yeẓri n wecḍan uca ad idweř d ijj n yeẓri n wecḍan \add s tidett\add*.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Aɣewweɣ n Israil  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa, deg uyur wiss xemsa, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss ɛecra n uyur\bd* imsar belli usin-dd \bd iryazen zeg imɣaren n Israil\bd*, maḥend ad sseqsan SIDI, uca qqimen zzati.  
\v 2 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 3 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, siweř ak-d imɣaren n Israil, uca ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Ma tusim-dd maḥend ad ayi tesseqsam? S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, war kenniw ttejjiɣ ad kidi temcawaren, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 4 ‘Ma texsed ad xasen tḥekmed, ma texsed ad \add xasen\add* tḥekmed, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem? Scen asen jjɛayef n řejdud nsen \x ◘ \xo 20:4 \xt Ḥiz. 22:2; 23:36\x*  
\v 5 uca ini asen: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Deg wass nni di ixḍareɣ Israil, ssgeɛɛdeɣ Necc afus inu, \add jjuǧeɣ\add* i zzariɛet n taddart n Yaɛqub uca ssecneɣ ixef nnes ɣarsen di temmurt n Miṣra. Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu di ṭṭweɛ nsen, nniɣ: Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem. \x ◘ \xo 20:5 \xt Uf. 3:8; 4:31; 6:7 \x*  
\v 6 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ssgeɛɛdeɣ asen afus inu \add jjuǧeɣ,\add* maḥend ad ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra ɣar temmurt nni ixḍareɣ Necc i nitni, \add tammurt\add* ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, aqa-tt d talwizt n marra timmura.  
\v 7 Nniɣ asen: Ejj kuř ijj ad immenḍar nnɛawat nnes n l’aṣnam zzat i tiṭṭawin nnes, ittxeṣṣa war ssxemmijen nitni ixef nwem s imeyḍa n l’aṣnam n Miṣra, Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem.’”   
\m
\v 8 “\add Maca\add* nitni ɣewwɣen xafi uca war xisen ad ɣari dd-sřen. War nḍaren nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen \add u\add* war jjin imeyḍa nsen n l’aṣnam \add nni dd-iwyen\add* zi Miṣra. \add Xenni\add* nniɣ ad xasen zeǧɛeɣ asɛar inu maḥend ad xasen kemmřeɣ lɣaḍab inu di řwesṭ n temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 9 Necc ggiɣ t di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu ařami wanita war ittwassefsad zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus nni tuɣa zeddɣen jar asen, i umi secneɣ ixef inu zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen xmi ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 10 Ssuffɣeɣ ten-dd zi temmurt n Miṣra uca nedheɣ ten ɣar řexřa. \x ◘ \xo 20:10 \xt Uf. 13:18\x*  
\v 11 Wciɣ asen tiweṣṣa inu uca ssargbeɣ ten x lfarayiḍ inu i zi ɣa iddar bnadem nni zzaysent i ɣa yegg. \x ◘ \xo 20:11 \xt Lawi 18:5; Aɛwd. 30:15, 16, 19, 20; Rum. 10:5; Gal. 3:12\x*  
\v 12 Wciɣ asen ɛawed ussan inu n ssebt maḥend ad iřin d řeɛřamet jar ayi d nitni, ḥima ad ssnen, aqa Necc d SIDI wenni ten issqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 20:12 \xt Uf. 20:8; 31:13-17; 35:2\x*  
\v 13 \add Maca\add* taddart n Israil tɣewweɣ xafi di řexřa. Nitni war uyuren ca ɛlaḥsab tiweṣṣa inu uca mmenḍaren lfarayiḍ inu i zi ɣa iddar bnaden nni tent iggin uca nitni ssɛiǧten ussan n ssebt inu ařami nniɣ tuɣa xseɣ ad xasen farrɣeɣ asɛar inu di řexřa ḥima ad xasen qḍiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 20:13 \xt Uf. 16:28\x*  
\v 14 \add Maca\add* Necc ggiɣ t di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu, ḥima wanita war ittwassɛiǧit ca zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus nni tuɣa ittwařin umi ssuffɣeɣ \add taddart n Israil\add* zi \add Miṣra\add*.  
\v 15 Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu ḍidd nsen di řexřa \add uca jjuǧeɣ\add* aqa war ten ttawyeɣ ɣar temmurt nni d asen wciɣ, tammurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, tenni yeǧan d talwizt n marra timmura,  
\v 16 minzi nitni nḍaren lfarayiḍ inu, war uyuren di tweṣṣa inu u ssɛiǧten ussan inu n ssebt, maɣar uř nsen iḍfar imeyḍa nsen n l’aṣnam.  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* semḥeɣ asen di tiṭṭawin inu ařami Necc war ten areddǧeɣ u war xasen qḍiɣ di řexřa.”   
\m
\v 18 “Necc nniɣ i iḥenjiren nsen di řexřa: ‘War ggurem di tweṣṣa n řejdud nwem, war ttᵉṭṭfem di lfarayiḍ nsen u war ssxemmijem ixef nwem s imeyḍa nsen n l’aṣnam.  
\v 19 Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem! Uyurem di tweṣṣa inu u ḥḍam lfarayiḍ inu uca ggem zzaysent.  
\v 20 Sqeddsem ussan inu n ssebt, \add maḥend\add* ad iřin d řeɛřamet jar ayi d kenniw, ḥima ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem.’  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* ɛad arraw \add nsen\add* ɣewwɣen xafi: War gguren di tweṣṣa inu u war ḥḍin lfarayiḍ inu maḥend ad daysent uyuren, min zi bnadem nni tent itteggen ad zzaysent iddar. Nitni ssɛiǧten ussan inu n ssebt \add ařami\add* nniɣ, ad xasen farrɣeɣ asɛar inu, maḥend ad asen kemmřeɣ \add ammu\add* aɣḍab inu di řexřa.  
\v 22 Necc arriɣ-dd afus inu \add i tuɣa isswiẓẓḍen ḍidd nsen\add*. Ggiɣ t di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu, ḥima war ittwassexmij \add Isem inu\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus, \add maɣar\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen ssuffɣeɣ ten-dd zi Miṣra.  
\v 23 \add Ɛawed\add* ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu di řexřa, \add jjuǧeɣ\add* ad ten bezzɛeɣ jar řegnus u ad ten zuzzareɣ di temmura,  
\v 24 minzi war gguren di lfarayiḍ inu, \add maca\add* nḍaren tiweṣṣa inu u ssɛiǧten ussan inu n ssebt, u \add minzi\add* tiṭṭawin nsen ḍeffarent awarni i imeyḍa n l’aṣnam n řejdud nsen.  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* Necc wciɣ asen tiweṣṣa war iḥřin d lfarayiḍ i zi war zemmaren nitni ad ddaren.  
\v 26 Necc ssxemjeɣ ten s tewhibin nsen umi nitni arrin marra min yarezmen řemřawet \add d amezwaru\add* ad yekk timessi, \add ggiɣ tt\add* ḥima ad ten teḥḥiɣ ařami ɣa ssnen aqa Necc d SIDI.”\x ◘ \xo 20:26 \xt Ḥiz. 16:21\x*   
\m
\v 27 “S uya, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, siweř ak-d taddart n Israil, ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Uřa s man aya tuɣa řejdud nwem ttceqqafen dayi umi tuɣa dayi ɣeddaren aṭṭas.  
\v 28 \add Řami\add* ten ssidfeɣ di temmurt tenni x ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu maḥend ad ten tt wceɣ, xezzaren nitni ɣar kuř tawrirt yuɛřan u ɣar wezɣar imcubbcen uca iwyen din tiɣarṣa nsen u qeddmen din tiwhibin nsen \add i d ayi\add* sɛarent, u qqedmen din arriḥet nsen ittfuḥen u seyyben din tiwhibin nsen n useyyeb.  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ asen: ‘Man řgeɛɛdet nni ɣar ɣa traḥem? Isem nnes ‘Bamah’, \add ixs ad yini ‘Řgeɛɛdet’\add*, ař ass-a.’”   
\m
\v 30 “S uya, ini i taddart n Israil: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Ma \add war\add* tessxemmijem kenniw ixef nwem x simant n webrid n řejdud nwem u \add war\add* tessefsidem uřa d kenniw ixef nwem am tḍeffaram nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam?  
\v 31 Am tessgeɛɛadem tiwhibin nwem, tessekkam iḥenjiren nwem x tmessi u tessxemmajem ixef nwem s imeyḍa nwem n l’aṣnam ař ass-a? Ma Necc \add xenni\add* ad kenniw jjeɣ ad ayi tesseqsam, \add a\add* taddart n Israil? S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, Necc war ttijjiɣ kenniw ad ayi tesseqsam!  
\v 32 Min dd-igeɛɛden di buḥbeř nwem, war ittiři, min teqqarem kenniw: Neccin ad niři am řegnus u am řaǧat n temmura umi ɣa neɛbed \add ṣṣanam\add* n ukeccuḍ d weẓru.  
\v 33 S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Necc ad xawem ṣellṭeɣ s ufus ijehden u s uɣiř isswiẓẓḍen u s ufarreɣ n wesɛar \add inu\add*!  
\v 34 Maɣar Necc ad kenniw ssuffɣeɣ zi řegnus uca ad kenniw ssmuneɣ zi temmura mani di tᵉttwabezzɛem kenniw, s ufus ijehden d uɣiř isswiẓẓaḍen u s ufarreɣ n wesɛar \add inu\add*.  
\v 35 Ad kenniw awyeɣ ɣar řexřa n řegnus, uca din ad kenniw carrɛeɣ, udem d udem.  
\v 36 Am mammec ḥekmeɣ x řejdud nwem di řexřa n temmurt n Miṣra, ammu i xawem ɣa ḥekmeɣ, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 37 Ad kenniw ssekkeɣ sadu uzeǧad \add n umeksaw\add* uca ad kenniw ssidfeɣ di ttarbiyyet n Řɛahd. \x ◘ \xo 20:37 \xt Ḥiz. 34\x*  
\v 38 Necc ad zzaywem zuzzareɣ̮ imɣewwaɣen d yinni xafi ittɛeddan. Necc ad ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n řɣubbiyet nsen mani zeddɣen am yibarraniyyen, \add maca\add* war dd-ttikkwiḍen ca ɣar temmurt n Israil. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 39 “Uca kenniw, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, ejj kuř ijj ad yuyur ɣar imeyḍa nnes n l’aṣnam. \add Maca\add* awarni as ad ɣari tesřem s tidett. \add Xenni\add* war tᵉssexsaram ɛad Isem inu s tewhibin nwem d imeyḍa nwem n l’aṣnam.  
\v 40 Minzi x wedrar inu iqeddsen, x wedrar yuɛřan n Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, din ad ayi tsexxar qaɛ taddart n Israil, marra nitni. Din ad xasen arḍiɣ uca din ad ttareɣ tiwhibin nwem n usgeɛɛed uřa d tmenzut n min ɣa tessgeɛɛdem zi marra tiwhibin nwem iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 20:40 \xt Ḥiz. 40:2; Ḥiz. 43:12\x*  
\v 41 Necc ad xawem arḍiɣ zi ssibbet n arriḥet ittfuḥen xmi kenniw ɣa ssuffɣeɣ zi řegnus u ad kenniw ssmuneɣ zi temmura mani kenniw zuzzareɣ uca ad ttwaqeddseɣ zzaywem zzat i-t tiṭṭawin n řegnus  
\v 42 uca ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, řami kenniw dd-iwyeɣ ɛawed ɣar temmurt n Israil, ɣar temmurt x tenni umi sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu, \add jjuǧeɣ\add* ad tt wceɣ i řejdud nwem.  
\v 43 Din ad tidarem ibriden nwem d marra timegga nwem nni zi tessxemjen ixef nwem uca kenniw ad tcarhem ixef nwem zi ssibbet n marra timegga nwem iɛeffnen i teggim.  
\v 44 Kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, řami ggiɣ akidwem di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu \add uca\add* war iǧi ɛlaḥsab ibriden nwem iɛeffnen, \add u war iǧi\add* ɛlaḥsab timegga nwem iɣeccen, \add a\add* taddart n Israil!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Řḥukm x temmurt n ljanub  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, egg udem nnec ɣar ljanub, ejj \add awařen nnec\add* ad udumen jjihet n ljanub uca nabb ḍidd i wezɣar n yeyyar di \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub. \f ◼ \fr 21:2 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  
\v 3 Ini i wezɣar n \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub: ‘Seř i wawař n SIDI: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad ssarɣeɣ dayem ict n tmessi, tenni i ɣa iccen kuř tacejjart tazizawt u kuř tacejjart yuẓɣen. Aceɛɛař n řɛabuq war ittwaxessi u s uya ad ttwacemḍen marra iɣembab zi ljanub ař ccamal \x ◘ \xo 21:3 \xt Lk. 23:31\x*  
\v 4 uca marra iwdan d řmař ad ẓaren aqa Necc, SIDI, d wenni issarɣen \add timessi\add*. War tᵉttwaxessi ca.’ \f ◼ \fr 21:4 \ft \+fk marra iwdan d řmař\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘marra aysum’.\f*  
\v 5 Nniɣ necc: ‘A, Sidi inu, SIDI, ɛad nitni qqaren xafi: ‘Ma war issiweř netta s tḥuja n twafit \add waha\add*?’!”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řḥukm n SIDI x Urcalim  
\m
\v 6 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 7 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, egg udem nnec ɣar Urcalim, ejj \add awařen nnec\add* ad udumen ḍidd i tzawiyyin Iqeddsen uca nabb ḍidd i temmurt n Israil.  
\v 8 Ini i temmurt n Israil: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, aqa ɣarem, Necc ad dd-jebdeɣ ssif inu zeg ufurru n weɣřaf nnes uca ad qeḍɛeɣ am umsegged am uɛeffan.  
\v 9 Minzi ad qeḍɛeɣ am umsegged am uɛeffan zi řwesṭ nnem, s uya ad dd-iffeɣ ssif inu zeg ufurru n weɣřaf nnes, ḍidd i marra \add inni ɣarsen arrimet n\add* weysum, zi ljanub ař ccamal,  
\v 10 uca marra \add inni ɣarsen arrimet n\add* weysum ad ssnen, belli Necc, SIDI, jebdeɣ ssif inu zeg ufurru n weɣřaf. Ɛemmarṣ war \add ɣares\add* dd-iddikkwiř.’”   
\m
\v 11 “\add Maca\add* cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, sɣunfa, sɣunfa zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen s tejɛinnatin ttwarẓent d tarzugi.  
\v 12 Ad imsar xmi d ac i ɣa inin: ‘Maɣar tessɣunfid \add ammu\add*?’, aqa cek ad tinid: ‘Zi ssibbet n min sřiɣ, maɣar ad dd-yas uca kuř uř ad ifsi u marra ifassen ad heyyfen u marra buḥbeř ad yarxu u marra ifadden ad ardben am waman. Xzar, ad dd-yas uca ad yiři, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 21:12 \xt Irm. 6:24; 49:23; Ḥiz. 4:17; 7:17\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 14 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, nabb uca ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI!’ Uca ini:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Ssif, ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ittwasseqḍeɛ u ittwassuyda.\qt*   
\m
\v 15 \qt Ittwasseqḍeɛ maḥend ad iɣarṣ tiɣarṣa,\qt*  
\m \qt ittwassuyda maḥend ad ilellec.’\qt*  
\b  
\m \qt Niɣ ittxeṣṣa i neccin ad nfarreḥ, \+tl ad nini:\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Azeǧaḍ \+tl n řeḥkamet\+tl* n mmi\qt*  
\m \qt isseḥqar kuř akeccuḍ \+tl nneɣni\+tl*?’\qt* \f ◼ \fr 21:15 \ft \+fk Azeǧaḍ\ft  - aqa-t d azeǧaḍ (n ṣṣulṭa) n Yahuda (xzar Amz. 49:10). Deg Amz. 49:10 nettaf aqa azeǧaḍ-a war dd-ittwakkes zi Yahuda. Řexxu Ḥizqiyal, umi řgens issen aqa ixs ad iṭṭef di lwaɛd-a, isseqsa ‘Ma ad teqqim ṣṣulṭa n Yahuda am mammec d as ittɣiř i řgens x dsas n lwaɛd niɣ lla? Minzi nitni qqaren s yixef nsen ‘azeǧaḍ n mmi isseḥqar kuř akeccuḍ (nneɣni)’, ixs ad yini lwaɛd ad iqqim uca ajeǧid n Babil (‘ssif’) war d aneɣ izemmar. Xenni yarra-dd SIDI belli řgens n Yahuda ad ittwařqef s ssif n ujeǧid n Babil u Netta ad ten issuffeɣ di tmeḥbast ɣar Babil, maca lwaɛd i Yahuda di Amz. 49:10 ad iqqim uca ad ittwakemmeř di Lmasiḥ wenni dd i ɣa ittwaxeřqen awarni ɛřayen 500 n iseggʷusa di Bayt-Laḥm, tandint n Yahuda, zi Arruḥ Iqeddsen, zeg uɛeddis n Maryam, tenni tuɣa ittwaxḍben i Yusuf. Yusuf d Maryam tuɣa-ten s tnayen idsen zi twacunt n Dawud, zeg ict n twacunt igellden, waxxa Udayen war ɣarsen ajeǧid zeg yixef nsen di řweqt nni maɣar Hirudus zi Idum tuɣa d ajeǧid x řumur n Irumaniyyen. \fk mmi\ft  - aqa-t d Yahuda (xzar Amz. 49:9)\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 \qt ‘Immewc maḥend ad ittwassuyda,\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad t ṭṭfen deg ufus.\qt*  
\m \qt Ssif ittwaqḍeɛ u ittwassuyda,\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad ittwagg deg ufus n uqettař.\qt*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Sɣuyy uca trud, \+tl a\+tl* mmis n bnadem,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar ad yiři x řgens inu,\qt*  
\m \qt ad yiři x marra řḥukkam n Israil.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa mmewcen i ssif \+tl munen\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d řgens inu.\qt*  
\m \qt S uya, wwet x tmeṣṣaḍt nnec.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:17 \xt Ḥiz. 6:11; 7:27\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 \qt ‘Wah, \+tl ssif\+tl* ittwaqeǧeb.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Maca\+tl* mana, mařa azeǧaḍ\qt*  
\m \qt nni isseḥqaren \+tl marra akeccuḍ\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt war dd-ittiři \+tl ɛad\+tl*?’\qt*,  
\m \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.\x ◘ \xo 21:18 \xt Ica. 1:5; Irm. 6:28-30\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 \qt ‘Cek, \+tl a\+tl* mmis n bnadem, nabb,\qt*  
\m \qt uca wwet ifassen ijj deg wenneɣni,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar ssif ad iwwet tnayen,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl wah\+tl*, třata n imuren.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa-t d ssif n yinni ittwanɣen,\qt*  
\m \qt ssif n umeqqran nni ittwaneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt ssif nni ɣarsen ittadfen,\qt*   
\m
\v 20 \qt ḥima \+tl xenni\+tl* uř ad ifsi\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad mmarenyent tɛenkrifin.\qt*  
\m \qt Řeqḍeɛ n ssif ggiɣ t\qt*  
\m \qt x marra tiwwura nsen.\qt*  
\m \qt Ay, aqa \+tl ssif\+tl* iwjed maḥend ad ilellec,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ittwajebb-dd zeg ufurru n weɣřaf\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad iɣarṣ.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:20 \xt Ḥiz. 21:32\x*   
\m
\v 21 \qt Smun jjehd nnec, qess ɣar ufusi,\qt*  
\m \qt bedd, qess ɣar uzeřmaḍ,\qt*  
\m \qt arr řeqḍeɛ nnec mani ma texsed.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 22 \qt ‘Uřa d Necc ad wteɣ ifassen inu\qt*  
\m \qt ijj deg wenneɣni\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ssareyyḥeɣ asɛar inu.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc, SIDI, aqa ssiwřeɣ.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 24 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, egg tnayen n ibriden zi mani dd ɣa yas ssif n ujeǧid n Babil. Zeg ict n temmurt ad ffɣen nitni s tnayen idsen. Nqec ijj n uciyyar ɣar \add u\add*beṭṭu n webrid, nqec \add i-t\add* ɣar \add u\add*beṭṭu n webrid ɣar tendint.  
\v 25 Ad tneyyced abrid s manis dd ɣa yas ssif ɣar Rabba n ayt n Ɛammun u ɣar Yahuda ař daxeř di tendint ittwassjehden: Urcalim.  
\v 26 Minzi ajeǧid n Babil ad ibedd ɣar mani farqen ibriden, ɣar \add u\add*beddu n tnayen n ibriden nni maḥend ad iɛezzem. Ad izzerz fřitcat n řqewṣ, ad isseqsa řexyařat n l’aṣnam, ad ixzar tsa.  
\v 27 Deg ufus nnes ufusi yusa-dd wectab n ‘Urcalim!’, maḥend ad \add din\add* yegg řeqcuɛ n wedham, maḥend ad yarzem aqemmum \add nnes\add* s iɣuyyan n wenɣi, maḥend ad issgeɛɛed tmijja \add nnes\add* s iɣuyyan \add n umenɣi\add*, maḥend ad igg řeqcuɛ n wedham ḍidd i tewwura, maḥend ad yegg acbar, maḥend ad igg lbarajat. \x ◘ \xo 21:27 \xt Ḥiz. 4:2; 17:17\x*  
\v 28 Maca man aya ad ɣarsen yiři am ugezzen iɣeccen di tiṭṭawin nsen, \add maɣar nitni\add* aqa ɣarsen tijaǧatin imetnen, \add maca\add* Netta ad isseɛqeř x řmuɛṣiyyet nsen, maḥend ad ttwaṭṭfen \add nitni\add*.”   
\m
\v 29 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu SIDI: ‘Minzi tesseɛqiřem x řmuɛṣiyyet nwem umi iɛeddiyen nwem ttbanen nican, xmi ttwaẓarren ddnub nwem s marra min tᵉtteggem, \add wah,\add* minzi tsseɛqiřem \add x řmuɛṣiyyet nwem\add*, \add s uya\add* ad kenniw ṭṭfen s ufus.’  
\v 30 U cek, aɛeffan iyezzmen i řmewt, \add cek,\add* \add a\add* řḥakem n Israil, wenni ass nnes ad dd-yas di řweqt n řeḥsab aneggaru n řmuɛṣiyyet,  
\v 31 ammu i \add d ac\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Kkes areẓẓet nni, kkes ttaj nni. \add Ammu\add* war ittiři ɛad. Min issehwan, ad ittwassuɛřa, u min issuɛřan, ad dd-ittwassehwa.  
\v 32 Ad arreɣ aya d řxarbet, d řxarbet, \add wah,\add* ad t arreɣ d řxarbet. \add Maca\add* \add marra\add* aya war ittɣimi ɛad, \add mɣir\add* ař dd ɣa yas wenni ɣar iǧan řḥeqq uca Necc ad as t wceɣ.’” \x ◘ \xo 21:32 \xt Amz. 49:10\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řḥukm n SIDI x Iɛammuniyyen  
\m
\v 33 “U cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, nabb uca ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, x ayt n Ɛammun u x useḥqar nsen!’ Ini:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Ssif, ssif ittwajebd-dd,\qt*  
\m \qt ittwassuyda maḥend ad yecc,\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad ilellec, ...\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 34 - waxxa nitni ttwařan i cek ijj n řewḥiy war iǧin, waxxa nitni ttgezznen i cek ijj n ugezzen issxarriqen -  
\b  
\m \qt \+tl ... aqa ssif ittwajebd-dd\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad cek yarr\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar irawen n iɛeffanen ittwassnuqqben\qt*  
\m \qt nni zi dd-yusa wass nsen\qt*  
\m \qt di řweqt n řeḥsab aneggaru n řmuɛṣiyyet.\qt*   
\m
\v 35 \qt Arr \+tl ssif\+tl* ɣar ufurru n weɣřaf nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Deg wemcan mani dd-tᵉttwaxeřqed,\qt*  
\m \qt di temmurt n ř’aṣeř nnec\qt*  
\m \qt ad cek ḥekmeɣ.\qt*   
\m
\v 36 \qt Ad xak zeǧɛeɣ wesxeḍ inu.\qt*  
\m \qt S tmessi n uduqqez inu \+tl n ufugem\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ad xak suḍeɣ uca ad cek ggeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt deg ufus n ayt n bu-ɣezzu\qt*  
\m \qt nni issnen ad deǧen.\qt*   
\m
\v 37 \qt Ad tiřid d macca i tmessi,\qt*  
\m \qt idammen nnec ad ten ssizzřen\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n temmurt.\qt*  
\m \qt War tᵉttiři qaɛ řidaret dayek,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Necc, SIDI, aqa ssiwřeɣ.’”\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\s1 Ddnub n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ma texsed ad tḥekmed, ma texsed ad tḥekmed x \bd Tendint n idammen\bd*? Scen as \add xenni\add* jjɛayef nnes, \x ◘ \xo 22:2 \xt Ḥiz. 20:4; 23:36\x*  
\v 3 ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: \add Cem\add*, \add a\add* tandint, tenni issizzřen \bd idammen\bd* di řwesṭ nnes, ařami dd-tiweḍ řweqt nnes, \add a\add* tandint, tenni iggin imeyḍa n l’aṣnam x yixef nnes maḥend ad zzaysen tessexmej ixef nnes!  
\v 4 S \bd idammen\bd* nni tessizzřed, tdewřed s umarwas u s imeyḍa nnem n l’aṣnam nni teggid, aqa tessxemjed ixef nnem, tessiwḍed ussan nnem uca trehhged ař iseggʷusa nnem. X uya wciɣ cem i řegnus i useḥqar u i temmura i ustehzi. \x ◘ \xo 22:4 \xt 2 Ij. 21:16; Ḥiz. 5:14; 20:30,31 \x*  
\v 5 Inni yudsen d yinni iggʷejen ad zzayem stehzan: \add ’Cem, a\add* tamexmujt n yisem, \add cem, tenni\add* iccuren s uṣeddeɛ!  
\v 6 Xzar, řḥukkam n Israil tuɣa aten dayem, kuř ijj x řeḥsab jjehd nnes, maḥend ad sizzřen \bd idammen\bd*.  
\v 7 Sseḥqaren babatsen d yemmatsen dayem, ggin s uɣiř ak-d ubarrani di řwesṭ nnem, ḥṣaren ayujiř d tajjač i dayem.  
\v 8 Min iǧan iqeddsen i Necc, aqa tesseḥqared t, uca ussan n ssebt inu tessɛiǧted i-ten.  
\v 9 Imceqqafen tuɣa aten dayem maḥend ad ssizřen \bd idammen\bd*. Nitni qqimen ccin x idurar nni \add dinni\add* ɣarem, aqa ggin řefḍiḥet di řwesṭ nnem. \x ◘ \xo 22:9 \xt Ḥiz. 18:6, 11\x*  
\v 10 Nitni ssɛarran řɛar n babam nni din ɣarem, u tenni tuɣa texmej umi xas idammen, aqa ɣeṣben tt dayem. \x ◘ \xo 22:10 \xt Lawi 18:8, 19; Ḥiz. 18:6\x*  
\v 11 Ijjen igga nnɛi ak-d tmeṭṭut n wajjar nnes, uca ijjen nneɣni issexmej tamɣart n mmis, \add ittegg\add* řefḍiḥet \add akides\add*, uca \add ɛawed\add* ijjen nneɣni iɣṣeb učmas, yeǧis n babas, \add din\add* ɣarem.\x ◘ \xo 22:11 \xt Lawi 18:15, 20; Irm. 5:8\x*  
\v 12 Aqa ṭṭfen din ɣarem arrecwet, maḥend ad ssizzřen \bd idammen\bd*, teksid arriba d arbeḥ uca tbeɛɛjed ajjar nnec s uɣiř, maca tᵉttud ayi!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\m
\v 13 “Xzar, wtiɣ ifassen inu ijj deg wenneɣni zi ssibbet n ubeɛɛej i teggid u zi ssibbet n \bd idammen\bd* nni issizzřen di řwesṭ nnem. \f ◼ \fr 22:13 \ft \+fk ubeɛɛej ... idammen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ubeɛɛej nnem ... idammen nnem’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 22:13 \xt Ḥiz. 21:22\x*  
\v 14 Ma ad iqqim uř nnem imten? Ma ad iřin ifassen nnem jehden deg wussan nni di ɣa ggeɣ \add min iǧan\add* ḍidd nnem. Necc, SIDI, aqa ssiwřeɣ uca ad t ggeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 22:14 \xt Ḥiz. 17:24\x*  
\v 15 Ad cem zuzzareɣ jar řegnus, ad cem bezzɛeɣ x temmura, u ad kemmřeɣ taxmuji nnem qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 22:15 \xt Ḥiz. 12:14, 15\x*  
\v 16 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa tᵉttwassɛiǧted zeg yixef nnem zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus u cem ad tessned belli Necc d SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 18 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, inni n taddart n Israil dewřen ayi am kuffu. Marra nitni dewřen d nnḥas d istanyu d wuzzař d řexfif di řwesṭ n tefqunt, aqa aten dewřen kuffu n nnuqart.” \x ◘ \xo 22:18 \xt Ica. 1:22\x*   
\m
\v 19 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, minzi marra kenniw tdewřem am kuffu, s uya, xzar, Necc ad kenniw ssmuneɣ di Urcalim.  
\v 20 Axmi yarwen nnḥas d istanyu d wuzzař d řexfif di tefqunt, ḥima ad xasen ceɛɛřen timessi maḥend ad ssfesyen man aya \add marra\add*, ammu i \add kenniw\add* ɣa ssmuneɣ deg weɣḍab inu u deg wesɛar inu. Ad kenniw ssarseɣ dinni uca ad kenniw ssfesyeɣ.  
\v 21 Necc ad kenniw ssmuneɣ uca ad xawem suḍeɣ s tmessi n uduqqez inu \add n ufugem\add* ařami kenniw ad tᵉttwafesyem di řwesṭ nnes.  
\v 22 Axmi ssfesyen nnuqart di tefqunt, ammu i ɣa tᵉttwassfesyem kenniw dayes uca ad tessnem aqa Necc, SIDI, ssfarɣeɣ xawem asɛar inu.”   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 24 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ini i \add temmurt\add*: ‘Cem d ict n temmurt i war ittwassizdigen, \add ict n temmurt\add* i war ittwasuffen s wenẓar ijehden deg wass n wesxeḍ.  
\v 25 Aqa din ict n tmeɛmuč n inabiyyen \add nnes\add* di řwesṭ nnes. Am weyrad izehharen isarḍ taymart nnes, \add ammu i\add* ccin nitni řeɛmur. Kksen \add min iǧan d\add* taxabect d min iɣřan. Nitni arnin tijjař nnes di řwesṭ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 22:25 \xt Mt. 23:14\x*  
\v 26 Ikehhanen nsen ssɛiǧiten Ccariɛa inu uca ssxemmajen timesřayin inu iqeddsen. Nitni war farrzen ca jar min iqeddsen d min ittwassɛiǧten, war sscanan ca lfarq jar min ixemjen d min izdigen uca ttbellaɛen uřa d tiṭṭawin nsen i wussan inu n ssebt uca \add ammu\add* ttwassɛiǧiteɣ di řwesṭ nsen. \x ◘ \xo 22:26 \xt Lawi 10:10; Ḥiz. 44:23\x*  
\v 27 Řḥukkam nnes di řwesṭ nnes ggin am wuccanen nni icarrgen taymart maḥend ad ssizzřen \bd idammen\bd* u maḥend ad areddǧen řeɛmur, ḥima ad ṭṭfen arbeḥ war iḥřin. \x ◘ \xo 22:27 \xt Mixa 3:11; Ṣaf. 3:3\x*  
\v 28 Inabiyyen nnes dřin ten s jjiř yuẓɣen. Nitni ttwařan iweḥḥan war iǧin uca ssawařen ɣarsen s tgezzant issxarriqen. Nitni qqaren: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI!, \add am\add* SIDI tuɣa war ini walu. \x ◘ \xo 22:28 \xt Ḥiz. 13:7, 9, 10; 21:29, 22:12\x*  
\v 29 Řgens n temmurt igga bezzez \add x iwdan\add* s řexcunet, keccḍen takeccaḍt, ḥeṣṣaren řmeskin d umezřuḍ, uca deǧen abarrani břa ma \add ɣarsen yiři\add* řḥeqq.  
\v 30 Arzuɣ jar asen ijj n weryaz nni i ɣa issbedden ijj n řḥiḍ uca ad ibedd di tazzit di ṭṭweɛ n temmurt ařami war tt ttaredǧeɣ, maca war t ufiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 22:30 \xt Izhd. 106:23\x*  
\v 31 \add Xas uca\add* ssfarɣeɣ xasen asxeḍ inu. S tmessi n uduqqez inu \add n ufugem\add* qḍiɣ xasen, abrid nsen arriɣ t x uzeǧif nsen!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 22:31 \xt Ḥiz. 9:10; 11:21; 16:43\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 23
\s1 Uhula d Uhuliba  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, tuɣa \add din\add* tnayen n temɣarin, yessis n ict n temɣart.  
\v 3 Nitenti ssfesdent ixef nsen di Miṣra, di temẓi nsent ssfesdent ixef nsent. Din tuɣa ɛebzent deg idmaren nsent uca din ḥadan ibbac nsent iɛuzryen. \x ◘ \xo 23:3 \xt Ḥiz. 20:8\x*  
\v 4 Ismawen nsent tuɣa Uhula, tameqqrant nsent, d učmas Uhuliba. Nitenti dewřent inu uca urwent iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin. Ina d ismawen nsent: Samarya d Uhula, u Urcalim d Uhuliba.  
\v 5 Uhula tessefsed ixef nnes ɣari u teɛceq inni tt ittexsen, ayt n Accur, jjiran \add nnes\add*,  
\v 6 \add iryazen\add* nni arḍen arruḍ adeḥmi, lwulat d imḍebbaren, marra iḥudriyyen icennɛen, imnayen nni yenyin s uyis.  
\v 7 S farq-ccɣeř nnes tewca ixef nnes i nitni, ɣar řemxeyyar n ayt n Accur, ɣar marra nitni uca nettat tᵉttwassexmej s marra wi tᵉttexs, s marra imeyḍa nsen n ṣṣanam.  
\v 8 Nettat war tejji farq-ccɣeř nnes ak-d Imiṣriyyen, minzi di temẓi nnes ṭṭsen akides uca ḥadan ibbac nnes iɛuzryen uca ssfarrɣen xas farq-ccɣeř nsen.”   
\m
\v 9 “S uya wciɣ tt deg ufus n yinni tuɣa tt ittexsen, deg ufus n ayt n Accur i tuɣa teɛceq. \x ◘ \xo 23:9 \xt 2 Ij. 17; 18\x*  
\v 10 Nitni ssɛarran řɛar nnes uca kksen iḥenjiren nnes d tḥenjirin nnes uca nɣin tt s ssif. Tedweř as ijj n yisem war icniɛ jar temɣarin uca nitni ssiwḍen xas řeḥkamat.”   
\m
\v 11 “\add Umi\add* teẓra man aya učmas, Uhuliba, aqa tarni ɛad deg weɛceq nnes uca tarni uřa di farq-ccɣeř nnes ktar x farq-ccɣeř n učmas.  
\v 12 Nettat teɛceq ayt n Accur, lwulat d imḍebbaren, jjiran nni yarḍen arruḍ d lemliḥ qaɛ, imnayen nni yenyin x yeysan, marra iḥudriyyen icennɛen. \x ◘ \xo 23:12 \xt 2 Ij. 16:7\x*  
\v 13 Ẓriɣ aqa nettat tessexmej ixef nnes. Nitenti s tnayen idsent uyurent abrid d ijjen.  
\v 14 \add maca\add* nettat tarni \add ɛad\add* di farq-ccɣeř nnes. \add Umi\add* teẓra iryazen, ḥenncen ten x řḥiḍ, tṣawar n yeryazen, arcamen di tintat tizeggʷaɣin,  
\v 15 beysen s webyas ɣar tejɛinnatin nsen, s ireẓẓat s tintat ifarqen x izeǧifen nsen, marra ɣarsen ccuf am yineɣrafen \add n řɛeskar\add*, arewsen di ayt n Babil, \add iryazen\add* zi \add temmurt n\add* Ikaldaniyyen, tammurt mani xeřqen.  
\v 16 Ammu i tedweř nettat tᵉttexs i-ten umi tiṭṭawin nnes ẓrint \add ten\add* uca nettat tessekk ɣarsen ireqqasen, ɣar \add temmurt n\add* Ikaldaniyyen.  
\v 17 Usin-dd ɣares ayt n Babil maḥend ad ṭṭṣen akides di qama n tmexsa uca ssxemjen tt s farq-ccɣeř nsen uca nettat tessexmej ixef nnes zzaysen. \add Xenni\add* iggʷej xasen řeɛmar nnes.  
\v 18 Tessefsed nettat ixef nnes s bṭayṭay uca tessɛarra řɛar nnes. \add Xenni\add* iggʷej xas řeɛmar inu am mammec tuɣa iggʷej řeɛmar inu uřa x učmas.  
\v 19 Tessefsed ixef nnes aṭṭas umi teɛqeř x wussan n temẓi nnes řami tuɣa tessefsed ixef nnes di temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 20 Nettat teɛceq inni tt ittexsen, inni aysum nsen am weysum n iɣyař u inni adɛaq nsen am wedɛaq n iysan.  
\v 21 Aqa teɛqeb-dd ɣar řefḍihet n temẓi nnem, ařami Imiṣriyyen ḥadan idmaren nnem n temẓi.”   
\m
\v 22 “S uya, Uhuliba, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad xam ssekkareɣ inni cem ittexsen i x tuɣa iggʷej řeɛmar nnem uca ad ggeɣ ad xam dd-asen zeg wenneḍ nnem:  
\v 23 tarwa n Babil d marra Ikaldaniyyen, imeḥḍayen d imcennɛen d tarwa n taṣiřet u marra ayt n Accur akidsen, iḥudriyyen ijebbden meẓri, lwulat, marra nitni d imḍebbaren, ineɣrafen \add n řɛeskar\add* d yeryazen s yisem, aqa marra nitni d imnayen inni yenyin x yeysan.  
\v 24 Nitni ad xam dd-usin s ikarruten i umenɣi ak-d tjarrarin iqarqben u s ijj n wegraw n řegnus, s tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* timeqqranin d tseddariyin timeẓyanin, uřa s lkask x uzeǧif. Nitni ad ssbedden ixef nsen deg wenneḍ nnem u Necc ad asen wceɣ ddeɛwet u nitni ad cem ḥekmen ɛlaḥsab ccariɛa nsen.  
\v 25 Necc ad ggeɣ tusmi inu \add iqeddsen\add* ḍidd i cem uca nitni ad zzayem ggen s wesɛar. Nitni ad qqsen tinzarin nnem d tiṭṭawin nnem uca min zzayem iqqimen ad iwḍa s ssif. Nitni ad kksen iḥenjiren nnem d yessim nnem uca min iqqimen ad ittwacc s tmessi.  
\v 26 Ad kksen arruḍ nnem uca ad kksen řehzuṭ nnem. \x ◘ \xo 23:26 \xt Ḥiz. 16:39\x*  
\v 27 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ssbeddeɣ řefḍiḥet nnem uřa d farq-ccɣeř nnem zi temmurt n Miṣra uca war ɣarsen tessgiɛɛded ɛad tiṭṭawin nnem u war tidared ɛad Miṣra.’  
\v 28 Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad cem ggeɣ deg ufus n yinni cem icarrhen, deg ufus n yinni i x tuɣa iggʷej řeɛmar nnem. \x ◘ \xo 23:28 \xt Ḥiz. 16:37, Ḥiz. 23:17\x*  
\v 29 Ad zzayem ggen am wecrah nsen u ad kksen marra i umi tarbred uca ad cem jjen awarni asen tᵉttwaɛarrid d tuɛaryant ařami ittwaɛarra řɛar n farq-ccɣeř nnem uřa d řefḍihet nnem d farq-ccɣeř nnem. \x ◘ \xo 23:29 \xt Ḥiz. 16:39, Ḥiz. 23:25, 26\x*  
\v 30 Ad zzayem ggen aya minzi teḍfared řegnus am iggur bnadem awarni i temɣart n farq-ccɣeř u minzi tessxemjed ixef nnem s imeyḍa n ṣṣanam nsen.  
\v 31 Tuyured deg webrid n učmam, uca ad am wceɣ řkas nnes deg ufus nnem.’”   
\m
\v 32 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Ad teswed řkas n učmam\qt*  
\m \qt wenni yuǧɣen u iwesɛen,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami řqedd nnes ad yarr \+tl řɛedyan\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ad \+tl zzayem\+tl* dehcen s řḥegra\qt*  
\m \qt u ad \+tl zzayem\+tl* stehzan.\qt*   
\m
\v 33 \qt Ad teccured s wescar d wecḍan.\qt*  
\m \qt Řkas n učmam Samarya d ijj n řkas\qt*  
\m \qt n unexřiɛ d wareddeǧ.\qt*   
\m
\v 34 \qt Ad t teswed uca ad t tẓemmed,\qt*  
\m \qt ad tɣezzed cquf nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tqebced \+tl zzayes\+tl* idmaren nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi Necc nniɣ \+tl t\+tl*!’,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu i\+tl* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.\qt*   
\m
\v 35 \qt ‘S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Umi dayi tᵉttud uca temmenḍared ayi\qt*  
\m \qt awarni i weɛrur nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt s uya ittxeṣṣa cem\qt*  
\m \qt ad tarbud s yixef nnem\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d řefḍiḥet nnem d farq-ccɣeř nnem.’”\qt*\x ◘ \xo 23:35 \xt Irm. 2:32; 3:21; 13:25; 18:15; Ḥiz. 22:12\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 36 Inna ayi SIDI: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ma texsed ad tcarrɛed Uhula d Uhuliba? Ini asent \add xenni\add* jjɛayef nsent. \x ◘ \xo 23:36 \xt Ḥiz. 20:4; 22:2\x*  
\v 37 Minzi zennant uca idammen řeṣqen ɣar ifassen nsent u zennant ak-d imeyḍa n l’aṣnam nsent. Sennej i uya arrint iḥenjiren nsent, inni urwent i Necc, ad ẓwan timessi d macca i imeyḍa n l’aṣnam nsent. \x ◘ \xo 23:37 \xt Ḥiz. 16:21; 20:26,31\x*  
\v 38 Marra aya ggint dayi: \bd deg wass nni\bd* ssxemjent nitenti Zzawect inu Iqeddsen uca ssɛiǧtent ussan inu n ssebt. \x ◘ \xo 23:38 \xt Ḥiz. 22:8\x*  
\v 39 Minzi umi ɣarṣen i tarwa nsent i imeyḍa nsent n l’aṣnam, usint-i-dd \bd deg wass nni\bd* simant nnes di Zzawect inu Iqeddsen maḥend ad tt ssɛiǧtent. Xzar, ammu i ggint di řwesṭ n Taddart inu. \x ◘ \xo 23:39 \xt 2 Ij. 21:4-7; Ḥiz. 16:21, Ḥiz. 20:13, 16\x*  
\v 40 Ɛad ssekkent x yeryazen i dd-yusin zi řaggʷaj. Ssekken areqqas ɣarsen, u xzar, usin-dd nitni, inni i x tessirded ixef nnem, i x tkulared tiṭṭawin nnem uca thezṭed s telwizt.  
\v 41 Teqqimed x ijj n řectu yecna, tuɣa zzates ṭṭabřa isswejden i x tessarsed řebxur inu d zzect inu. \x ◘ \xo 23:41 \xt Awřn. 7:17\x*  
\v 42 \add Řami\add* issusem řḥess n řɣaci inhewřen \add nni din\add* ɣares, ttwanedhen iskarjiyyen zi řexřa ɣar yeryazen nni \add iǧan\add* zi řɣaci n iwdan, uca nitni ggin timeqyasin ɣar ifassen nsent uřa d ijj n tajj izewwqen x izeǧifen nsent.  
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ Necc: Aqa aten zennan ak-d ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř dduysaren. Řexxu farq-ccɣeř nnes simant nnes ad issefsed ixef nnes uca nettat \add tuyur akides dayes\add*.  
\v 44 Nitni udfen xas am udfen x ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř. Ammu udfen x Uhula u x Uhuliba, timɣarin nni ittwafeḍḥen.  
\v 45 Iryazen iseggden ad tent ḥekmen ɛlaḥsab řḥeqq n tinni izennan u ɛlaḥsab řḥeqq n tinni issizzařen idammen, minzi nitenti d timɣarin izennan uca idammen řeṣqen ɣar ifassen nsent.” \x ◘ \xo 23:45 \xt Ḥiz. 16:38\x*   
\m
\v 46 “Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Necc ad xasent ssekkareɣ ijj n wegraw uca ad tent arreɣ d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d takeccaḍt.  
\v 47 Agraw n řgens ad tent yarjem uca ad tent qeḍɛen s řesyuf. Iḥenjiren nsent d tḥenjirin nsent ad ten nɣen uca ad sscemḍen tudrin nsent s tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 23:47 \xt Ḥiz. 16:41\x*  
\v 48 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ssbeddeɣ řefḍayeḥ nsent di temmurt ařami ɣa ttwaɛeřment marra timɣarin uca war tteggent ɛad am řefḍayeḥ nsent.  
\v 49 \add Ammu i\add* xakent ɣa ggen řefḍiḥet nkent uca ad tarbunt ddnub n \add weɛbed n\add* imeyḍa nkent n l’aṣnam uca ad tessnent, aqa Necc Sidi d SIDI!’” \x ◘ \xo 23:49 \xt Ḥiz. 16:58. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 24
\s1 Urcalim d ict n marmita dayes ddra  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI \bd deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa, deg uyur wiss ɛecra, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss ɛecra n uyur\bd*, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ari i yixef nnec isem n ass-a, \add isem n\add* ass n yiḍa. Deg wass-a nnit ad iḥṣar ujeǧid n Babil Urcalim.  
\v 3 Siweř ijj n umedya i taddart iɣewwɣen nni, ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\b  
\m \qt Egg ict n teydurt,\qt*  
\m \qt egg i-tt uca kebb dayes aman.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 24:3 \xt Irm. 1:13\x*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Egg dayes tifettutin \+tl n weysum\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt marra tifettutin icnan,\qt*  
\m \qt tameṣṣaḍt d teɣruḍt,\qt*  
\m \qt ɛemmar \+tl i-tt\+tl* s yeɣsan d lemliḥ qaɛ.\qt*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Ksi lemliḥ n wuǧi\qt*  
\m \qt uca arr uřa d akeccuḍ sadu nsen.\qt*  
\m \qt Ejj ad sehden \+tl marra\+tl* mliḥ\qt*  
\m \qt ařami ɛad iɣsan nnes ad dayes ttwanennan.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “S uya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\b  
\m ‘\bdit Uct x tendint n idammen!\bdit*  
\m \qt taydurt i zi řexmej nnes \+tl ɛad\+tl* dayes,\qt*  
\m \qt tenni zi war yekkis řexmej nnes!\qt*  
\m \qt Kkes zzayes tafettut\qt*  
\m \qt awarni i tfettut \+tl nneɣni\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt břa ad xas teggid taqedduḥt.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 24:6 \xt Ḥiz. 22:2\x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Minzi idammen nnes aqa di řwest nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt tessizeř i-ten x ict n teṣḍart taqeccart.\qt*  
\m \qt War ten tessizziř x temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad ten teddiř s ucař.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Ḥima ad ittwassekkar wesɛar,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad yiři wenqam,\qt*  
\m \qt ggiɣ idammen i tessizzeř nettat\qt*  
\m \qt x teṣḍart taqeccart,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima war ddařen \+tl idammen nnes\+tl*.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \bdit ‘Uct x tendint n idammen!\bdit*  
\m \qt Necc s Yixef inu ad ggeɣ aqellij n ukeccuḍ\qt*  
\m \tl i uceɛɛař n tmessi imɣar!\tl* \x ◘ \xo 24:9 \xt Nḥm. 3:1; Ḥab. 2:12\x*   
\m
\v 10 \qt Arni akeccuḍ, ejj timessi ad tareɣ aṭṭas,\qt*  
\m \qt cennef aysum mliḥ\qt*  
\m \qt uca ejj axeǧeḍ n řebẓar\qt*  
\m \qt ad ittexttex mliḥ\qt*  
\m \qt uca ejj iɣsan ad cemḍen.\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Arr xenni taydurt ixwan \+tl ɛawed\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt x řefḥem nnes itteḥduduqen,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad iḥma ad icmeḍ\qt*  
\m \qt ddra nnes n nnḥas\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tefsi zzayes texmuji i dayes iǧan\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl u xenni\+tl* ad ittwaqḍi řexmej.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt \+tl Marra\+tl* amarret aqa-t di baṭeř.\qt*  
\m \qt Řexmej nnes ifeyyḍen war dd-iffiɣ zzayes.\qt*  
\m \qt Arr řexmej nni di tmessi!\qt*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Di texmuji nnem \+add teǧi\+add* řefḍiḥet nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi Necc tuɣa xseɣ ad cem ssizedgeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt uca \+tl xenni\+tl* war tᵉttwassizdiged.\qt*  
\m \qt X uya war tᵉttwassizdiged\qt*  
\m \qt zi řexmej nnem\qt*  
\m \qt ař xam i ɣa ssiwḍeɣ asɛar inu.\qt*   
\m
\v 14 \qt Necc, SIDI, ssiwřeɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad iffeɣ u Necc ad t ggeɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt War semḥeɣ deg imerwusa\qt*  
\m \qt u war zziǧzeɣ u war ndimeɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad xam ḥekmen\qt*  
\m \qt ibriden nnem d tmegga nnem!’,\qt*  
\m \tl ammu i\tl* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”\x ◘ \xo 24:14 \xt Ḥiz. 5:11; 23:24\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmewt n temɣart n Ḥizqiyal  
\m
\v 15 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 16 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, xzar, s ict n tecti Necc ad kesseɣ meẓri nnec zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec. War ttᵉttru, war ttejji ad uzzřen imeṭṭawen nnec.  
\v 17 Sɣuyy deg uhedden, war ceṭṭen x umettin. Qqen areẓẓet nnec xak uca egg tisiřa nnec deg iḍaren nnec, u war ttřeḥḥif acřaɣem ɣar uyencic niɣ ad tecced aɣrum nni dd ɣa yawyen iwdan \add i wecḍan\add*.”   
\b  
\m
\v 18 Ɣar tuffut ssiwřeɣ i řgens u ɣar tmeddit temmut tmeṭṭut inu u di twecca ggiɣ am mammec i d ayi ittwaweṣṣa.   
\m
\v 19 Inna ayi řgens: “Ma war texsed ad aneɣ tessecned min ɛnant tmesřayin-a, mayemmi i tegged ammu?”  
\v 20 Necc nniɣ asen: “Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 21 ‘Ini i taddart n Israil: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI! Xzar, Necc ad ssɛiǧteɣ Zzawect inu Iqeddsen \add tenni d\add* aɛuǧi n jjehd nwem d umeẓri n tiṭṭawin nwem d řehzuṭ i řeɛmar nwem, uřa d iḥenjiren nwem d tḥenjirin nwem nni tejjim din ad wḍan s ssif.  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* ad teggem am mammec ggiɣ Necc. War tᵉttřeḥḥifem acřaɣem ɣar uyencic uca aɣrum \add i dd-yiwyen\add* iryazen, war \add t\add* tᵉttettem.  
\v 23 Areẓẓat nwem ad iřint x izeǧifen nwem u sandaliyat nwem deg iḍaren nwem. War tceṭṭnem u war tᵉttrum. Ad tᵉteḥḥam di řmuɛṣiyyet nwem uca ad tweḥweḥem ijjen x wenneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 24:23 \xt Ḥiz. 4:17\x*  
\v 24 Ammu i ɣa yiři Ḥizqiyal d řeɛřamet n řeɛjeb i kenniw. Ad teggem nican am mammec igga netta. Xmi dd ɣa yas ddegga, ad tessnem, belli Necc Sidi, d SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 24:24 \xt Ḥiz. 12:6\x*   
\m
\v 25 “Uca cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ma war ittiři aqa deg wass i zzaysen i ɣa kesseɣ lburj nsen, řefraḥet x telwizt nsen, uřa d meẓri n tiṭṭawin nsen d iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin nsen nni yarebbun nitni deg wuř,  
\v 26 aqa \bd deg wass nni\bd* simant nnes ad ɣarek dd-yas ijjen wenni yarewřen maḥend ad yegg tnayen n imezzuɣen nnec ad sřen \add uya\add*.  
\v 27 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yarzem uqemmum nnec ak-d \add uqemmum\add* n wenni yarewřen uca ad tessiwřed, war tᵉttiřid ɛad d aynaw. Cek ad asen tiřid d řeɛřamet n řeɛjeb uca nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 25
\s1 Awař ḍidd i ayt n Ɛammun  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, arr udem nnec ɣar \bd ayt n Ɛammun\bd* uca nabb xasen. \x ◘ \xo 25:2 \xt Irm. 49:1 \x*  
\v 3 Ini i ayt n Ɛammun: ‘Sřem i wawař n Sidi inu, SIDI! Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Umi tennid ‘Ya, ayuz!’ x Zzawect inu Iqeddsen umi tt ssɛiǧten, u x temmurt n Israil umi tt areddǧen, uřa x taddart n Yahuda řami ten iwyen ɣar lmenfa,  
\v 4 s uya, xzar, Necc ad wceɣ cem \add a, tammurt n Ɛammun\add* d tasɣart i yinni dd-yusin zi ccarq uca nitni ad ggen řemrageḥ nsen dayem uca ad arren tizeddiɣin nsen dayem. Nitni ad ccen řɣiǧet nnem uca ad swen aceffay nnem. \f ◼ \fr 25:4 \ft \+fk dayem\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘di temmurt. \fk řɣiǧet nnem\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘řɣiǧet n temmurt’.\f*  
\v 5 Necc ad ggeɣ Rabba d amcan n arraḥet i iřeɣman uca \add tammurt n\add* ayt n Ɛammun d ddmani n wareyyeḥ i wuǧi uca kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.’  
\v 6 Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Umi tewtid ifassen nnec ijj deg wenneɣni \add s řefraḥet\add*, tedzed s uḍar u tfarḥed s marra nnfaxet nnec di řeɛmar x temmurt n Israil,  
\v 7 s uya, xzar, Necc ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍḍid nnec uca ad cek arreɣ d takeccaḍt i řegnus u ad cek qeḍɛeɣ zi jar řegnus uca ad cek teḥḥiɣ zi temmura. Ad cek areddǧeɣ uca ad tessned aqa Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Awař ḍidd i Mu’ab  
\m
\v 8 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Umi \bd Mu’ab\bd* d Saɛir qqaren: Xzar, taddart n Yahuda \add teǧa\add* am marra řegnus!, \x ◘ \xo 25:8 \xt Irm. 48:1-49:7-22\x*  
\v 9 s uya, xzar, Necc ad arzmeɣ aɣezdis n zzat n Mu’ab, zi tneddam, zi tneddam nnes nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar ṭṭarf qaɛ \add n temmurt nnes\add*, tinni d talwizt n temmurt: Bayt-Yacimut, Baɛl-Maɛun d Qaryatayim.  
\v 10 Necc ad tent wceɣ d tasɣart i ayt n ccarq \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d \add temmurt n\add* ayt n Ɛammun, ḥima war tᵉttiři \add ɛad\add* řidaret deg ayt n Ɛammun jar řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 25:10 \xt Ḥiz. 21:37\x*  
\v 11 Ad ssiwḍeɣ řeḥkamat x Mu’ab u nitni ad ssnen, belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Awař ḍidd i Idum  
\m
\v 12 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Umi \bd Idum\bd* igga s nneqmet waha ḍidd i taddart n Yahuda uca umi idweř daysen řɛib aṭṭas umi zzaysen neqmen,  
\v 13 s uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd i Idum uca ad zzayes qeḍɛeɣ bnadem d řmař uca ad t ggeɣ d řxirbet zi Tayman, uca ad wḍan s ssif ař Dadan.  
\v 14 Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ nneqmet inu x Idum s ufus n řgens inu Israil. U nitni ad ggen ak-d Idum ɛlaḥsab aɣḍab inu u ɛlaḥsab asɛar inu, ad ssnen nneqmet inu!’, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Awař ḍidd i Ifilisṭiniyyen  
\m
\v 15 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Umi \bd Ifilisṭiniyyen\bd* ggin s nneqmet u neqmen s nnfaxet n wuř umi areddǧen nitni zi řeɛdawet ittduman,  
\v 16 s uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI inu, SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd i Ifilisṭiniyyen uca ad qeḍɛeɣ Ikaritiyyen uca ad areddǧeɣ min iqqimen x tma n řebḥar. \f ◼ \fr 25:16 \ft \+fk řebḥar\ft  - niɣ ‘il’.\f*  
\v 17 Nneqmat timeqqranin s leɛqayeb iqesḥen ad daysen ggeɣ u nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, xmi ɣa kemmřeɣ nneqmet inu daysen.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 26
\s1 Awař ḍidd i Ṣur  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss ḥiṭɛac, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* amezwaru n uyur\bd* imsar belli yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, umi tenna \add tendint n\add* Ṣur x Urcalim: ‘Ya ayuz, aqa tᵉttwareẓẓa, tawwart n řegnus tᵉttwarzem ɣari. Ad ɣari yiři \add wagřa\add* aṭṭas, umi nettat tᵉttwareddeǧ \add řexxu\add*!’,  
\v 3 s uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ǧiɣ ḍidd nnec, \add a\add* Ṣur! Ad xam ssekkareɣ aṭṭas n řegnus, am mammex issgeɛɛed řebḥar řemwaj nnes.  
\v 4 Nitni ad areddǧen řehyuḍ n \add tendint n\add* Ṣur uca ad arẓen ṣṣumɛat nnes u Necc ad xas kkseɣ acař nnes uca ad tt arreɣ d taṣḍart taqeccart.  
\v 5 Ad \add din\add* tiři di řwest n řebḥar, maḥend ad xas bezzɛen tiracciwin i tneymart n iseřman, minzi Necc nniɣ \add t\add*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, u nettat ad tiři d takeccaḍt i řegnus.  
\v 6 Yessis nni \add iǧan\add* deg iyyar \add x řbarr\add*, ad ttwanɣent s ssif u nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 7 “Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, zi ccamal ad ssiwḍeɣ Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ajeǧid n ijeǧiden, x Ṣur ak-d iysan d ikarruten, ak-d imnayen u ak-d ijj n wegraw d ijj n řgens ameqqran. \f ◼ \fr 26:7 \ft \+fk ak-d iysan d ikarruten\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ak-d uyis d ukarru’.\f*  
\v 8 Ad ineɣ s ssif yessim nni yeǧan deg iyyar, ad issbedd řqammat ḍidd nnem, ad ibna ijj n wecbar ḍidd nnem u ad issbedd ḍidd nnem ict n tesqift \add ttwaggen tt s\add* tseddariyin timeqqranin.  
\v 9 Netta ad igg icarriyyen n wedham ḍidd i řeḥyuḍ nnem uca ad issḥeyyed ssumɛat nnem s řesyuf nnes.  
\v 10 Ad am ideř řeɛjaj n ubarru n yeysan nnes, s zzhir n imnayen d uqarqeb n tjarrarin d \add ddriz n\add* ikarruten ad arjijen řeḥyuḍ nnem xmi ɣa yadef x tewwura nnem am dd-udfen x ict n tendint tᵉttwahdem.  
\v 11 S icucca n yeysan nnes ad iɛfes x ibriden nnem marra, ad ineɣ řgens nnem s ssif uca ipilaren nnem ijehden \add iqeddsen\add* ad wḍan ɣar temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 26:11 \ft \+fk ipilaren nnem ijehden\ft  - aqa-ten d ipilaren n weɛbed n Baɛal di zzawect n Hirkulis di Ṣur. War ǧin d řexyařat n ṣṣanam maca d ipilaren.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 26:11 \xt Ica. 5:28; Irm. 47:3\x*  
\v 12 Nitni ad acaren agřa nnem ad keccḍen tasebbabt nnem, ad areddǧen řeḥyuḍ nnem, ad ɣeḍřen tudrin nnem iɛizzen. Iẓra nnem d tḥenya n ukeccud nnem d řeɛjaj nnem ad ten mmenḍaren deg waman.  
\v 13 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ssesqareɣ ddriz n iẓřan nnem uca řḥess n řgambriyat nnem war ittwaseř ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 26:13 \xt Ica. 24:7, 8; Irm. 7:34; 16:9\x*  
\v 14 Ad cem arreɣ d taṣḍart taqeccart i wefsar n tracciwin i tneymart n iseřman. Ɛemmarṣ ad tᵉttwabnid \add ɛawed\add*, minzi Necc, SIDI, nniɣ t!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 15 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI i \add tegzirt n\add* Ṣur: ‘Ma war ttarjijint tegzirin s řḥess n uweṭṭu nnem, xmi ssbuɛruren inni ittwayezzmen i řmewt, xmi ɣa temsar ict n tecti ineqqen di řwest nnem?  
\v 16 Marra řḥukkam n řebḥar ad dd-hwan zi řekrasi nsen igellden uca ad ɣeḍřen iḥacen nsen, ad kksen arruḍ nsen iburḍaren s tintat ifarzen. Ad řeḥḥfen s řɛurret, ad qqimen x temmurt uca ad arjijen di kuř řweqt uca ad xam nxeřɛen.  
\v 17 Ad xam ssiřyen ijj n wezři n wecḍan, ad am inin:  
\b  
\m \qt Mammec tᵉttwateḥḥid,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a cem\+tl*, tenni i di zedɣen\qt*  
\m \qt inni \+tl dd-iffɣen\+tl* zi řebḥar,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a cem\+tl* tandint icennɛen,\qt*  
\m \qt tenni ijehden aṭṭas di řebḥar,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl cem,\+tl* \+tl a Ṣur\+tl* d imezdaɣ nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt tenni itteggen arjef jar asen\qt*  
\m \qt di marra inni dayes izedɣen.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 26:17 \ft \+fk inni \+bdit dd-iffɣen\+bdit* zi řebḥar\ft  - imezdaɣ n Ṣur tuɣa arwesen deg imezdaɣ n řebḥar minzi tuɣa tagzirt tgeɛɛed-dd zi řebḥar ak-d imezdaɣ nnes umi ɣares dd-texzared zi řaggʷaj, zi temmurt. \fk tenni itteggen arjef ... \ft  - man aya war ixs ad yini aqa imezdaɣ n Ṣur tuɣa ssiggʷiden ijj zeg wenneɣni, maca, umi ɣarsen ijj n isem icenɛen zi ssibbet n tsebbabt nsen di marra ddunect, aqa arjfen umi ẓrin nitni ccan n tendint nsen, uca uřawen nsen dewřen ccuren s uweqqar ařami tandint tḥewwes i-ten s yisem nnes icenɛen.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 26:17 \xt Asa. 18:9-19\x*   
\m
\v 18 \qt Řexxu ad arjijent tegzirin\qt*  
\m \qt deg wass n uweṭṭu nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl wah\+tl* tigzirin di řebḥar\qt*  
\m \qt ad nnxeřɛent s uneggar nnec.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 “Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xmi Necc ad cem yarreɣ d tandint ittwaredǧen am tneddam nni war izdiɣen, xmi xam i ɣa ssiwḍeɣ \add aman\add* ihewřen uca \add xmi\add* aṭṭas n waman ad cem dřen,  
\v 20 \add xenni\add* ad cem dd-ssehwiɣ ak-d yinni dd-ihwan deg weḥfur \add n wenḍeř\add*, ɣar řgens n řweqt n zic. Ad cek ssarseɣ di řaǧaɣ n temmurt, di řxirbat n řweqt n zic, ɣar inni dd-ihwan deg \add weḥfur n\add* wenḍeř, ḥima war dayem ttiřin imezdaɣ ɛad. \add Maca\add* di temmurt n yinni iddaren ad wceɣ řɛezz.  
\v 21 Ad cem arreɣ d ijj n umedya n warjef uca war tᵉttiřid \add ɛad\add*. Ad xam arzun uca war tᵉttwifid ɛemmarṣ i řebda!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI inu SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 27
\s1 Izři n wecḍan x Ṣur  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, sgeɛɛed ijj n weẓri n wecḍan, x Ṣur.  
\v 3 Ini i Ṣur, \add tandint\add* i din izeddɣen ɣar tewwura n řebḥar, \add tandint\add* nni ittsebbaben ak-d řegnus \add nni izeddɣen\add* di tegzirin aṭṭas:  
\b  
\m ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt \+tl A\+tl* Ṣur, cem teqqared:\qt*  
\m \qt Necc aqa ayi nican deg waẓri!’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 27:3 \xt Ḥiz. 28:12\x*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Iseɣwan \+tl n uyeřzim\+tl* nnem\qt*  
\m \qt aqa aten deg wuř n řebḥur,\qt*  
\m \qt inni cem ibnan\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ggin aẓri nnem nican.\qt*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Marra tiřwiḥin n tfeřwin n tɣarruba nnem\qt*  
\m \qt ggin tent i cem\qt*  
\m \qt di tnayen zi tcejjura n umerzi,\qt*  
\m \qt iwyen ticejjura n tengelt zi Lubnan,\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad am ggen tiḥenya i řbaccat.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 27:5 \ft \+fk amerzi\ft  - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Zi tcejjura n řbeǧuḍ n Bacan\qt*  
\m \qt ggin řemqadef nnem\qt*,  
\m \qt řbankuwat nnem \+tl i iqeddafen\+tl* aqa atent zi řɛaj\qt*  
\m \qt ittwagg deg ukeccud n tengelt,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl iwyen t\+tl* zi tegzirin n ayt n Kittim.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 27:6 \ft \+fk řɛaj\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘accawen n lfil’. \fk Kittim\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘Qubrus’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 27:6 \xt Ica. 2:13\x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Řbacc nnem tuɣa-t s řeqṭen azdad zi Miṣra,\qt*  
\m \qt xeyyḍen t s waṭṭas n tintat.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Řbacc\+tl* tuɣa i cem d taɛeǧant,\qt*  
\m \qt tasqift n uqiḍun nnem tuɣa-tt\qt*  
\m \qt zeg \+tl ufiřu\+tl* udehmani d arjuwani\qt*  
\m \qt zi tegzirin n Ilica.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Imezdaɣ n Ṣidun u n Arwad tuɣa aten\qt*  
\m \qt d iqeddafen nnem.\qt*  
\m \qt Imiɣisen nnem, \+tl a\+tl* Ṣur, nni dayem iǧan,\qt*  
\m \qt tuɣa aten d ineddahen nnem.\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 \qt Iwessura n Jubayl d imiɣisen nnes\qt*  
\m \qt tuɣa aten dayem,\qt*  
\m \qt ɛeddřen \+tl marra\+tl* tizza nnem.\qt*  
\b  
\m Marra tiɣarruba n řebḥar d ibeḥriyyen nsen usin-dd ɣarem ḥima ad kidem sebb\add e\add*ben.   
\m
\v 10 Ayt n Lfurṣ, n Lud u n Fuṭ tuɣa aten di řɛeskar nnem, iryazen iɛeskariyyen. Uyřen dayem taseddart \add nsen\add* d lkask \add nsen\add* uca wcin am řɛezz.   
\m
\v 11 Ayt n Arwad d řɛeskar nnem tuɣa aten x řeḥyuḍ nnem uca Igammadiyyen, \add ayt n bu-teryast nnem\add*, \add bedden\add* x ssumɛat nnem. Tiseddariyyen nsen iqesḥen n useřqi i tuɣa uyřent deg wenneḍ x řeḥyuḍ, arnint deg waẓri nnem aṭṭas.   
\m
\v 12 Tarcis tuɣa tᵉttsebbab akidem i ssibbet n ufeyyeḍ n ɛřam kuř igeřwan. Nitni wcin am nnuqart, uzzař, astanyu d řexfif di ṭṭweɛ \add n sseřɛet\add* nni \add d asen\add* tezzenzed.   
\m
\v 13 Yawan d Tubal d Macix tuɣa aten d isebbaben nnem. Nitni wcin am řeɛmur n iwdan d řeqcuɛ n nnḥas di ṭṭweɛ n sseřɛet nnem.   
\m
\v 14 Zi taddart \add n ijeǧiden\add* n Tujarma wcin am yiysan d imnayen d iserdan di ṭṭweɛ \add n sseřɛet\add* nni \add d asen\add* tezzenzed.   
\m
\v 15 Arraw n Dadan tuɣa aten d isebbaben di ṭṭweɛ nnem. Aṭṭas n tegzirin tuɣa xsent ad ṭṭfent sseřɛet zeg ufus nnem. Tiɣmas timeqqranin n řfiř d ukeccuḍ n webnus arrint am tent-i-dd d arriɣaluten. \f ◼ \fr 27:15 \ft \+fk akeccuḍ n webnus\ft  - ict n marka n ukeccuḍ d tabarcant nni iweznen ktar zeg waman ařami ad dd-ihwa ukeccuḍ n ‘ibnus’ umi ittwammenḍar deg waman.\f*   
\m
\v 16 Aram tuɣa ittsebbab akidem x waṭṭas n řeqcuɛ i tṣennɛed. Nitni wcin am karbunkel d ajurwani d lburḍa s tintat ifarzen d řeqṭen azdad d řmarjan d řeɛqaq izeggwaɣen di ṭṭweɛ n sseřɛet nni \add d asen tqeddmed\add*.   
\m
\v 17 Yahuda d temmurt n Israil tuɣa ttsebbaben akidem. Nitni wcin am yimendi zi Minnit uřa d ḥalawit, tamment, zzect d balsam di ṭṭweɛ n sseřɛet nnem.   
\m
\v 18 Dimacq tuɣa ittsebbab akidem deg waṭṭas n řeqcuɛ i tṣennɛed, x marra igeřwan nnem, s binu n Xilbun d tḍuft tacemřařt.   
\m
\v 19 Di ṭṭweɛ n \add sseřɛet\add* nni \add d asen\add* tezzenzed, wcin am Wadan d Yawan uzzař n wemziř d qassiya d uɣanim aḥemmum ittfuḥen zi Uzal.   
\m
\v 20 Dadan tuɣa ittsebbab akidem s werruḍ n tbardiwin i uneddah.   
\m
\v 21 Iɛraben \add di řwaṭat\add* d marra řḥukkam n Qidar tuɣa ttsebbaben akidem. Deg izemrawen d icarriyyen d iɣayḍen tuɣa ttsebbaben akidem.   
\m
\v 22 Isebbaben n Caba d yinni n Raɛma tuɣa aten d isebbaben nnem. Nitni wcin řemxeyyer n řeɛṭur d ɛřam kuř iẓra iɣřan d wureɣ di ṭṭweɛ n sseřɛat nni d asen tqeddmed.   
\m
\v 23 Ḥaran d Kinna d Ɛadan, isebbaben n Caba, Accur \add d\add* Kilmad, tuɣa ttsebbaben akidem.  
\v 24 Nitni tuɣa ttsebbaben akidem deg řeɛbayat icennɛen d iseřhamen ideḥmiyyen d lburḍat tiqarqacin u di řkettan iɣřan s \add ifiřan n\add* tintat ifarzen nni \add iǧan\add* jar sseřɛet nnem s tesɣunin ijehden ittwamuden.   
\b  
\m
\v 25 Iɣarruba n Tarcic tuɣa aten d ikaravanen nnem d sseřɛet nnem.  
\b  
\m \qt Tuɣa cem \+tl dinni\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt teccured u tdeqřed aṭṭas\qt*  
\m \qt deg wuř n řebḥur.\qt*   
\m
\v 26 \qt Iqeddafen \+tl nnem\+tl* iwyen cem\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar waman yuɛřan,\qt*  
\m \qt asemmiḍ zi ccarq yarẓa cem\qt*  
\m \qt deg wuř n řebḥur.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 27:26 \xt Ḥiz. 17:1\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 27 \qt Igeřwan nnem d sseřɛet nni tezzenzed\qt*  
\m \qt d tsebbabt nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt ibeḥriyyen nnem d ineddahen nnem\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni iɛeddřen tireẓẓa nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt d isebbaben nni ittsebbaben akidem,\qt*  
\m \qt d marra iɛeskariyyen \+tl inni\+tl* akidem\qt*  
\m \qt u ak-d marra agraw di řwesṭ nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt ad wḍan \+tl marra\+tl* deg wuř n řebḥur\qt*  
\m \qt deg wass n uweṭṭu nnem.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 27:27 \xt Asa. 18:9-19\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 28 \qt Zi řḥess n tɣuyyit n ineddahen nnem\qt*  
\m \qt ad arjijen dcurat nnem.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 27:28 \xt Ḥiz. 26:10, 15\x*   
\m
\v 29 \qt Ad hwan zi tɣarruba\qt*  
\m \qt marra inni iṭṭfen timeqdafin,\qt*  
\m \qt marra ibeḥriyyen d marra ineddahen nnem.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad bedden x temmurt,\qt*   
\m
\v 30 \qt uca ad ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad sɣuyen s \+tl imeṭṭawen imarzagen\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt ad nḍaren \+tl a\+tl*cař x izeǧifen nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad zuzzaren iɣɣeḍ x yixef nsen,\qt*   
\m
\v 31 \qt uca ad ḥeffen ixef nsen zi ssibbet nnem.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad beysen s txuncay \+tl n wecḍan\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad xam run s řeɛmar \+tl iccur\+tl* s tarzugi\qt*  
\m \qt u ad ssgeɛɛden ict n tɣuyyit tamerzagt.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 27:31 \xt Irm. 48:37\x*   
\m
\v 32 \qt Am ttweḥwiḥen ad xam ssgeɛɛden\qt*  
\m \qt ijj n izři n wecḍan,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad xam wten agejdur,\qt*  
\m \qt ad inin: Man wen \+tl iǧan\+tl* am Ṣur,\qt*  
\m \qt am \+tl tendint\+tl* ittwahedmen\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n řebḥar?\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 33 \qt Řami dd-iwyen sseřɛet nnem\qt*  
\m \qt zeg \+add ujemmaḍ n\+add* řebḥur,\qt*  
\m \qt tuɣa tessjiwned aṭṭas n řegnus.\qt*  
\m \qt S waṭṭas n igeřwan nnem d tsebbabt nnem\qt*  
\m \qt tarrid ijeǧiden n temmurt d ttwajaren.\qt*   
\m
\v 34 \qt Di tsaɛɛet nni di tᵉttwarẓed s řebḥur,\qt*  
\m \qt di řmehmud n waman,\qt*  
\m \qt tuɣa tewḍa tsebbabt nnem marra\qt*  
\m \qt u marra agraw i ɣarem \+tl di řebḥar\+tl*.\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 35 \qt Marra imezdaɣ n tegzirin ttbehten\qt*  
\m \qt u ijeǧiden nsen ttarjifen,\qt*  
\m \qt ttnexřaɛen udmawen nsen.\qt*   
\m
\v 36 \qt Isebbaben jar řegnus ad xam ṣeffaren,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa tdewřed d ijj n umedya i warjef,\qt*  
\m \qt uca war tᵉttiřid ɛad i řebda.’”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 27:36 \xt Ḥiz. 26:21\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 28
\s1 Awař x řḥakem n Ṣur  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ini i řḥakem n Ṣur: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Minzi tessgeɛɛded uř nnec, tennid: Necc d arebbi, necc ttɣimiɣ x řkursi n arebbi di řwesṭ n řebḥur!, waxxa cek d bnadem, war teǧid d arebbi, aqa teggid uř nnec \add xenni\add* am wuř n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 28:2 \xt Ica. 31:3\x*  
\v 3 Xzar, cek d amiɣis x Daniyil, war din \add iǧi\add* uřa d ijj n ssirr xak innuffaren.  
\v 4 S tiɣit nnec d řefhamet nnec aqa tessmuned i yixef nnec igeřwan \add mɣaren\add* u teggid ureɣ d nnuqart deg ixxamen nnec n txubay.  
\v 5 S tiɣit nnec imɣaren ɣar tsebbabt nnec, tarnid deg igeřwan nnec uca di ssibbet n igeřwan nnec \add mɣaren,\add* issgeɛɛed wuř nnec ixef nnes.’  
\v 6 S uya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Umi teggid uř nnec am wuř n AREBBI,  
\v 7 s uya, xzar, Necc ad xak dd-awyeɣ ibarraniyyen, řegnus iqesḥen aṭṭas. Nitni ad dd-jebden řesyuf nsen ḍidd i weẓri n tiɣit nnec uca ad ssfesden tissiqt nnec. \x ◘ \xo 28:7 \xt Irm. 6:23\x*  
\v 8 Nitni ad cek ssehwan ɣar \add weḥfur n\add* turṣuḍi uca ad temmted řmewt n yinni ittwassnuqqben deg wuř n řebḥur.  
\v 9 Ma tzeɛmed s tidett ad tinid zzat i wudem n yinni cek i ɣa inɣen: ‘Necc d AREBBI’? Aqa cek d bnadem, war iǧi d arebbi deg ufus n yinni i cek i ɣa ideǧen.  
\v 10 Ad temmted s ufus n ibarraniyyen am yinni war ittwaxetnen, maɣar Necc nniɣ \add t\add*!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 12 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, sgeɛɛed \bd ijj n yezři n wecḍan x ujeǧid n Ṣur\bd* uca ini as:  
\b  
\m ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt \+tl A\+tl* cek, wenni d řxatem n řebni ifarzen,\qt*  
\m \qt teccured s tiɣit u tkemmřed deg weẓri!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 28:12 \xt Ḥiz. 27:3\x*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Tuɣa cek di Ɛadn, di jjennet n AREBBI.\qt*  
\m \qt Tuɣa dřin cek s ɛřam kuř iẓra iɣřan,\qt*  
\m \qt s řeɛqaq, tyaqut d dyamanti,\qt*  
\m \qt s texrisulit, uniks d yaspis,\qt*  
\m \qt s ṣaffir aziza, karbunkel, smaraxt d wureɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Řxedmet n ibendiren nnec\qt*  
\m \qt d ubarru n temɣarin nnec \+tl tuɣa\+tl* dayek,\qt*  
\m \qt deg wass nni di dd-tᵉttwaxeřqed tuɣa wejdent\qt*.   
\m
\v 14 \qt Tuɣa cek d ijj n ukirub\qt*  
\m \qt d amedhun issdurruyen,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu i\+tl* ggiɣ cek \+tl din\+tl*.\qt*  
\m \qt Tuɣa cek x wedrar iqeddsen n AREBBI,\qt*  
\m \qt teggured di řwesṭ n iẓra itteḥduduqen.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 28:14 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*   
\m
\v 15 \qt Tuɣa cek tkemmřed deg ibriden nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt zeg wass nni di dd-tᵉttwaxeřqed,\qt*  
\m \qt ař dayek tᵉttwaf řmuɛṣiyyet.\qt*   
\m
\v 16 \qt S řemɣaret n tsebbabt nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt iccur daxeř nnec s řexcunet\qt*  
\m \qt uca \+tl xenni\+tl* texḍiḍ.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl S uya\+tl* ad cek ssiggʷejeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt x wedrar n arebbi,\qt*  
\m \qt ad cek mḥiɣ zi řwesṭ n iẓra itteḥduduqen,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a\+tl* cek akirub issdurruyen!\qt*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Uř nnec issgeɛɛed ixef nnes s waẓri nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa tessɛiǧted tiɣit nnec\qt*  
\m \qt di ṭṭweɛ n tissiqt nnec \+tl iɛeffaren\+tl*.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc nḍareɣ cek x temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt uca ggiɣ cek zzat i wudem n ijeǧiden,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami zemmaren ad ɣarek xzaren s řḥegra.\qt*   
\m
\v 18 \qt Zi ssibbet n waṭṭas n řmuɛṣiyyet nnec\qt*  
\m \qt d řɣecc n tsebbabt nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa tɣesbed tizawiyyin nnec iqeddsen.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl S uyenni\+tl* arriɣ timessi teffeɣ-dd\qt*  
\m \qt zi řwesṭ nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt tenni cek iccen,\qt*  
\m \qt uca arriɣ cek d iɣɣeḍ x temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra inni cek ittwařan.\qt*   
\m
\v 19 \qt Marra inni cek issnen jar řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt arejfen zzayek.\qt*  
\m \qt Tdewřed d ijj n umedya n warjef\qt*  
\m \qt u war tᵉttiřid \+tl ɛad\+tl* i řebda.\qt*’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Awař ḍidd i Ṣur  
\m
\v 20 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 21 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, arr udem nnec ɣar Ṣidun uca nabb ḍidd nnes,  
\v 22 uca ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, Necc aqa ayi ḍidd nnem, \add a\add* tandint n Ṣidun! Necc ad ttwassɛuǧeɣ di řwest nnec. Uca nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI xmi i ɣa ggeɣ řeḥkamat di \add Ṣidun\add* uca ad dayes ttwaqeddseɣ.  
\v 23 Ad ssekkeɣ ṭṭaɛun di řwesṭ nnes uřa d idammen deg ibriden nnes u wenni ittwanɣen ad iwḍa di řwesṭ nnes s ssif nni xas \add i ɣa yiřin\add* zeg wenneḍ nnes. \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen, belli Necc d SIDI,  
\v 24 uca ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad yiři i taddart n Israil asennan iqebcen niɣ tazeggʷart itteqqsen zeg inni d asen dd-innḍen, inni ten isseḥqaran. Nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d Sidi, d SIDI \add i ǧiɣ\add*.’”   
\m
\v 25 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI inu, SIDI: ‘Xmi ɣa ssmuneɣ taddart n Israil zi řegnus nni mani ttwabezzɛen nitni uca Necc ssecneɣ ixef inu d Amqeddes daysen zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus, \add xenni\add* ad zedɣen di temmurt nni wciɣ i umsexxar inu Yaɛqub.  
\v 26 Nitni ad zedɣen di řaman uca ad bnan tudrin, ad ggen imarjaɛen n uḍiř u ad daysen ẓẓun tizayarin, \add wah,\add* nitni ad \add din\add* zedɣen di řaman awarni řami ggiɣ řeḥkamat x marra inni ten ikeccḍen zi \add temmura\add* i d asen dd-innḍen. \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nsen.’” \x ◘ \xo 28:26 \xt Irm. 31:5\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 29
\s1 Awař x Miṣra am ict n řhaycet  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI \bd deg useggʷas wiss ɛecra, deg uyur wiss ɛecra, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss tenɛac n uyur\bd*, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, arr udem nnec ɣar firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra uca nabb xas u x marra \add tammurt n\add* Miṣra.  
\v 3 Siweř, ini:  
\b  
\m ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt Xzar, Necc ḍidd nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a\+tl* firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl cek\+tl* d řhaycet tameqqrant\qt*  
\m \qt nni izzřen di řwesṭ n iɣezran nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt tenni iqqaren: Iɣzar inu,\qt*  
\m \qt necc ggiɣ \+tl t\+tl* i yixef inu!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 29:3 \xt Izhd. 74:13, 14; Ica. 27:1; 51:9\x*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Necc ad ggeɣ tisennarin deg uɣesmar nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ssřesqeɣ iseřman n iɣezran nnec\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar teqcurin nnec.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad cek dd-jebdeɣ zi řwesṭ n iɣezran nnec\qt*  
\m \qt uca marra iseřman n iɣezran nnec\qt*  
\m \qt ad řesqen ɣar teqcurin nnec.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 29:4 \xt Ḥiz. 38:4\x*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Necc ad cek nḍareɣ \+tl barra\+tl* di řexřa,\qt*  
\m \qt cek d marra iseřman n iɣezran nnec.\qt*  
\m \qt X wudem n yeyyar ad tewḍid.\qt*  
\m \qt War \+tl din\+tl* wenni cek i ɣa yawyen\qt*  
\m \qt niɣ cek i ɣa iṭṭfen.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc ad cek wceɣ d macca\qt*  
\m \qt i řewḥuc n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt u i ijḍaḍ n ujenna.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Marra imezdaɣ n Miṣra ad ssnen\qt*  
\m \qt belli Necc d SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar nitni tuɣa aten d azeǧaḍ n uɣanim\qt*  
\m \qt i \+tl x tuɣa tsenned\+tl* taddart n Israil.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 29:6 \xt 2 Ij. 18:21; Ica. 36:6\x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Mařa nitni ksin cek s ufus nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt tfeǧqed uca tessnuqqbed ɣarsen\qt*  
\m \qt taɣruḍt nsen marra,\qt*  
\m \qt u mařa xak ssenden,\qt*  
\m \qt tarẓid uca tessarjijed\qt*  
\m \qt tijɛinnatin \+tl nsen\+tl* marra.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 “\bd S uya\bd*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad xak sseɛduɣ ssif uca ad qesseɣ zzayek bnadem d řmař.  
\v 9 Tammurt n Miṣra ad tedweř i ureddeǧ u i řxirbet uca nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, minzi netta inna: ‘Iɣzar inu u necc ggiɣ \add t\add*!’”   
\m
\v 10 “\bd S uya\bd*, xzar, Necc xak u x iɣezran nnec u Necc ad ggeɣ tammurt n Miṣra d řexrabi, \add wah,\add* d ict n řxirbet n wareddeǧ zi Majdal ař Aswan, ař aymir n \add temmurt n\add* Kuc.  
\v 11 Uřa d ijj n bnadem war zzayes iẓekkwi x uḍar u uřa d ijj n uḍar n řmař ad xas iẓwa. War dayek ttiřin imezḍaɣ i yijj n řmijar n \bd arebɛin n iseggʷusa\bd*.  
\v 12 \add Minzi\add* Necc ad ggeɣ tammurt n Miṣřa d areddeǧ di řwesṭ n temmura ttwaredǧent uca tineddam ad iřint d areddeǧ di řwesṭ n tneddam \add nneɣni\add* nni idewřen d řxirbat, \add řmijar n\add* \bd arebɛin n iseggʷusa\bd*, u Necc ad ssuyseɣ Imiṣriyyen jar řegnus uca ad ten bezzɛeɣ x temmura.”   
\m
\v 13 “Maca ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Awarni řami i ɣa ɛdun \bd arebɛin n iseggʷusa\bd* Necc ad ssmuneɣ Imiṣriyyen zi řegnus nni mani tuɣa ttwabezzɛen.  
\v 14 Necc ad beddřeɣ tameḥbast n Imiṣriyyen uca ad ten ssɛeqbeɣ di temmurt n Fatrus, di temmurt i zzayes dd-iffɣen, uca dinni ad iřin d ict n tgeldit tameɛnanuct.  
\v 15 Tageldit nsen ad tiři d tameɛnanuct zi tgeldatin nneɣni u war tessgeɛɛad ixef nnes ɛad x řegnus, minzi Necc ad ten ssmeẓyeɣ ařami war ttṣellṭen ɛad x řegnus.  
\v 16 War tᵉttiři ɛad i taddart n Israil d atecři nni ten i ɣa issidar řmuɛṣiyyet, řami dewřen ɣarsen, ḍeffaren ten. Nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d Sidi, d SIDI \add i ǧiɣ\add*.’” \x ◘ \xo 29:16 \xt Igjd. 4:17\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmunet n Nabuxadraṣṣar x umenɣi nnes ḍidd n Ṣur  
\m
\v 17 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u-ɛicrin, deg uyur wiss amezwaru, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* amezwaru n uyur\bd* imsar belli yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:   
\m
\v 18 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, yarra řɛeskar nnes ad yegg ict n řxedmet tameqqrant ḍidd i Ṣur. Marra azeǧif iqqim d aqeccar u marra taɣřuḍt tarkec, \add maca\add* war ɣares tuɣi řexřaṣ zi \add tendint n\add* Ṣur, i netta u i řɛeskar nnes x řxedmet i yegga ḍidd nnes.   
\m
\v 19 \bd S uya\bd*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad wceɣ tammurt n Miṣra i Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil. Netta ad \add zzayes\add* dd-yawi afeyyeḍ n wagřa nnes uca ad ikecceḍ takeccaḍt nnes uca ad ikkes tukkarḍa. Aya ad yiři d řexřaṣ nnes i řɛeskar nnes.  
\v 20 X řxedmet nni yegga ḍidd \add Ṣur\add* wciɣ as tammurt n Miṣra d řexřaṣ, minzi nitni ggin tt di ṭṭweɛ inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 21 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad arreɣ icc n Israil ad dd-iffeɣ uca ad arzmeɣ aqemmum nnec di řwesṭ nsen. \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 30
\s1 Řḥukm x Miṣra s ssif  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, nabb uca ini:  
\b  
\m ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt Rum! Ayyehhat x wass nni!\qt*   
\m
\v 3 \qt Minzi yudes i yeǧa wass \+tl nni\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt yudes i yeǧa wass i SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt ass n iseynuten.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad yiři d tasaɛɛet n řegnus.\qt*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Ad dd-yas ssif di Miṣra.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad yiři warjef ameqqran\qt*  
\m \qt di \+tl temmurt n\+tl* Kuc,\qt*  
\m \qt xmi ɣa wḍan inni ittwassnuqqben di Miṣra,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi ad awyen afeyyeḍ n wagřa nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt ad areddǧen dsusa nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Kuc d Fuṭ d Lud d ɛřam kuř ibarraniyyen,\qt*  
\m \qt d Kub d ayt n temmurt n Řɛahd\qt*  
\m \qt ad kisen wḍan s ssif.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Inni ittcařen x Miṣra ad wḍan\qt*  
\m \qt u nnfaxet n ṣṣulṭa nnes ad tɣarq.\qt*  
\m \qt Zi Majdal ař Aswan ad wḍan\qt*  
\m \qt s ssif di temmurt!’,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu i\+tl* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 30:6 \ft \+fk di temmurt\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘dayes’.\f*   
\m
\v 7 \qt ‘Nitni ad ttwaredǧen\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n temmura ittwaredǧent\qt*  
\m \qt u tineddam nnes ad iřint\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n tneddam \+tl nneɣni\+tl* ittwaxarrben.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt \+tl Xenni\+tl* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt xmi ɣa ssarɣeɣ timessi di Miṣra\qt*  
\m \qt uca marra inni tt ittɛawanen ad ttwarẓen.\qt*   
\m
\v 9 \bdit Deg wass nni\bdit*  
\m \qt ad ffɣen ireqqasen s tɣarruba\qt*  
\m \qt zi zzat n wudem inu,\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad ssiggʷeden Kuc\qt*  
\m \qt wenni umi ittɣiř aqa netta di řaman.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad daysen yiři warjef ameqqran,\qt*  
\m \qt amecnaw deg wass nni n Miṣra,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar xzar, ad dd-yas!’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 \qt “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Necc ad ssbeddeɣ řɣaci inhewřen n Miṣra\qt*  
\m \qt s ufus n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil.\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Netta d řgens nnes akides,\qt*  
\m \qt imsaggʷaden qaɛ n řegnus\qt*  
\m \qt ad dd-asen ḥima ad teḥḥan tammurt.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad ssuffɣen řesyuf nsen ḍidd i Miṣra\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ccuren tammurt\qt*  
\m \qt s yinni ittwassnuqqben.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 30:11 \xt Ḥiz. 28:7\x*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Necc ad ssiẓɣeɣ iɣezran\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad zzenzeɣ tammurt i iɛeffanen\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad areddǧeɣ tammurt d marra min dayes\qt*  
\m \qt s ufus n ibarraniyyen.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc, SIDI, wenni innan \+tl aya\+tl*.’”\qt* \f ◼ \fr 30:12 \ft \+fk marra min dayes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘tacurret nnes’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Necc ad areddǧeɣ imeyḍa n l’aṣnam\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad qḍiɣ x l’aṣnam zi Nuf.\qt*  
\m \qt War ittɣimi ɛad uřa d ijj n řḥakem zi Miṣra.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc ad ssidfeɣ řɛurret di temmurt n Miṣra.\qt*   
\m
\v 14 \qt Necc ad areddǧeɣ Fatrus\qt*  
\m \qt u ad ssarɣeɣ Ṣuɛan\qt*  
\m \qt u ad awyeɣ řeḥkamat inu di Nu.\qt*   
\m
\v 15 \qt Necc ad ssfarɣeɣ asɛar inu x Sin,\qt*  
\m \qt lburj n Miṣra,\qt*  
\m \qt ad qeḍɛeɣ řɣaci inhewřen n Nu.\qt*   
\m
\v 16 \qt Necc ad ssidfeɣ timessi ɣar Miṣra,\qt*  
\m \qt Sin ad tefsi s řeḥriq,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl tammurt n\+tl* Nu ad tᵉttwafeǧeq\qt*  
\m \qt u Nuf ad tiři di řeḥṣaret kuř ass.\qt*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Iḥudriyyen zi Awan d Fibista\qt*  
\m \qt ad wḍan s ssif\qt*  
\m \qt u \+tl timɣarin\+tl* ad uyurent di tmeḥbast.\qt*   
\m
\v 18 \qt Ass ad ittbarcen di Taḥfaḥis\qt*  
\m \qt xmi ɣa \+tl y\+tl*arẓeɣ Necc azayřu n Miṣra,\qt*  
\m \qt u ad as ssbeddeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt nnfaxet n jjehd nnes dinni.\qt*  
\m \qt Ijj n useynu ad tt issdurri\qt*  
\m \qt uca yessis ad uyurent\qt*  
\m \qt di tmeḥbast.\qt*   
\m
\v 19 \qt Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ řeḥkamat x Misřa\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řḥukm x Firɛun d uzzuzar n řgens nnes  
\m
\v 20 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss ḥiṭac, deg uyur amezwaru, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss sebɛa n uyur\bd* imsar belli yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:   
\m
\v 21 “‘\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, Necc arẓiɣ aɣiř n firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra. Xzar, war t ijebbar uřa d ijjen maḥend ad ittwassgenfa, war t ttennḍen s bindat ařami zzaysent t ɣa ssjehden, ḥima ad iṭṭef ssif \add ɛawed\add*!’  
\v 22 \bd S uya\bd*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc x firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣřa, u Necc ad arẓeɣ iɣaǧen nnes, \add am uɣiř\add* ijehden \add ɛad\add* am wenni ittwarẓin. Necc ad arreɣ ssif nnes ad iwḍa zeg ufus nnes.  
\v 23 Necc ad zuzzareɣ Imiṣriyyen jar řegnus u ad ten bezzɛeɣ x temmura.  
\v 24 Necc ad ssjehdeɣ iɣaǧen n ujeǧid n Babil uca ad wceɣ ssif inu deg ufus nnes, \add maca\add* iɣaǧen n firɛun ad ten arẓeɣ, \add ařami\add* i ɣa isɣuy am isɣuyyu wenni issnuqben.  
\v 25 \add Wah\add* Necc ad ssjehdeɣ iɣaǧen n ujeǧid n Babil, \add maca\add* iɣaǧen n firɛun ad wḍan. \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, xmi ɣa ggeɣ ssif inu deg ufus n ujeǧid n Babil u netta ad t isswiẓẓeḍ x temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 26 Necc ad zuzzareɣ Imiṣriyyen jar řegnus, ad ten bezzɛeɣ x temmura. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 31
\s1 Accur aqa-t d ijj n weɛřem i Miṣra  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss ḥiṭac, deg uyur wiss třata, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* amezwaru n uyur\bd* imsar belli yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ini i firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, u i marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Wi akidek imquddan\qt*  
\m \qt s \+tl marra\+tl* řemɣaret nnec?\qt*   
\m
\v 3 \qt Xzar, tuɣa Accur d tacejjart n tengelt\qt*  
\m \qt x \+tl idurar n\+tl* Lubnan\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d tseḍwin icnan d tifray i itticen tiři mliḥ\qt*  
\m \qt u ak-d tiddi d azirar yuɛřan,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami tuccent nnes\qt*  
\m \qt tiweḍ-dd ař iseynuten.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 31:3 \xt Dan. 4:7\x*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Aman arrin tt ad iyma,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl aman\+tl* ihewřen ssgeɛɛden tt aṭṭas.\qt*  
\m \qt Iɣezran n waman nnes ssizzřen\qt*  
\m \qt deg wenneḍ n tebhirt nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uca \+tl aman ihewřen\+tl* arrin\qt*  
\m \qt iɣezran nnes ad raḥen\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar marra ticejjura n yeyyar.\qt*   
\m
\v 5 \qt X uya ittwassuɛřa tiddi nnes\qt*  
\m \qt x marra ticejjura n yeyyar,\qt*  
\m \qt u tiseḍwin nnes dewřent s waṭṭas\qt*  
\m \qt u ifetwan nnes zzuggarten\qt*  
\m \qt s waman ifeyyḍen,\qt*  
\m \qt xmi tuɣa tessɣemmi.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Marra ijḍaḍ n ujenna\qt*  
\m \qt ggin řɛucc nsen di tseḍwin nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt marra řmař n yeyyar\qt*  
\m \qt ferxen sadu ifetwan nnes\qt*  
\m \qt u marra řegnus mɣaren\qt*  
\m \qt tuɣa ttɣiman di tiři nnes.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 31:6 \xt Dan. 4:9\x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Tuɣa-tt tecna s řemɣaret nnes\qt*  
\m \qt u s tuzzeggart n tseḍwin nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar aẓwar nnes\qt*  
\m \qt tuɣa-t ak-d waṭṭas n waman.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Ticejjura n tengelt di jjennet n AREBBI\qt*  
\m \qt war xas ɛdunt,\qt*  
\m \qt ticejjura n umerzi\qt*  
\m \qt war sekkwint tseḍwin nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uca ticejjura n dulb\qt*  
\m \qt war sekkwint ifetwan nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Uřa d ict n tcejjart di jjennet n AREBBI\qt*  
\m \qt tarwes dayes deg waẓri nnes.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 31:8 \ft \+fk ticejjura\ft  - niɣ ‘iddagen’. \fk amerzi\ft  - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 31:8 \xt Amz. 2:8\x*   
\m
\v 9 \qt Ggiɣ tt tecna ak-d waṭṭas n tseḍwin nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami zzayes usment\qt*  
\m \qt marra ticejjura n Ɛadn,\qt*  
\m \qt tinni tuɣa di jjennet n AREBBI.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “\bdit S uya\bdit*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Umi tessgeɛɛded ixef nnem s tiddi nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl wah\+tl* nettat tegga tuccent nnes\qt*  
\m \qt jar iseynuten\qt*  
\m \qt u uř nnes issgeɛɛed ixef nnes\qt*  
\m \qt zi ssibbet n řuɛřa nnes,\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt s uyenni wciɣ tt deg ufus\qt*  
\m \qt n wenni d amzemmar qaɛ jar řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl wenni\+tl* iggin s tidett\qt*  
\m \qt am dd-ittřiqen ak-d tuɛeffna nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl uca\+tl* ammu i uẓẓřeɣ xas.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Zedmen tt ibarraniyyen,\qt*  
\m \qt řegnus iqesḥen aṭṭas,\qt*  
\m \qt zedmen t uca jjin tt.\qt*  
\m \qt Tiseḍwin nnes wḍant x idurar\qt*  
\m \qt u di marra tiɣzurtin,\qt*  
\m \qt ifetwan nnes ttwarẓen\qt*  
\m \qt di marra tiɣezratin n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt u marra řegnus n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt hwan-dd zi \+tl sadu\+tl* tiři nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uca jjin tt.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 31:12 \xt Ḥiz. 28:7; 30:11\x*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Marra ijḍaḍ n ujenna zedɣen\qt*  
\m \qt x \+tl ukeccuḍ\+tl* nnes nni iwḍan\qt*  
\m \qt uca marra řmař n yeyyar\qt*  
\m \qt tuɣa aten x ifetwan nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 14 \qt \+tl Necc ggiɣ tt\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima marra ticejjura war dikkwiřent ɛad\qt*  
\m \qt ttneffxent s tiddi nsent\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ggent tuccent nsen deg iseynuten,\qt*  
\m \qt u marra \+tl ticejjura\+tl* nni iswin aman\qt*  
\m \qt s ufeyyeḍ,\qt*  
\m \qt war ttbeddint ɛad s yixef nsent\qt*  
\m \qt di nnfaxet nsent,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar nitenti marra\qt*  
\m \qt ttwamewcent i řmewt,\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar řaǧaɣ n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n tarwa n bnadem,\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d inni ihekkwan\qt*  
\m \qt deg weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Deg wass nni di tehwa ɣar řaxart,\qt*  
\m \qt ggiɣ ijj wecḍan.\qt*  
\m \qt Di ṭṭweɛ nnes dřiɣ \+tl aman\+tl* ihewřen\qt*  
\m \qt uca ssbeddeɣ iɣezran nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uca fecřen waman imɣaren.\qt*  
\m \qt Di ṭṭweɛ nnes ssbarrecneɣ\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl idurar n\+tl* Lubnan\qt*  
\m \qt uca marra ticejjura n yeyyar ceḍnent xas.\qt*   
\m
\v 16 \qt S ddriz n uweṭṭu nnes ssarjijeɣ řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt umi tt ssehwiɣ ɣar řaxart\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d inni ihekkwan deg weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*.\qt*  
\m \qt Marra ticejjura n Ɛadn,\qt*  
\m \qt tinni iɛizzen aṭṭas d tinni icnan qaɛ\qt*  
\m \qt zi Lubnan,\qt*  
\m \qt tinni iswin \+tl aṭṭas n\+tl* waman marra,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ttwassfewwjent \+tl s man aya\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt di řaǧaɣ n temmurt.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 31:16 \xt Ica. 14:9\x*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Uřa d nitenti hwant akides ɣar řaxart,\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar inni ittwanɣen s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt inni tuɣa aɣiř nnes \+tl ijehden\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt inni tuɣa iqqimen di tiři nnes\qt*  
\m \qt di řwest n řegnus.\qt*   
\m
\v 18 \qt Ak wi tsawid ammu di řɛezz d řemɣaret\qt*  
\m \qt jar tcejjura n Ɛadn?\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Waxxa amenni\+tl* ad tᵉttwassehwid\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d tcejjura n Ɛadn\qt*  
\m \qt ař raǧaɣ n temmurt.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad tbuzzřed di řwest n yinni war ittwaxetnen,\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d inni ittwanɣen s ssif.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Uca ad inin:\+tl* Wa d firɛun\qt*  
\m \qt d marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen!’,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu i\+tl* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 31:18 \xt Ḥiz. 28:10\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 32
\s1 Izři n wecḍan x firɛun  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss tenɛac, deg uyur wiss tenɛac, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* amezwaru n uyur\bd* imsar belli yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, sgeɛɛed ijj n yezři n wecḍan x firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, uca ini as:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Tuɣa cek am weyrad d ameẓyan\qt*  
\m \qt jar řegnus\qt*  
\m \qt u tuɣa cek am řhaycet di řebḥur.\qt*  
\m \qt Tɣeḍřed ixef nnec deg iɣezran,\qt*  
\m \qt tessenhezzed aman s iḍaren nnec\qt*  
\m \qt uca tessefsad iɣezran nsen.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 32:2 \xt Ḥiz. 29:3\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Necc ad xak sswiẓẓḍeɣ tracca inu,\qt*  
\m \qt s yijj n wegraw n řegnus aṭṭas.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad cek ssiřyen ak-d tracca inu.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 32:3 \xt Ḥiz. 12:13; 17:20\x*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Necc ad cek jjeɣ di temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt ad cek nḍareɣ x wudem n yeyyar.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad xak sszedɣeɣ marra ijḍaḍ n ujenna\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad zzayek ssjiwneɣ imuddaren\qt*  
\m \qt zi marra tammurt.\qt*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Ad ggeɣ weysum nnec x idurar\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ccureɣ tiɣzurin\qt*  
\m \qt s řegɛudi \+tl n warrayem\+tl* nnec.\qt*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Necc ad ssesweɣ tammurt ař idurar,\qt*  
\m \qt s ufeyyeḍ n idammen nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt uca tiɣezratin ad ccurent zzayek.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \qt ‘Necc ad ssduryeɣ ajenna\qt*  
\m \qt xmi cek ɣa ssxesyeɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad ssbarrecneɣ itran nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ssduryeɣ tafuct s iseynuten,\qt*  
\m \qt uca taziri war ttejji \+tl ɛad\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ad tarɣa tfawt nnes.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 32:7 \xt Ica. 13:10; Yuw. 3:4. \x*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Marra tifawin yareqqen deg ujenna\qt*  
\m \qt ad tent ssbarrecneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nnec\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ssekkeɣ taǧest x temmurt nnec!’,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ammu\+tl* i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.\qt*   
\m
\v 9 \qt ‘Necc ad ɣezziɣ uř n waṭṭas n řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt umi i ɣa yawyeɣ \+tl řexbar\+tl* n treẓẓit nnec\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar řegnus, ɣar temmura\qt*  
\m \qt i war tent tessined ca.\qt*   
\m
\v 10 \qt Necc ad ssnexřɛeɣ aṭṭas n řegnus\qt*  
\m \qt di ssibbet nnec\qt*  
\m \qt u acuwwaf n ijeǧiden nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ad geɛɛden \+tl zeg warjef\+tl* di ṭṭweɛ nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt xmi ɣa ssenhezzeɣ ssif inu \+tl ssa d ssa\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt zzat i wudmawen nsen.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad arjijen řebda,\qt*  
\m \qt kuř ijj di ssibbet n tudart nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt deg wass n uweṭṭu nnec.’\qt* \f ◼ \fr 32:10 \ft \+fk tudart\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Ssif n ujeǧid n Babil ad xak yemmars.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt S řesyuf n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt\qt*  
\m \qt ad ɣeḍřeɣ řɣaci nnec inhewřen.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa-ten řegnus iqesḥen aṭṭas marra,\qt*  
\m \qt nitni ad qḍan x nnfaxet n Miṣra\qt*  
\m \qt uca marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen\qt*  
\m \qt ad ittwateḥḥa.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 32:12 \xt Ḥiz. 28:7; 31:12; 31:2, 18; 32:16 \x*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Necc ad qḍiɣ x imuddaren nnes\qt*  
\m \qt inni \+tl iǧan\+tl* ɣar waṭṭas n waman,\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d ijj n uḍar n bnadem\qt*  
\m \qt ad ten issarwi ɛawed\qt*  
\m \qt uca uřa d ict n tecḍect n řmař\qt*  
\m \qt ad ten tessarwi \+tl ɛad\+tl*.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 \qt ‘Xenni ad ssehwiɣ aman nsen\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ařami i ɣa ṣfan\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt u Necc ad ggeɣ iɣezran nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ad ssizzřen am zzect!’\qt*  
\m \add ... ammu\add* i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI ...   
\m
\v 15 \qt ‘... Ařami ggiɣ tammurt n Miṣra d areddeǧ\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tiři temmurt tᵉttwareddeǧ,\qt*  
\m \qt teḥfa zi marra min dayes,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami wteɣ marra inni dayes izeddɣen,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl xenni\+tl* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.’”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 “Wa d izři n wecḍan uca ad t ɣennjen am yezři n wecḍan, yessitsent n temmura ad t ɣennjent am yezři n wecḍan, ad t ɣennjent am \bd yezři n wecḍan x Miṣra u x marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen!\bd*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iẓri n wecḍan ɣar wenḍeř n firɛun ak-d ubarru nnes  
\m
\v 17 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss tenɛac, \+bdit deg uyur wiss tenɛac\+bdit*, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss xemmesṭac n uyur\bd* imsar belli yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:   
\b  
\m
\v 18 \qt “\+tl A\+tl* mmis n bnadem,\qt*  
\m \qt wwet agejdur x řɣaci inhewřen n\qt* \bdit Miṣra\bdit*.  
\m \qt Ejj i-t ad ihwa,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Miṣra\+tl* ak-d yessis n řegnus ijehden,\qt*  
\m \qt di řaǧaɣ n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d yinni ihwan deg weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*.\qt*   
\m
\v 19 \qt Ma cek iɛizzen x man mma?\qt*  
\m \qt Hwa, ejj ad cek ssarsen\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d yinni war ittwaxetnen.\qt*   
\m
\v 20 \qt Ad wḍan di řwesṭ\qt*  
\m \qt n yinni ittwanɣen s ssif.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa immewc ssif.\qt*  
\m \qt Jarr \+tl Miṣra\+tl* \+tl zeg webrid\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen.\qt*   
\m
\v 21 \qt Inni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa aṭṭas\qt*  
\m \qt zeg ayt n bu-teɣruḍt\qt*  
\m \qt ad ssiwřen akides\qt*  
\m \qt u ak-d yinni t iɛawanen\qt*  
\m \qt zi řwesṭ n řaxart.\qt*  
\m \qt Hwan nitni, aqa zzřen \+tl dinni\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt inni war ittwaxetnen,\qt*  
\m \qt inni ittwanɣen s ssif.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 22 \qt ‘Diha iǧa\qt* \bdit Accur\bdit* \qt ak-d marra agraw nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt nnḍen as-dd imeḍřan nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Marra nitni ttwanɣen, wḍan s ssif.\qt*   
\m
\v 23 \qt Imeḍřan nnes aqa aten di tɣemmar\qt*  
\m \qt n weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt u agraw nnes aqa-t deg wenneḍ n wenḍeř nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Marra nitni ttwassnuqqben,\qt*  
\m \qt wḍan s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt inni tuɣa issaggʷaden\qt*  
\m \qt di temmurt n yinni iddaren.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 24 \qt ‘Diha\qt* \bdit Ɛilam\bdit* \qt d marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen\qt*  
\m \qt deg wenneḍ n wenḍeř nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Marra nitni ttwassnuqqben, wḍan s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt hwan břa axtan di řaǧaɣ n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt inni tuɣa issaggʷaden\qt*  
\m \qt di temmurt n yinni iddaren.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni iwyen řefḍiḥet nsen akidsen,\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d yinni ihekkwan\qt*  
\m \qt deg weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*.\qt*   
\m
\v 25 \qt Ggin as ijj n wemcan n arraḥet\qt*  
\m \qt di řwest n yinni ittwanɣen,\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen.\qt*  
\m \qt Imeḍřan nnes nnḍen as-dd.\qt*  
\m \qt Marra nitni war ittwaxetnen,\qt*  
\m \qt wḍan s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi tuɣa ssaggʷaden \+tl iwdan\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt di temmurt n yinni iddaren.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni iwyen řefḍiḥet nsen akidsen,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl jmiɛ\+tl* ak-d yinni ihekkwan\qt*  
\m \qt deg weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa netta ittwassars\qt*  
\m \qt di řwest n yinni ittwanɣen.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 26 \qt Diha\qt* \bdit Macix-Tubal\bdit*  
\m \qt d marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen.\qt*  
\m \qt Nnḍen as-dd imeḍřan nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Marra nitni war ttwaxetnen,\qt*  
\m \qt ttwassnuqqben s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar nitni tuɣa ssaggʷaden \+tl iwdan\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt di temmurt n yinni iddaren.\qt*   
\m
\v 27 \qt Inni iwḍan zeg yinni war ittwaxetnen\qt*  
\m \qt war zziřen ak-d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt\qt*  
\m \qt nni ihwan ɣar řaxart\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d řesnaḥ nsen n umenɣi.\qt*  
\m \qt Mmarsen řesyuf nsen sadu izeǧifen nsen\qt*  
\m \qt uca řmuɛṣiyyet nsen aqa-tt x yeysan nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt waxxa tuɣa nitni d tiggʷudi i ayt n bu-teɣruḍt\qt*  
\m \qt di temmurt n yinni iddaren.\qt*   
\m
\v 28 \qt Uřa d cek ad tiřid tarẓed\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n yinni war ittwaxetnen\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tezzřed\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d yinni ittwassnuqben s ssif.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 29 \qt ‘Diha\qt* \bdit Idum,\bdit* \qt ijeǧiden nnes d marra řḥukkam nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt inni \+tl i din ittwaggen\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt s \+tl marra\+tl* ṣṣulta nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d yinni ittwassnuqqben s ssif.\qt*  
\m \qt Zzřen \+tl dinni\+tl* ak-d yinni war ittwaxetnen\qt*  
\m \qt u ak-d yinni ihwan\qt*  
\m \qt deg weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 30 \qt ‘Diha\qt* \bdit ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa zi ccmal,\bdit*  
\m \qt marra nitni, u marra\qt* \bdit ayt n Ṣidun,\bdit*  
\m \qt inni ihwan ak-d yinni ittwanɣen.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa ttseḍḥan \+tl dinni\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt waxxa tuɣa ssaggʷaden \+tl iwdan\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt s teryast nsen n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa zzřen dinni břa axtan\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d yinni ittwanɣen s ssif\qt*  
\m \qt uca arebbun řefḍiḥet nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ak-d yinni ihwan deg weḥfur \+tl n wenḍeř\+tl*.’\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 31 \qt ‘Firɛun ad ten iẓar uca ad ittwassfewwej\qt*  
\m \qt zi marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen,\qt*  
\m \qt inni ittwassnuqqben s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt Firɛun d marra řɛeskar nnes,’\qt*  
\m \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI,   
\m
\v 32 \qt ‘minzi Necc jjiɣ t ad issiggʷed\qt*  
\m \qt inni di temmurt n yinni iddaren.\qt*  
\m \qt Netta ad immars di řwesṭ\qt*  
\m \qt n yinni war ittwaxetnen,\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar yinni ittwassnuqqben s ssif,\qt*  
\m \qt Firɛun d marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen,’\qt*  
\m \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 33
\s1 Ḥizqiyal d aɛessas x Israil i twařa wiss tnayen  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, siweř ak-d tarwa n řgens nnec, ini asen: ‘Xmi ɣa \add y\add*awyeɣ ssif x temmurt uca řgens n temmurt ad iksi ijj n weryaz zi ṭṭrufa nnes uca ad t ggen d aɛessas i yixef nsen  
\v 3 uca wanita itwařa yusa-dd ssif x temmurt, \add xenni\add* ittsuḍ deg uyicc n icarri uca iɛeǧem i řgens,  
\v 4 uca aqa din ijjen isřa i usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri, \add maca\add* war ijji ixef nnes ad zzayes ittwaɛřem uca yusa-dd ssif, ikkes i-t, \add xenni\add* idammen nnes ad iřin x uzeǧif nnes.  
\v 5 Netta isřa i řḥess n usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri, \add maca\add* war ijji ixef nnes ad ittwaɛřem, idammen nnes aqa aten xas, \add maca\add* řeɛmar n wenni ijjin ixef nnes ad ittwaɛřem, ad injem.   
\m
\v 6 Maca mařa aɛessas itwařa ssif yusa-dd uca war isuḍ deg uyicc n icarri, \add ařami\add* war ittwaɛřem řgens uca ssif yusa-dd, ikkes ijj n řeɛmar jar asen, \add xenni\add* aqa netta immeksi zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet \add n yixef\add* nnes, \add maca\add* Necc ad ttareɣ idammen nnes zeg ufus n uɛessas.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, Necc ggiɣ cek d aɛessas x taddart n Israil. Ad tesřed ijj n wawař zeg uqemmum inu uca ad asen tɛeřmed zzayi. \x ◘ \xo 33:7 \xt Ḥiz. 3:1enz.\x*  
\v 8 Umi Necc nniɣ i uɛeffan: ‘\add A\add* aɛeffan, cek ad temmted řmewt!’, u cek war tessiwiřed maḥend ad tɛeřmed i uɛeffan x webrid nnes \add iweddaren\add*, \add xenni\add* ad immet uɛeffan \add nni\add* s řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, \add maca\add* Necc ad ttareɣ idammen nnes zeg ufus nnec.  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* mařa cek tɛeřmed i uɛeffan x webrid nnes, maḥend ad as iḥeyyed uca netta war iḥeyyed x webrid nnes, \add xenni\add* netta ad immet s řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, \add maca\add* cek tessnejmed řeɛmar nnec.”   
\m
\v 10 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ini i taddart n Israil: ‘\add Ammu i\add* tessawařem, teqqarem: ‘Iɛeddiyyen nneɣ d ddnub nneɣ \add aqa aten\add* xaneɣ uca nhellek daysen, \add xenni\add* mammec ɣa \add neqqim\add* neddar?’ \x ◘ \xo 33:10 \xt Ḥiz. 24:23\x*  
\v 11 Ini asen: ‘\add S tidett am\add* ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, ɛemmarṣ war areṭṭiɣ x řmewt n uɛeffan, maca ad arḍeɣ aɛeffan xmi ɣa itub zeg webrid nnes uca ad iddar. Tubem, tubem zeg webriden nwem iɛeffnen, maɣar mayemmi ɣa temmted, \add a\add* taddart n Israil?’” \x ◘ \xo 33:11 \xt Ḥiz. 18:23, 32\x*   
\m
\v 12 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ini i tarwa n řgens nnec: ‘Tasegda n umsegged war t issnejjim deg wass nni di ɣa ixḍa uca tuɛeffna n uɛeffan war zzayes i ɣa inqareḍ deg wass nni di ɣa itub zi tuɛeffna nnes. Amsegged war izemmar ad iqqim iddar s tsegda nnes deg wass nni di ɣa ixḍa.\x ◘ \xo 33:12 \xt Ḥiz. 18:24\x*  
\v 13 Umi nniɣ Necc i umsegged, aqa netta ad iddar s tidett, \add maca\add* netta ittiqq di tsegda nnes uca igga řmuɛṣiyyet, \add xenni\add* war tᵉttiři ɛad řidaret di tsegda nnes, maca di řɣecc nnes nni igga, aqa ad dayes immet.  
\v 14 Mařa Necc nniɣ i uɛeffan: Řmewt i ɣa temmted!, uca netta itub x ddenb nnes uca ad igg řḥeqq d tsegda,  
\v 15 - aqa aɛeffan ad isseɛqeb ddiyyet nnes, ad ixeǧeṣ min ittwacaren, ad yuyur di tweṣṣa n tudart břa ma ad igg řɣecc - \add xenni\add* ad iddar s tidett, war ittmetti ca.  
\v 16 Marra ddnub nni igga, war dd as ttwaḥessben ca. Igga řḥeqq d tsegda, ad iddar s tidett.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 17 “Tarwa n řgens nnec qqaren: ‘Abrid n Sidi inu war iǧi ca nican!’, umi abrid n simant nsen war iǧi ca nican. \x ◘ \xo 33:17 \xt Ḥiz. 18:25, 29; 33:20\x*  
\v 18 Mařa amsegged iḥeyyed x tsegda nnes uca ittegg řɣecc, \add xenni\add* ad dayes immet,  
\v 19 uca xmi ɣa itub uɛeffan x tuɛeffna nnes uca ad igg řḥeqq d tsegda, \add xenni\add* ad zzayes iddar.  
\v 20 \add Ɛad\add* teqqarem: ‘Abrid n Sidi war iǧi ca nican!’ Necc ad xawem ḥekmeɣ, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, kuř ijj am yibriden nnes.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řexbar x uweṭṭu n Urcalim  
\m
\v 21 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss tenɛac n lmenfa nneɣ, deg uyur wiss ɛecra, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss xemsa n uyur\bd* imsar belli yusa-dd ɣari ijj n umarwař zi Urcalim, inna: “Tandint tᵉttwaɣelleb!”\x ◘ \xo 33:21 \xt 2 Ij. 25; Ḥiz. 24:26\x*  
\v 22 Ɣar ǧiřet tuɣa afus n SIDI xafi, qbeř dd ɣa yas umarwař u Netta yarzem ayi aqemmum umi dd-yusa umarwař ɣari di ṣṣbeḥ. Tuɣa aqemmum inu ittwarzem uca war ttiřiɣ ɛad d aynaw.   
\m
\v 23 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 24 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, imezdaɣ n řxirbat-a di temmurt n Israil ssawařen, qqaren: ‘Ibrahim tuɣa-t d ijj uca iwart tammurt-a. Neccin \add řexxu\add* deg waṭṭas, temmewc aneɣ temmurt d tasɣart!’  
\v 25 \bd S uya\bd*, ini asen: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Kenniw tᵉttetem \add aysum\add* ak-d idammen uca tessgeɛɛadem tiṭṭawin nwem ɣar imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nwem\add* uca tessizzařem idammen. Ma iɛeddeř ad tᵉṭṭfem kenniw tammurt d řwart? \x ◘ \xo 33:25 \xt Amz. 9:4; Lawi 3:17\x*  
\v 26 Tettbeddam x ssif nwem, tᵉtteggem jjɛifect u kuř aryaz issxemmaj tamɣart n jjar nnes. Ma iɛeddeř ad tᵉṭṭfem kenniw tammurt d řwart?’  
\v 27 Ammu i d asen ɣa tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: \add S tidett am\add* ddareɣ Necc, aqa inni iǧan x řxirbat ad wḍan s ssif, u wenni iǧan x wudem n yeyyar ad t wceɣ i řewḥuc n řexřa maḥend ad t ṣarḍen uca inni iǧan di lqelɛat u deg ifran ad mmten s ṭṭaɛun!  
\v 28 \add Maɣar\add* Necc ad arreɣ tammurt d areddeǧ d ijj n umedya n warjef uca nnfaxet n ṣṣulṭa nnes ad tᵉttwassbedd. Idurar n Israil ad ttwareddǧen ařami war din wi xasen i ɣa iẓwan.  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, xmi ɣa arreɣ tammurt d areddeǧ d ijj n umedya n warjef zi ssibbet n jjɛayef nsen nni ggin.’”   
\m
\v 30 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ayt n řgens nnec ssawařen xak ɣar řeḥyuḍ u ɣar wadaf n tudrin. Ijj issawař ak-d wenneɣni, kuř ijj ak-d umas, uca iqqar: ‘Asem-dd xenni uca sřem man awař i dd iffeɣ \add zeg uqemmum\add* n SIDI!’  
\v 31 Nitni ad ɣarek dd-asen am mammec i dd-yusa \add ijj n ubarru n\add* řgens, ad qqimen zzatek am řgens inu uca ad sřen i wawařen nnec, maca war zzaysen tteggen, maɣar s uqemmum nsen ssniɛmiřen tayri, maca uř nsen iggur awarni i řefḍeř n \add yixef\add* nsen. \x ◘ \xo 33:31 \xt Ḥiz. 14:1-3; 20:1-3\x*  
\v 32 Uca xzar, aqa cek ɣarsen am wenni ittɣennajen izřan s tmijja teṣbeḥ, \add amecnaw\add* wenni izemmaren ad igga \add lmusiqa\add* mliḥ. Nitni ad sřen ɣar wawařen nnec, \add maca\add* war zzaysen tteggen.  
\v 33 \add Maca\add* řami ad dd-yas aya - xzar, ad dd-yas! - \add xenni\add* ad ssnen belli tuɣa ijj n unabi di řwesṭ nsen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 34
\s1 SIDI d Ameksaw Aṣebḥan x řgens nnes  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, nabb ḍidd i imeksawen n Israil uca ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI! Uct x imeksawen n Israil nni yarekkwesen ixef nsen! Ma war ittxeṣṣi i imeksawen ad arewsen uǧi? \f ◼ \fr 34:2 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 34:2 \xt Irm. 23:1\x*  
\v 3 Kenniw tᵉttettem tadunt uca tarrḍem taḍuft, tɣarrṣem i řmař imessřen mliḥ, \add maca\add* war tarekkwisem uǧi.  
\v 4 War tessmeɛzem min iheyyfen, war tᵉttessgenfim min iḥeřcen, min ittwarẓin war t tceffnem, min iweddaren war t tᵉttarrim u min ixsaren war xas tarezzum, \add maca\add* s uqabu d ufus iqesḥen tḥekkmem xasen. \x ◘ \xo 34:4 \xt 1 Bṭ. 5:3\x*  
\v 5 \add Ammu i\add* ttwazuzzaren, minzi war din tuɣi bu umeksaw. Nitni dewřen d teymart n řewḥuc n barra nni iǧan di řexřa uca \add ammu i\add* ttwabezzɛen.  
\v 6 Uyuren weddaren uǧi inu x marra idurar u x kuř tawrirt yuɛřan, uǧi inu ttwabezzɛen x marra tammurt. War din wi \add xasen\add* i ɣa isseqsan uca war din wi \add xasen\add* yarezzun.’”   
\m
\v 7 “\bd S uya\bd*, \add a\add* imeksawen, sřem i wawař n SIDI:  
\v 8 ‘\add S tidett am\add* ddareɣ Necc, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, ma war \add ttiřiɣ\add* Necc \add xasen\add*? Minzi uǧi inu dewřen d taymart u uǧi inu dewřen d macca i řewḥuc n řexřa, umi war din iǧi umeksaw u minzi imeksawen inu war ttseqsan ca x wuǧi inu u umi imeksawen inu arewsen ixef nsen, war iǧi uǧi inu!’”   
\m
\v 9 “\bd S uya\bd*, \add a\add* imeksawen, sřem i wawař n SIDI!  
\v 10 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc aqa ayi ḍidd i imeksawen \add nni\add*! Necc ad ttareɣ uǧi inu zeg ufus nsen uca ad ten ssbeddeɣ zeg warwas n wuǧi, ařami imeksawen war yarekkwesen ɛad ixef nsen. Necc ad ssnejmeɣ uǧi inu zeg uqemmum nsen, ařami war d asen ttiřin ɛad d macca.’  
\v 11 Minzi ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad sseqsiɣ x wuǧi inu u ad xasen arzuɣ.  
\v 12 Am umeksaw ad issmun taḥimart nnes deg wass nni di yeǧa di řwest n wuǧi nnes ibezzɛen, amenni i ɣa \add y\add*arzuɣ Necc x wuǧi inu. Necc ad ten ssnejmeɣ zi marra imucan mani ttwabezzɛen, deg wass n iseynuten d taǧest.  
\v 13 Necc ad ten ssuffɣeɣ zi řegnus, ad ten ssmuneɣ zi temmura uca ad ten awyeɣ ɣar temmurt nsen. Necc ad ten arewseɣ x idurar n Israil, ɣar tɣezratin u di marra imucan i ittřiqen i tzeddiɣt di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 34:13 \xt Ḥiz. 28:25\x*  
\v 14 Necc ad ten arewseɣ x ict n ddemnet n tarewsa d taṣebḥant. X idurar yuɛřan n Israil ad yiři řmedweř n tarewsa nsen. Dinni ad areyyḥen deg ict n ddemnet n tarewsa taṣebḥant u ad arewsen deg ict n ddemnet n tarewsa d lemliḥ aṭṭas, x idurar n Israil.  
\v 15 Necc ad arewseɣ uǧi inu uca ad ten ssareyyḥeɣ!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 16 ‘Necc ad arzuɣ min ixsaren uca min iweddaren ad t arreɣ u min ittwarẓin ad t cefneɣ u min iheřcen ad t ssjehdeɣ, \add maca\add* min imessřen d min ijehden ad t areddǧeɣ. Necc ad ten arewseɣ s řḥeqq.  
\v 17 U kenniw, \add a\add* uǧi inu, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, xzar, Necc ad ḥekmeɣ jar ijjen zeg wuǧi d wuǧi nneɣni, jar icarriyyen d iɣayḍen.  
\v 18 Ma drust awem umi teccim ddemnet n tarewsa inu d taṣebḥant? Ma texsem \add xenni ɛawed\add* ad tɛefsem x min iqqimen i tarewsa s iḍaren nwem? Ma texsem ad teswem aman iṣfan uca \add xenni\add* ad tessarwyen min iqqimen s iḍaren nwem?  
\v 19 Ma ittxeṣṣa \add xenni\add* i wuǧi inu ad ccen min xef ɛefsen iḍaren nwem u ad swen min ssarwyen iḍaren nwem?’”   
\m
\v 20 “\bd S uya\bd* ammu i d asen iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad carrɛeɣ jar wuǧi imessřen d wuǧi ikkucḍen,  
\v 21 minzi marra uǧi iḍeɛfen tɛarnem i-ten s uɣezdis u s teɣruḍt u tessqarbem ten s waccawen nwem, ařami ten tbezzɛem di barra.  
\v 22 Necc ad ssnejmeɣ uǧi inu ařami war ttiřin ɛad i teymart u Necc ad carrɛeɣ jar ijjen zeg wuǧi d wuǧi nneɣni.  
\v 23 Necc ad xasen ssekkareɣ ijj n Umeksaw nni ten i ɣa yarewsen: Amsexxar inu Dawud. Netta ad ten yarwes u Netta ad asen yiři d Ameksaw. \x ◘ \xo 34:23 \xt Ica. 40:11; 42:1; 50:10; 52:13; 53:11; Irm. 30:9; Ḥiz. 20:35-38; Yḥ. 10:11\x*  
\v 24 Necc, SIDI, ad asen iřiɣ d AREBBI u Amsexxar inu Dawud ad yiři d Řḥakem di řwesṭ nsen, Necc, SIDI, aqa nniɣ t. \x ◘ \xo 34:24 \xt Ica. 55:4\x*  
\v 25 Necc ad ggeɣ ijj n Řɛahd n řehna akidsen uca ad kkseɣ řewḥuc iwɛaren zi temmurt. Nitni ad zedɣen di řexřa s řaman uca ad ṭṭṣen deg izeɣran. \f ◼ \fr 34:25 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  
\v 26 Ad ggeɣ min innḍen i wedrar inu d lbaraka u Necc ad dd-ssehwiɣ anẓar di řweqt nnes. Ad din yiři wenẓar aṭṭas s lbaraka.  
\v 27 Ticejjura n yeyyar ad wcent řɣiǧet nsent uca tammurt ad tewc ṣṣabet nnes uca nitni ad zedɣen di řaman di temmurt nsen. \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, xmi ɣa arẓeɣ imqeǧaden n zzayřet nsen uca ad ten qeřɛeɣ zeg ufus n yinni ten ijjin ad asen sexxaren.  
\v 28 War ttiřin ɛad d takeccaḍt i řegnus uca řewḥuc n temmurt war ten ṣarrḍen ɛad, \add maca\add* nitni ad zedɣen di řaman u war ten issnexřiɛ uřa d ijj.  
\v 29 Necc ad asen ssduqqzeɣ ijj n uɣemmuy, ad yiři i yijj n yisem \add icennɛen\add*. \add Xenni\add* war ttmeksin ɛad s řaẓ zi temmurt uca war arebbun ɛad řḥegra n řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 34:29 \xt Ḥiz. 36:6-38\x*  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc, SIDI AREBBI nsen, aqa ayi kidsen, uca nitni d řgens inu, taddart n Israil!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 31 Kenniw, \add a\add* uǧi inu, uǧi n řmedweř inu n tarewsa, kenniw d bnadem, \add maca\add* Necc d AREBBI nwem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 34:31 \xt Yḥ. 10:11\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 35
\s1 Aneqqam n SIDI x Idum  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, arr udem nnec ɣar idurar n Saɛir u nabb xas,  
\v 3 \add wah,\add* ini as: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI! Xzar, Necc \add ad\add* ɣarek \add dd-aseɣ\add*, \add a,\add* idurar n Saɛir uca ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd nnec uca ad cek arreɣ d tareddeǧt d řexřa.  
\v 4 Necc ad arreɣ tineddam nnec d řxarbet u cek ad tdewřed d tareddeǧt u cek ad tessned belli Necc d SIDI,  
\v 5 minzi ɣarek řeɛdawat ittduman u \add minzi\add* tsellmed ayt n Israil i tzemmar n ssif di řweqt n uḍeyyeɛ nsen, di řweqt n lḥisab aneggar x řmuɛṣiyyet.’” \x ◘ \xo 35:5 \xt Ḥiz. 25:15\x*   
\m
\v 6 “\bd S uya\bd*, \add s tidett am\add* ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Necc ad cek arreɣ d idammen \add qaɛ\add* u idammen ad cek ḍfaren. \add Wah\add* umi war tcarhed ca asizzeř n idammen, ad cek ḍfaren idammen.  
\v 7 Necc ad arreɣ idurar n Saɛir d tareddeǧt d řxarbet. Necc ad zzayes qesseɣ wi iɛeddun d wi dd-idekkwařen.  
\v 8 Necc ad ccureɣ idurar nnes s yinni ittwanɣen, tiwririn nnec d teɣzurtin nnec, \add wah,\add* inni ittwanɣen s ssif ad wḍan di marra tiɣezratin nnec.  
\v 9 Necc ad cek ggeɣ d tireddeǧin i řebda u tineddam nnec ɛemmarṣ war daysent ttwifen \add ɛad\add* imezdaɣ u kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI,  
\v 10 minzi tennid: Tnayen n řegnus nni d tnayen n temmura nni ad iřint inu u neccin ad tent ṭṭfen d řwart!, \add am\add* SIDI aqa-t din.’” \x ◘ \xo 35:10 \xt Izhd. 83:13\x*   
\m
\v 11 “\bd S uya\bd*, \add s tidett am\add* ddareɣ Necc, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Necc ad ac ggeɣ anect n weɣḍab nnec u anect n tusmi nnec nni tuɣa ɣarek deg wecrah nnec zzaysen, \add maca\add* nitni ad ayi ssnen xmi xak ɣa ḥekmeɣ.  
\v 12 Ad tessned, belli Necc, SIDI, sřiɣ i marra aceqqaf nnec nni tessiwřed ḍidd i idurar n Israil, tennid: Aqa twareddǧen, mmewcen aneɣ d macca.  
\v 13 \add Ammu i\add* xafi tqeřbem s uqemmum nwem iccur s ukebbar uca tarnim tfarrɣem awařen nwem xafi aṭṭas. Necc sřiɣ t.’  
\v 14 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Am tfarreḥ marra tammurt, Necc ad cek arreɣ d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen.  
\v 15 Am mammec tfarḥed s tesɣart n taddart n Israil, minzi aqa tᵉttwareddeǧ, Necc ad kik ggeɣ ammu, \add a kenniw,\add* idurar n Saɛir, \add cem\add* marra \add tammurt\add* n Idum, ad tiřid d tareddeǧt! Uca nitni ad ssnen, belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 36
\s1 Asizdeg d ureqqeɛ n Israil  
\m
\v 1 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, nabb i idurar n Israil, ini: ‘Idurar n Israil, sřem i wawař n SIDI!\x ◘ \xo 36:1 \xt Ḥiz. 6:2\x*  
\v 2 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Minzi řeɛdu inna xawem: Iya, aqa řegɛudi n řebda dewřent aneɣ d tasɣart! ... \x ◘ \xo 36:2 \xt Ḥiz. 35:10\x*   
\m
\v 3 ... \bd s uya\bd* nabb, ini: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Minzi areddǧen u ṣarḍen kenniw zi marra iɣezdisen, ḥima ad tdewřem d tasɣart n min iqqimen n řegnus u \add minzi\add* tᵉttwassekkaren xawem awařen uca tdewřem i uceqqaf jar řgens,   
\m
\v 4 ... \bd s uya\bd*, idurar n Israil, sřem i wawař n Sidi inu, SIDI! Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, i idurar d tewririn, i tɣezratin d řwaṭat, i řxirbat ttwareddǧent u i tneddam i ijjin, tinni idewřen i tkeccaḍt d řḥegra i min iqqimen n řegnus nni dd awem dd-innḍen,   
\m
\v 5 ... \bd s uya\bd*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: S tidett, aqa di tmessi n tusmi inu \add iqeddsen\add* ssiwřeɣ ḍidd i min iqqimen n řegnus u ḍidd i marra \add tammurt\add* n Idum, inni iwcin tammurt inu d tasɣart i yixef nsen, s řefraḥet n wuř marra, s řeɛmar \add iccuren\add* s useḥqar, maḥend ddmani n tarewsa ad asen iřint d takeccaḍt!   
\m
\v 6 ... \bd s uya\bd*, nabb ḍidd i temmurt n Israil uca ini i idurar d tewririn u i tɣezratin d řwaṭat: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, xzar, Necc siwřeɣ di tusmi inu \add iqeddsen\add* u deg wesɛar inu, minzi kenniw aqa tarbum řḥegra n řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 36:6 \xt Ḥiz. 34:29\x*   
\m
\v 7 ... \bd s uya\bd*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu, \add ẓuǧeɣ\add*: S tidett, řegnus i d awem dd-innḍen ad arbun řḥegra s yixef nsen!  
\v 8 \add Maca\add* kenniw, idurar n Israil, ad tewcem \add ɛawed\add* řefruɛ nwem uca ad dd-tawyem řɣiǧet nwem i řgens inu Israil, minzi ɛřaḥař ad dd-asen.  
\v 9 Maɣar xzar, Necc \add ad iřiɣ\add* akidwem uca Necc ad ɣarwem nqeřbeɣ u kenniw, \add a idurar\add*, ad xawem carzen \add ɛawed\add* u ad xawem zarrɛen.  
\v 10 Necc ad arniɣ iwdan xawem, marra taddart n Israil, \add wah,\add* marra nettat, uca ad sszedɣen tineddam u ad bnan řxirbat \add ɛawed\add*.  
\v 11 Ad xawem arniɣ iwdan d řmař u nitni ad arnin deg yixef nsen u ad dd-jjen řɣiǧet u Necc ad kenniw sszedɣeɣ \add din\add* ɛawed, am deg wussan n wecḥař uya, \add wah,\add* Necc ad arreɣ řḥař ḥsen x umezwar nwem u kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.  
\v 12 Ad jjeɣ iwdan ad xawem uyuren: řgens inu Israil. Nitni ad cek ṭṭfen d řwart, \add a řgens inu\add*, u kenniw, \add a idurar n Israil,\add* ad asen tiřim d řwart, u kenniw war tᵉttkeccaḍem ɛad arraw \add nsen\add*.  
\v 13 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Minzi qqaren awem: Cem tᵉtted iwdan u cem d \add ict n temmurt\add* i ittkeccaḍen arraw n řgens nnem! ...   
\m
\v 14 ... \bd s uya\bd* war tecced ɛad iwdan u war tessneqraḍed ɛad řgens nnem!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 15 Necc ad ggeɣ ɛemmarṣ ad tᵉttwaseř ɛad řḥegra n řegnus xam u war tkessid ɛad astehzi n řegnus u war tessneqraḍed ɛad řgens nnem!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 17 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, \add umi\add* tuɣa taddart n Israil tzeddeɣ di temmurt nnes, aqa ssxemmjen tt s webrid nsen d tmegga nsen. Abrid nsen tuɣa-t am řexmej n temɣart i x ǧan idammen \add deg wussan n\add* weɛzař \add nnes\add*.  
\v 18 Necc ssfarrɣeɣ xasen asɛar inu zi ssibbet n idammen nni ssizzřen x temmurt u zi ssibbet n imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nsem\add* i zi tt ssxemjen.  
\v 19 Nexx ssbezzɛeɣ ten jar řegnus u nitni ttwassuysen di temmura. Necc ḥekmeɣ xasen ɛlaḥsab tuyurt nsen u ɛlaḥsab řexdayem nsen.  
\v 20 \add Umi\add* iwḍen ɣar řegnus mani tuɣa uyuren, ssfeḍḥen Isem iqeddsen inu, minzi ittwanna xasen: ‘Ina d řgens n SIDI, \add maca\add* tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad ffɣen zi temmurt nnes.’ \x ◘ \xo 36:20 \xt Ica. 52:5; Rum. 2:24\x*  
\v 21 Maca Necc ssɛizzeɣ ten di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu iqeddsen nni tessefḍeḥ taddart n Israil jar řegnus mani tuɣa uyuren nitni ...   
\m
\v 22 ... \bd s uya\bd*, ini i taddart n Israil: Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: War tt tteggeɣ di ṭṭweɛ nwem, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, maca di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu iqeddsen nni tessfeḍḥem kenniw jar řegnus mani tuɣa tuyurem.  
\v 23 Maɣar ad ssqeddseɣ Isem inu imɣaren nni tessfeḍḥem di řwest nsen, uca řegnus ad ssnen aqa Necc d SIDI, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, xmi ɣa ttwaqeddseɣ daywem zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen.  
\v 24 Minzi ad kenniw ksiɣ zi řegnus, ad kenniw ssmuneɣ zi marra timmura uca ad kenniw awyeɣ ɣar temmurt nwem.  
\v 25 Ad xawem zeǧɛeɣ aman izdigen uca ad ttwassizdegem. Necc ad kenniw ssizdegeɣ zi marra řexmujat nwem u zi marra imeyḍa nwem \add n l’aṣnam\add*.  
\v 26 Ad awem wceɣ uř n jdid u ad ggeɣ buḥbeř amaynu di daxeř nwem uca ad kkseɣ zi arrimet nwem uř n weẓru uca ad awem wceɣ uř n weysum. \x ◘ \xo 36:26 \xt Irm. 32:39; Ḥiz. 11:19\x*  
\v 27 Ad ggeɣ Arruḥ inu di daxeř nwem u ad arreɣ kenniw ad teggem tiweṣṣa inu u ad teḥḍam lfarayiḍ inu u ad zzaysent teggem.  
\v 28 Ad tzedɣem di temmurt nni wciɣ i řejdud nwem, uca kenniw ad tiřim d řgens inu uca Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nwem.  
\v 29 Necc ad kenniw ssnejmeɣ zi marra řexmujat nwem. Ad řaɣiɣ i imendi uca ad dayes arniɣ aṭṭas u war d awem tticeɣ řaẓ. \x ◘ \xo 36:29 \xt Ḥiz. 34:29\x*  
\v 30 Ad arniɣ \add amenni\add* řɣiǧet n tcejjura u n yeyyar, ḥima war xawem tekk ɛad řḥegra n řaẓ jar řegnus.  
\v 31 \add Xenni\add* ad tidarem deg ibriden nwem iɛeffnen d tmegga nwem war iṣebḥen u kenniw ad tɛiffem zeg yixef nwem u zi jjɛayef nwem. \x ◘ \xo 36:31 \xt Ḥiz. 6:9; 20:43; 16:61, 63\x*  
\v 32 \add Maca\add* war tt tteggeɣ di ṭṭweɛ nwem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, snem tt mliḥ! Seḍḥam u ssnem řefḍiḥet n ibriden nwem, \add a\add* taddart n Israil.”   
\m
\v 33 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ssizedgeɣ marra řmuɛṣiyyat nwem, ad sszedɣeɣ tineddam \add ɛawed\add* uca ad bniɣ \add ɛawed\add* řxirbat.  
\v 34 Tammurt ittwareddǧen ad tᵉttwacarz deg wemcan i ɣa tiři tᵉttwareddeǧ zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra inni tt iẓekkwan.  
\v 35 Ad inin: Tammurt nni tuɣa tᵉttwareddeǧ, tedweř am jjennet n Ɛadn u tineddam ttwaxarrabent d ttwareddǧent d ttwahedment, aqa ttwassjehdent u zeddɣen daysent imezdaɣ \add ɛawed\add*. \x ◘ \xo 36:35 \xt Ica. 51:3; Ḥiz. 28:13\x*  
\v 36 \add Xenni\add* ad ssnen řegnus nni iqqimen deg wenneḍ nwem, aqa Necc, SIDI, ad bniɣ min ittwahedmen \add ɛawed\add* u ad ẓẓuɣ x min ittwareddǧen. Necc, SIDI, ssiwřeɣ u Necc ad t ggeɣ.’” \x ◘ \xo 36:36 \xt Ḥiz. 17:24; 22:14; 37:14\x*   
\m
\v 37 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Ad ayi tᵉttar taddart n Israil uřa d man aya ḥima ad asen t ggeɣ. Necc ad daysen arniɣ \add iwdan\add*, \add ařami ad din iřin\add* anect n iwdan am wuǧi.  
\v 38 Anect iǧan n wuǧi iqeddsen am wuǧi i ccuren \add tandint n\add* Urcalim di řeɛyudat nnes ittwaggen, ammu i ɣa iřint tneddam ittwareddǧen ccurent s wuǧi d iwdan u nitni ad ssnen aqa Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 37
\s1 Tanukra n Israil  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa ufus n SIDI xafi uca SIDI issuffeɣ ayi-dd di Arruḥ uca issars ayi di řwesṭ n řewḍa nni tuɣa yeccuren s iɣsan.  
\v 2 Netta indeh ayi deg wenneḍ nnes, u xzar, aqa din aṭṭas s waṭṭas \add n iɣsan\add* x wudem n řewḍa, u xzar, aqa aten uẓɣen aṭṭas.  
\v 3 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ma ad ddaren iɣsan-a \add ɛawed\add*?” Nniɣ necc: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, SIDI, Cek tessned \add t\add*!”  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Nabb x yeɣsan-a, ini asen: ‘\add A\add* iɣsan uẓɣen, sřem i wawař n SIDI.  
\v 5 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, i iɣsan-a: Xzar, Necc ad daywem ssidfeɣ buḥbeř uca ad teddarem \add ɛawed\add*.  
\v 6 Ad xawem ggeɣ iẓewran u ad xawem ssgeɛɛdeɣ aysum uca ad kenniw dřeɣ s iřem uca ad daywem ggeɣ buḥbeř, ad teddarem \add ɛawed\add*. \add Xenni\add* ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 7 \add Řami\add* tuɣa ttnabbeɣ am mammec d ayi ittwaweṣṣa, uca tuɣa \add din\add* ijj n řḥess řami tuɣa ttnabbeɣ, u xzar, \add aqa da\add* ict n tarjijit uca iɣsan munen, \add kuř\add* iɣes ak-d iɣes nnes.  
\v 8 Ẓřiɣ, u xzar, aqa dewřen xasen-dd iẓewran u yuři xasen weysum u Netta idřa i-ten s yiřem sennej nsen, \add maca\add* war daysen tuɣi \add ɛad\add* buḥbeř.  
\v 9 Netta inna ayi: “Nabb i Arruḥ, nabb, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, uca ini i Arruḥ: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: As-dd zi arebɛa n tɣemmura n usemmiḍ, \add a\add* Arruḥ, u suḍ deg ina inni ittwanɣen, \add ḥima\add* ad ddaren.’”  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* nabbeɣ am mammec i d ayi ittwaweṣṣa. Uca yudef Arruḥ daysen uca ddaren \add ɛawed\add* uca \add kkaren\add* bedden x iḍaren nsen, \add aqa\add* d ijj n řɛeskar d ameqqran aṭṭas s waṭṭas.   
\m
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, iɣsan-a \add aqa aten\add* marra taddart n Israil. Xzar, nitni qqaren: ‘iɣsan nneɣ uẓɣen uca řayas nneɣ iweddar u neccin nettwaqḍeɛ!’  
\v 12 \bd S uya\bd*, nabb, ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad arzmeɣ imeḍřan nwem, ad kenniw ssgeɛɛdeɣ zeg imeḍřan nwem, \add a\add* řgens inu, u Necc ad kenniw awyeɣ x wudem n temmurt n Israil.  
\v 13 Kenniw ad tessnem, belli Necc d SIDI, umi arzmeɣ imeḍřan nwem uca ssuffɣeɣ-dd kenniw zeg imeḍřan nwem, \add a\add* řgens inu.  
\v 14 Necc ad ggeɣ Arruḥ inu daywem \add di daxeř nwem\add* u kenniw ad teddarem \add ɛawed\add* u Necc ad kenniw ssarseɣ x wudem n temmurt nwem u kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc, SIDI, ssiwřeɣ uca ggiɣ \add t\add*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Asmuni n Israil d Yahuda  
\m
\v 15 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 16 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ksi ijj n uzeǧaḍ \add n ukeccuḍ\add* uca ari dayes: ‘I Yahuda u i arraw n Israil, imɛacaren nnes!’ Ksi awarni as azeǧaḍ nneɣni uca ari dayes: ‘I Yusuf, azeǧad n Ifrayim, u \add i\add* marra taddart n Israil, imeddukkař nnes!’  
\v 17 Smun ten xenni ijj ak-d wenneɣni, \add egg zzaysen\add* ijj n uzeǧaḍ i cek. Ad dewřen d ijj deg ufus nnec.   
\m
\v 18 Xmi kik i ɣa issiwřen tarwa n řgens nnec, ad inin: ‘Ma war texsed ad aneɣ tessecned min ixs ad inint tmesřayin-a i cek?’,  
\v 19 ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad ksiɣ azeǧaḍ n Yusuf, wenni iǧan deg ufus n Ifrayim, \add azeǧaḍ\add* n tqebbař n Israil, imɛacaren nnes, uca ad ten ssmuneɣ ak-d uzeǧaḍ n Yahuda uca ad ten ggeɣ d ijj n uzeǧaḍ uca ad dewřen d ijj deg ufus inu.’  
\v 20 Izeǧaḍen zeg ukeccuḍ i x turid, \add ad iřin\add* deg ufus nnec zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen.  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad ṭṭfeɣ ayt n Israil zi řwest n řegnus mani ɣar uyuren uca ad ten ssmuneɣ zeg wenneḍ uca ad ten awyeɣ ɣar wudem n temmurt nsen.  
\v 22 Necc ad ten ggeɣ d ijj n řgens di temmurt, x idurar n Israil, d ijj n Ujeǧid ad yiři i marra idsen d Ajeǧid uca ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad iřin i tnayen n řegnus u ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad ttwabḍan di tnayen n tgeldiwin. \x ◘ \xo 37:22 \xt Yḥ. 10:16\x*  
\v 23 War ssxemmajen ɛad ixef nsen s imeyḍa nsen n l’aṣnam, s nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam u s řmuɛṣiyyat nsen. Necc ad ten ssnejmeɣ zi marra tineddam nsen i di xḍin nitni u Necc ad ten ssizedgeɣ. \add Xenni\add* nitni ad ayi iřin d řgens u Necc ad asen iřiɣ d AREBBI.  
\v 24 Amsexxar inu Dawud ad xasen yiři d ajeǧid uca ad din yiři ijj n Umeksaw i marra nitni. Nitni ad ḍfaren lfarayiḍ inu uca ad ḥḍan tiweṣṣa inu, ad zzaysent ggen. \f ◼ \fr 37:24 \ft \+fk Ameksaw\ft  - niɣ ‘Aniči’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 37:24 \xt Ica. 40:11; Irm. 30:9; Ḥiz. 34:23\x*  
\v 25 Ad zedɣen di temmurt nni wciɣ i umsexxar inu Yaɛqub, i di tuɣa zeddɣen řejdud nwem, \add wah,\add* nitni ad dayes zedɣen i řebda, nitni d iḥenjiren nsen d iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nsen, uca Amsexxar inu Dawud ad yiři d Řḥakem nsen i řebda.  
\v 26 Necc ad kidsen qeḍɛeɣ ijj n Řɛahd n řehna, ad yiři d Řɛahd i řebda. Necc ad ten barkeɣ u ad daysen arniɣ aṭṭas u Necc ad ggeɣ Zzawect inu Iqeddsen di řwesṭ nsen i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 37:26 \xt Izhd. 89:4; Ḥiz. 34:25; 2 Kur. 6:16\x*  
\v 27 Ad ɣarsen tiři Tzeddiɣt inu u Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nsen u nitni ad iřin d řgens inu, \x ◘ \xo 37:27 \xt Ḥiz. 11:20; 14:11\x*  
\v 28 uca ad ssnen řegnus, belli Necc d SIDI nni issqeddsen Israil xmi ɣa tiři Zzawect inu Iqeddsen di řwesṭ nsen i řebda.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 38
\s1 Ahjam n Hajuj  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, arr udem nnec ɣar \add Ha\add*juj \add zi\add* temmurt n Majuj, řḥakem n Ruc, Macik d Tubal, uca nabb ḍidd nnes, \f ◼ \fr 38:2 \ft \+fk Hajuj\ft  - niɣ ‘Juj’, niɣ ‘Xux’, niɣ ‘Gug’. \fk Majuj\ft  - niɣ ‘Maxux’, niɣ ‘Magug’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 38:2 \xt Asa. 20:8\x*  
\v 3 ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, Necc aqa ayi ḍidd nnec, \add a\add* \add Ha\add*juj, řḥakem n Ruc, Macik d Tubal.  
\v 4 Necc ad cek qemmɛeɣ u ad ggeɣ tisennarin deg iqabsiwen nnec uca ad cek ssuffɣeɣ, cek d marra řɛeskar nnec, iysan d imnayen, marra arḍen arruḍ mliḥ aṭṭas, ijj n wegraw d ameqqran aṭṭas, s tseddart tameqqrant d tseddart tameẓyant \add n uɛeskari\add*, marra nitni ɣarsen tizemmar deg umenɣi s ssif. \x ◘ \xo 38:4 \xt Ḥiz. 29:4; 39:2\x*  
\v 5 Ayt n Lfurs, n Kuc u n Fuṭ akidsen, marra idsen s tseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* d lkask \add n uɛeskari\add*,  
\v 6 Jumar ak-d marra řɛeskar nnes, d taddart n Tujarma zi ṭṭrufa n ccamal qaɛ ak-d marra řɛeskar nnes, \add wah,\add* aṭṭas n řegnus \add ad dd-asen\add* akidek.  
\v 7 Iři twejded u sewjed ixef nnec, cek d marra agraw nnec nni tessmuned ɣarek, u iři d ameḥḍay nsen.  
\v 8 Awarni waṭṭas n wussan ad tᵉttwařaɣid, awarni řami ɛdun aṭṭas n iseggʷusa ad dd-tased ɣar temmurt nni ittwaɛedřen zi ssif, \add ɣar ijj n řgens\add* i ittwassmunen zi řegnus x idurar n Israil nni tuɣa d řxirbet i yijj n řweqt d azirar, \add ɣar ijj n řgens\add* nni ittwassuffɣen zi řegnus, u marra nitni zeddɣen \add dinni\add* di řaman.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ad tgeɛɛded am tḥaryaḍt, am useynu maḥend ad tedřed tammurt, cek d marra řɛeskar nnec uřa d aṭṭas n řegnus nni kik \add iǧan\add*.’”\x ◘ \xo 38:9 \xt Ḥiz. 30:18\x*   
\m
\v 10 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar, aqa ad adfen ixarriṣen deg wuř nnec u cek ad txarrṣed di tmeɛmuč taɛeffant.  
\v 11 Ad tinid: Ad geɛɛdeɣ ɣar ict n temmurt s tneddam břa řeḥyuḍ, ad dd-aseɣ ɣar \add yenni din\add* iddaren di řehna u \add ɣar yinni din\add* izeddɣen di řaman, inni din izeddɣen marra břa řḥiḍ u břa zzekrunat niɣ tiwwura,  
\v 12 maḥend ad keccḍeɣ u ad acareɣ agřa! \add Wah,\add* maḥend ad tarred afus nnec x řxirbat nni di zeddɣen \add ɛawed iwdan\add*, x yijj n řgens nni ittwassmunen zi řegnus, wenni ikesben řmař d wagřa, wenni izeddɣen x tɛebbuḍt n temmurt.  
\v 13 Caba d Dadan d ttujar n Tarcic d marra ayraden imeẓyanin nsen ad ac inin: Ma dd-tusid maḥend ad tᵉṭṭfed takeccaḍt? Ma tessmuned agraw nnec maḥend ad tkeccḍed, ḥima ad teksid nnuqart d wureɣ, ḥima ad tᵉṭṭfed řmař d wagřa, ḥima ad tacared takeccaḍt tameqqrant?’”   
\m
\v 14 “\bd S uya\bd*, nabb, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, uca ini i \add Ha\add*juj ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: \bd Deg wass nni\bd*, xmi ɣa izdeɣ řgens inu Israil di řaman, ma cek war tessined \add min ittxeṣṣa ad t tegged\add*?  
\v 15 Ad dd-tased zeg wemcan nnec, zi ṭṭrufa n ccamal qaɛ, cek d waṭṭas n řegnus akidek. Marra nitni d imnayen s iysan, ijj n wegraw d ameqqran d yijj n řɛeskar ijehden.  
\v 16 Ad tgeɛɛded ḍidd i řgens inu Israil, am yijj n useynu, maḥend ad tedřed tammurt. Ad yiři deg uneggar n wussan. Necc ad cek ssiwḍeɣ x temmurt inu, ḥima řegnus ad ayi ssnen, xmi zzayek i ɣa ttwaqeddseɣ zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, \add a\add* \add Ha\add*juj!’  
\v 17 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Ma aqa cek d wenni x ssiwřeɣ deg wussan n zic, s ufus n imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen n Israil nni tuɣa ittnabben deg wussan nni, \add řmijař n\add* waṭṭas n iseggʷusa, belli Necc ad cek ssiwḍeɣ ḍidd nsen?  
\v 18 \bd Deg wass nni\bd*, deg wass i di dd ɣa yas \add Ha\add*juj ḍidd i temmurt n Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, aqa ad yaři wesɛar inu deg wenzaren inu.  
\v 19 Di tusmi inu \add iqeddsen\add*, di tmessi n uduqqez inu \add n ufugem\add* nniɣ: \add S tidett, am ddareɣ Necc\add*, mařa \bd deg wass nni\bd* war ittiři ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt ameqqran di temmurt n Israil, \x ◘ \xo 38:19 \xt Ḥiz. 36:5, 6; Asa. 16:18\x*  
\v 20 \add ařami\add* iseřman n řebḥar d ijḍaḍ n ujenna d řmař n yeyyar d marra řmař nni ittbuɛen x temmurt d marra iwdan nni \add iǧan\add* x wudem n temmurt ad arjijen, u idurar ad ttwamenḍaren u řejruf iɛuǧen ad hruran d marra řeḥyuḍ ad wḍan. \f ◼ \fr 38:20 \ft \+fk řebḥar\ft  - niɣ ‘il’.\f*  
\v 21 Necc ad dd-řaɣiɣ x ssif ḍidd nnes x marra idurar inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI. Ssif n kuř ijj ad yiři x umas.  
\v 22 Necc ad xas ḥekmeɣ s ṭṭaɛun u s idammen uca ad xas ggeɣ u x řɛeskar nnes u x waṭṭas n řegnus nni kides i ɣa yiřin, anẓar ijehden d ibquqen imeqqranen n tebruri d tmessi d řecbariyyet. \x ◘ \xo 38:22 \xt Asa. 16:20.\x*  
\v 23 Necc ad ssecneɣ Ixef inu d ameqqran d amqeddas u ad ttwassneɣ zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus. Nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 39
\s1 Taɣarṣt tameqqrant x idurar n Israil  
\m
\v 1 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, nabb ḍidd i \add Ha\add*juj uca ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, aqa ayi xak, \add a, cek\add* \add Ha\add*juj, řḥakem n Ruc, Macik d Tubal. \f ◼ \fr 39:1 \ft \+fk Hajuj\ft  - niɣ ‘Juj’, niɣ ‘Xux’, niɣ ‘Gug’.\f*  
\v 2 Necc ad cek ssɛeqbeɣ u ad dayek ggeɣ tisennarin u ad cek ssgeɛɛdeɣ zi ṭṭrufa n ccamal uca ad cek gewwdeɣ x idurar n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 39:2 \xt Ḥiz. 29:4; 38:4\x*  
\v 3 Ad wteɣ řqews zeg ufus nnec azeřmaḍ uca ad ɣeḍřeɣ fřitcat nnec zeg ufus nnec afusi.  
\v 4 Ad tewḍid x idurar n Israil, cek d marra řɛeskar nnec d řegnus nni \add iǧan\add* akidek. Necc wciɣ cek d macca i ɛřam kuř ijḍaḍ ittkeccaḍen u i řmař n řexřa. \x ◘ \xo 39:4 \xt Ḥiz. 33:27\x*  
\v 5 X wudem n yeyyar ad tewḍid, minzi Necc nniɣ t, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 6 Necc ad ssekkeɣ timessi x Majuj u x inni izeddɣen s řeḥna di tegzirin u nitni ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 39:6 \ft \+fk Majuj\ft  - niɣ ‘Maxux’, niɣ ‘Magug’.\f*  
\v 7 Necc ad ssbaneɣ Isem inu iqeddsen di řwest n řgens Israil u Necc war ttejjiɣ ɛad ad ssxemjen Isem inu iqeddsen. Řegnus ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, Amqeddas di Israil.  
\v 8 Xzar, ad dd-yas u ad imsar!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI. Wa d ass nni x ssiwřeɣ.’”   
\m
\v 9 “Imezdaɣ n tneddam n Israil ad ffɣen uca ad ssarɣen timessi ad sscemḍen \add marra\add* řesnaḥ: am tseddariyin timeẓyanin am tseddariyin timeqqranin uřa d řqews d fřitcat d iɛumad i yifassen d iḥricen. \bd Sebɛa n iseggʷusa\bd* ad zzaysen ssarɣen timessi.  
\v 10 War dd-ttiwyen akeccuḍ zeg iyyar u war ttqessin tafřawt zeg izeɣran, \add minzi\add* ssarɣen timessi s řesnah uca ad keccḍen inni ten ikeccḍen uca ad acaren i yinni d asen yucaren!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”\f ◼ \fr 39:10 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*   
\m
\v 11 \bd “Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar, aqa Necc ad sswejdeɣ din amcan i \add Ha\add*juj ijj n wenḍeř di Israil, Řewḍa n yinni iẓekkwan, ɣar ccarq n řebḥar, u tanita ad tbelleɛ \add abrid\add* i yinni \add ixsen\add* ad ẓekkwan. Din i ɣa neḍřen \add Ha\add*juj d marra řɣaci nnes inhewřen u ad xas řaɣan: Řewḍa n Řɣaci Inhewřen n \add Ha\add*juj.  
\v 12 Taddart n Israil ad ten tenḍeř, maḥend ad ssizdegen temmurt, \add řmijař n\add* sebɛa n iyuren.  
\v 13 Marra řgens n temmurt ad \add ten\add* neḍřen uca aya ad asen yiři i ccan, deg wass i di ɣa ttwassɛuǧeɣ!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.\f ◼ \fr 39:13 \ft \+fk aya ad asen yiři i ccan\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘uca (aya) ad asen yiři i yisem’.\f*  
\v 14 ‘Ad farzen ɛawed iryazen maḥend ad ẓwan nitni tammurt břa qeṭṭu maḥend ad neḍřen inni xas ikkin, inni tuɣa iqqimen buzzřen x wudem n temmurt, ḥima ad ssizedgen \add tammurt\add*. Awarni sebɛa n iyuren ad qeǧben nitni.  
\v 15 Inni i d asen ittxeṣṣa ad ẓwan tammurt ad tt ẓwan u xmi ittwařa ḥed ijj n yiɣes n bnadem, ad yegg ɣares ict n řmarka ař t ɣa neḍřen inni ineṭṭařen di Řewḍa n Řɣaci Inhewřen n \add Ha\add*juj.  
\v 16 Ɛawed \add ad yiři\add* isem n ict n tendint ‘Řɣaci Inhewřen’. Nitni ad sizedgen tammurt.’”   
\m
\v 17 “Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Ini i marra řmarkat n ijḍaḍ u i marra řmař n yeyyar: Munem-dd \add da\add*, asem-dd, seddem ixef nwem zeg wenneḍ ɣar tɣarṣt inu nni ɣarṣeɣ i kenniw, taɣarṣt tameqqrant x idurar n Israil, uca ad teccem aysum, ad teswem idammen.  
\v 18 Ad teccem aysum n ayt n bu-řexcunet u ad teswem idammen n řḥukkam n ddunect, n icarriyyen d izmaren d iɣayḍen d ifunasen imeẓyanen, aqa aten marra dewsen di Basan.  
\v 19 Ad teccem tadunt ař ɣa tejjiwnem uca ad teswem idammen ař ɣa tescarem zi tɣarṣt inu i ɣarṣeɣ i kenniw.  
\v 20 Kenniw ad tejjiwnem ɣar ṭṭabřa inu s iysan d imnayen, s ayt n bu-teɣruḍt u s marra iɛeskariyyen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 21 Ad ggeɣ aɛuǧi inu jar řegnus uca marra řegnus ad ẓaren řḥukm inu nni ggiɣ, uřa d afus nni jar asen ssarseɣ.  
\v 22 Taddart n Israil ad tessen, aqa Necc, SIDI, d AREBBI nsen, zeg wass nni u zi ssa tsawent.  
\v 23 Ad ssnen řegnus aqa inni n taddart n Israil ttwanedhen di lmenfa zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet nsen, minzi ɣeddaren ayi uca Necc ffareɣ xasen udem inu uca wciɣ ten deg ufus n iɣrimen nsen u \add xenni\add* wḍan marra s ssif.  
\v 24 Necc ggiɣ asen am mammec taxmuji nsen u am mammec řmuɛṣiyyet nsen u Necc ffareɣ zzaysen udem inu.’”   
\m
\v 25 “\bd S uya\bd*, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Řexxu ad ssɛeqbeɣ imeḥbas n Yaɛqub, ad ḥinneɣ x marra taddart n Israil. Ad usmeɣ di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu iqeddsen.  
\v 26 Nitni ad arbun řefḍiḥet nsen d marra řmuɛṣiyyet nsen i zi d ayi ɣḍaren xmi nitni ɛad zedɣen di řaman di temmurt nsen u war iǧi wi ten i ɣa issiggʷeden.  
\v 27 Xmi ten i ɣa ssɛeqbeɣ zi řegnus u ad ten ssmuneɣ zi temmura n řɛedyan nsen u Necc ad ttwaqeddseɣ zzaysen zzat i tiṭṭawin n waṭṭas n řegnus,  
\v 28 \add xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nsen, minzi Necc nedheɣ ten d imeḥbas jar řegnus u Necc ssmuneɣ ten \add ɛawed\add* di temmurt nsen, war \add din\add* jjiɣ uřa d ijjen zzaysen.  
\v 29 Necc war xasen tteffareɣ ɛad udem inu, xmi aqa ssfarrɣeɣ Arruḥ inu x taddart n Israil!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 39:29 \xt Yuw. 3:1; Řex. 2:17\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 40
\s1 Tiwwura d řemraḥat n Zzawect Tameqqrant n jdid  
\m
\v 1 \bd Deg useggʷas wiss xemsa u-ɛicrin n lmenfa nneɣ, ɣar umezwar n useggʷas, deg \+bdit wass\+bdit* wiss ɛecra n uyur, deg useggʷas wiss arbeɛṭac awarni ma wtin tandint, deg wass nni \+bdit nnit\+bdit*\bd*, tuɣa afus n SIDI xafi uca indeh ayi din. \x ◘ \xo 40:1 \xt Ḥiz. 33:21\x*  
\v 2 Di iweḥḥan n AREBBI indeh ayi ɣar temmurt n Israil uca issars ayi x \bd ijj n wedrar yuɛřan mixef tuɣa ca n řebni am yict n tendint ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub nnes\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 40:2 \xt Ḥiz. 20:40; Ḥiz. 43:12\x*  
\v 3 Yiwyi ayi din, u xzar, ijj n weryaz. Ṣṣifet nnes am ṣṣifet n nnḥas u deg ufus nnes ijj n ufiřu n řeqṭen d ijj n uɣanim n řeɛbar. Netta tuɣa ibedd ɣar tewwart.  
\v 4 Issiweř akidi weryaz \add nni\add*: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, xzar s tiṭṭawin nnec, seř s imezzuɣen nnec uca sars uř nnec i marra nni i d ac ɣa ssecneɣ, maɣar tᵉttwassqebded ɣar da ḥima ad ac t ssecneɣ. Marra min twařid, ini t i taddart n Israil!”   
\b  
\m
\v 5 Xzar, \bd ɣar barra n Taddart tuɣa din ijj n weɣbar\bd* nni tuɣa i d as dd-innḍen kuřci. Deg ufus n weryaz tuɣa d ijj n uɣanim n řeɛbar n setta n iɣaǧen, \add kuř ijjen zzaysen d\add* ijj n uɣiř d ijj n cbar n ufus. Netta iɛbar tiru n řḥiḍ nni, aqa-t d ijj n uɣanim, u řuɛřa \add nnes\add* uřa d ijj n uɣanim. \f ◼ \fr 40:5 \ft \+fk Taddart\ft  - awař-a ixs ad yini ‘Taddart n Arebbi’ niɣ ‘Zzawect Iqeddsen’. \fk tiru n řḥiḍ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘tiru n řebni’.\f*   
\m
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ař \bd \+bdit řebni n\+bdit* tewwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq\bd* uca igeɛɛed x ddruj nnes, uca iɛbar tanebdat n tewwart, tiru nnes anect n ijj n uɣanim u tiru n tnebdat nneɣni uřa d ijj n uɣamin.  
\v 7 Tuzeggart n ict n texxamt \add n tewwart\add* d ijj n uɣanim u tiru nnes uřa d ijj n uɣanim. Jar texxamin \add n tewwart\add* \add tuɣa din\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen u tanebdat \add n řebni\add* n tewwart ɣar uɣezdis n wesqif n \add řebni n\add* tewwart ɣar uɣezdis n Taddart, \add aqa-tt\add* d ijj n uɣanim.  
\v 8 Netta iɛbar asqif \add n řebni\add* n tewwart ɣar daxeř, aqa-t d ijj n uɣanim.  
\v 9 Iɛbar asqif n řebni n tewwart, aqa-t di tmenya n iɣaǧen, uca řeḍruf n řḥiḍ nnes \add tuɣa aten\add* di tnayen n iɣaǧen. Asqif n \add n řebni\add* n tewwart tuɣa ɣar uɣezdis n Taddart.  
\v 10 Zi jjihet n texxamin n tewwart ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq \add n řebni n tewwart\add*, aqa din třata \add zzaysent\add* ɣar uɣezdis-a u třata \add zzaysent\add* ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni. Aqa atent ɣarsent d ijj n řeɛbar. Řeḍruf n řḥid \add ɣarsen\add* d řeɛbar d ijjen ɣar uɣezdis-a u ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni.  
\v 11 Iɛbar tiru n wadaf \add n řebni\add* n tewwart, aqa-t di ɛecra n iɣaǧen, uřa d tuzzeggart \add n řebni\add* n tewwart, aqa-tt di třeṭṭac n iɣaǧen.  
\v 12 Ttasiɛ zzat i texxamin n tewwart \add tuɣa\add* ijj n uɣiř \add ɣar uɣezdis-a\add* uca ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni \add tuɣa\add* ttasiɛ uřa d ijj n uɣiř. Ict n texxamt ɣares setta n iɣaǧen ɣar ijj n uɣezdis d setta iɣaǧen ɣar ijj n uɣezdis nneɣni.  
\v 13 Iɛbar \add ɛawed\add* \add řebni n\add* tewwart zi tzeqqa n ict n texxamt ař tazeqqa n wenneɣni. Tiru \add nnes tuɣa-t\add* di xemsa u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen, adaf arendad n wadaf \add nneɣni\add*.  
\v 14 Igga \add uřa d řeɛbar\add* ɣar řeḍruf n řḥiḍ: settin n iɣaǧen, uca řemraḥ ikka x ṭṭarf n řḥiḍ, inneḍ as-dd \add řemraḥ\add* i \add řebni n\add* tewwart marra.  
\v 15 Zi zzat n tewwart n wadaf ař zzat n wesqif n tewwart n daxeř, \add aqa din\add* xemsin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 16 \add Tuɣa\add* řekwazi ḥṣaren ɣar texxamin n tewwart u ɣar řeḍruf n řḥiḍ ɣar uɣezdis n daxeř \add n řebni\add* n tewwart deg wenneḍ, uřa di řeḥyuḍ n barra u tuɣa řekwazi deg wenneḍ xezzaren ɣar daxeř u x \add kuř ijj zi\add* řeḍruf n řḥiḍ tᵉttafed din ticejjura n tini.   
\m
\v 17 Indeh ayi-dd ɣar řemraḥ n barra, uca xzar, \add aqa din\add* ixxamen d ict n tisi n zzellij ittwaggen deg wenneḍ n řemraḥ. \add Tuɣa din\add* třatin n ixxamen ɣar tisi n zzellij \add nni\add*.  
\v 18 Tisi n zzellij \add tuɣa-tt\add* ɣar uɣezdis n \add řebniyyat n\add* tewwart, teqqen nican i tuzzeggart n \add řebniyyat n\add* tewwart. Tanita tuɣa-tt d tisi n zzellij i iǧan wadday.   
\m
\v 19 Netta iɛbar tiru zi zzat \add n řebni\add* n tewwart i iǧan ɣar wadday \add n řemraḥ\add* ař řemraḥ n daxeř ɣar uɣezdis nnes n barra, mya n iɣaǧen. \add Ammu i iɛbar\add* ccarq d ccamal \add n řemraḥ\add*.   
\m
\v 20 Zi \add řebni n\add* tewwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ccamal, ɣar řemraḥ n barra, iɛbar tuzzeggart nnes d tiru nnes.  
\v 21 Tuɣa třata n texxamin nnes ɣar uɣezdis-a d třata ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni, d řeḍruf nnes n řḥiḍ uřa d řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra ɣarsen d řeɛbar d ijjen am \add řebni n\add* tewwart tamezwarut. Tuzzuggart tuɣa-tt xemsin n iɣaǧen d tiru nnes tuɣa-tt xemsa u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 22 Řekwazi nnes d řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra uřa d ticejjura nnes n tini tuɣa ɣarsen řeɛbar d ijjen am \add řebni n\add* tewwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq. Ttgeɛɛaden ɣares x \add ijj n ddruj ak-d\add* \bd sebɛa n treffidin\bd* uca řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra tuɣa aten ɣar uɣezdis n zzat.  
\v 23 \add Řebni n\add* tewwart n řemraḥ n daxeř tuɣa-tt zzat \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ccamal d tenni n ccarq. Zeg řebni n tewwart \add n barra\add* ař řebni n tewwart \add n daxeř\add* iɛbar mya n iɣaǧen.   
\m
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* indeh ayi ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub, u xzar, tuɣa din ijj n \add řebni n\add* tewwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ljanub. Iɛbar řeḍruf n řḥiḍ d řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra \add uca\add* řeɛburat nsen tuɣa aten d ijj.  
\v 25 \add Řebni n\add* tewwart ɣares řekwazi uca uřa d řeḥyuḍ n barra daysen řekwazi am wenneɣni. Tuzzuggart \add nnes\add* tuɣa-tt di xemsin n iɣaǧen u tiru \add nnes\add* di xemsa u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 26 Drujj dayes sebɛa n treffidin u řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra \add tuɣa aten\add* ɣar zzat. Tuɣa ɣares ticejjura n tinni x řeḍruf n řḥiḍ, icten ɣar ijj n uɣezdis u icten ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*.  
\v 27 \add Tuɣa din ɛawed\add* ict n \add řebni n\add* tewwart ɣar řemraḥ n daxeř nni ixezzaren ɣar ljanub. Iɛbar zeg ict n \add řebni n\add* tewwart ař \add řebni n\add* tewwart \add nneɣni\add* ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub: mya n iɣaǧen.  
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* yiwi ayi ɣar \add řebni n\add* tewwart n ljanub ɣar řemraḥ n daxeř. Iɛbar \add řebni n\add* tewwart n ljanub, \add tuɣa\add* řeɛburat nnes d ijjen.  
\v 29 Ixxamen nnes d řeḍruf nnes n řḥiḍ uřa d řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra \add ɣarsen\add* d řeɛburat d ijjen. \add Řebni n tewwart\add* tuɣa ɣares řekwazi uca uřa d řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra ɣarsen \add řekwazi d ijjen am tinni\add*. Tuzzuggart \add nnes\add* \add tuɣa-tt\add* di xemsin n iɣaǧen u tiru \add nnes\add* di xemsa u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 30 Nnḍen as-dd řeḥyuḍ n barra. Tuzzuggart \add nnes\add* tuɣa-t di xemsa u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen u tiru \add nnes\add* di xemsa n iɣaǧen.  
\v 31 Tuɣa řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra ɣar řemraḥ n barra. \add Tuɣa din\add* ticejjura n tini x řeḍruf n řḥiḍ u ddruj nnes dayes tmenya n treffidin.   
\m
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* yiwi ayi ɣar řemraḥ n daxeř, ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq. Iɛbar \add řebni n\add* tewwart n ljanub, \add tuɣa\add* řeɛburat nnes d ijjen.  
\v 33 Tixxamin nnes d řeḍruf nnes n řḥiḍ uřa d řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra \add ɣarsen\add* d řeɛburat d ijjen. \add Řebni n tewwart\add* tuɣa ɣares řekwazi uca uřa ɣar řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra i dd asen innḍen marra. Tuzzuggart \add nnes\add* \add tuɣa-tt\add* di xemsin n iɣaǧen u tiru \add nnes\add* di xemsa u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 34 Řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra \add tuɣa aten\add* ɣar řemraḥ n barra. \add Tuɣa din\add* ticejjura n tini x řeḍruf n řḥiḍ nnes, \add am\add* ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* \add uřa\add* ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*, u ddruj nnes dayes tmenya n treffidin.   
\m
\v 35 \add Xenni\add* yiwi ayi ɣar \add řebni n\add* tewwart n ccamal uca iɛbar \add xenni\add* řeɛburat d ijjen.  
\v 36 Tixxamin nnes n tewwart d řeḍruf nnes n řḥid d řeḥyuḍ nnes n barra ɣarsen řekwazi deg wenneḍ nsen. Tuzzuggart \add nnes\add* \add tuɣa\add* di xemsin n iɣaǧen uca tiru \add nnes\add* di xemsa u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 37 Řeḍruf nnes n řḥiḍ \add tuɣa aten\add* ɣar řemraḥ n barra. \add Tuɣa din\add* ticejjura n tini ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* u ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add* x řeḍruf nnes. Ddruj nnes \add dayes\add* tmenya n treffidin.   
\m
\v 38 \add Tuɣa din\add* ijj n wexxam s ict n tewwart ɣar řeḍruf n řeḥyuḍ n \add řebniyyat\add* n tewwart, ad din ssirden taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.  
\v 39 Di daxeř n wesqif \add n řebni\add* n tewwart tuɣa din tnayen n ṭṭabřat ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* u tnayen n ṭṭabřat ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add* ḥima ad xasent ɣarṣen taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣt n ddenb d tɣarṣt n umarwas.  
\v 40 Barra ɣar ijj n uɣezdis n zzat ɣar mani geɛɛden ɣar wadaf \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ccamal \add tuɣa din\add* tnayen n ṭṭabřat, u ɣar uɣezdis n zzat nneɣni ɣar wesqif \add n řebni\add* n tewwart \add tuɣa din\add* ɛawed tnayen n ṭṭabřat.  
\v 41 \add Ammu tuɣa din\add* arebɛa n ṭṭabřat ɣar \add ijj n\add* uɣezdis u arebɛa n ṭṭabřat ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add* ɣar iɣezdis\add en\add* \add n řebni\add* n tewwart, aqa din tmenya n ṭṭabřat i min xef zemmaren ad ɣarṣen.  
\v 42 \add Tuɣa din\add* arebɛa n ṭṭabřat zi tṣuḍar ittwaneqcen ɣar ddruj \add n řebni n tewwart\add*. Tuzzuggart \add n ṭṭabřa\add* \add tuɣa-tt\add* d ijj n uɣiř d wezyen u tiru \add nnes\add* d ijj n uɣiř d wezyen u řuɛřa \add nnes\add* d ijj n uɣiř. Mmarsen xas řeqcuɛ i zi ɣarrṣen taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tewhibt n tɣarṣt.  
\v 43 Taryiwin n ijj n cbar n ufus ttwaggent deg wenneḍ ɣar daxeř \add n wesqif n řebni n tewwart\add*, u \add tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad mmarsen\add* aysum i tewhibt n tɣarṣt x ṭṭabřat \add i din iǧan\add*.   
\m
\v 44 Ɣar barra \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n daxeř \add tuɣa din\add* tixxamin n imeɣnajen di řemraḥ n daxeř nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar uɣezdis n zzat \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ccamal. Udem nnes ɣar zzat tuɣa ixezzar ɣar ljanub. Tawwart nni ɣar uɣezdis \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ccarq \add tuɣa\add* txezzar ɣar ccamal.  
\v 45 Netta issiweř akidi: “Taxxamt-a nni zi ixezzar wudem nnes ɣar ljanub, aqa-tt i ikehhanen nni iḥeṭṭan x tsexxart n Taddart.  
\v 46 Taxxamt nni txezzar wudem nnes ɣar ccamal, aqa-tt i ikehhanen nni iḥeṭṭan x tsexxart n uɛalṭar. Nitni d ayt n Ṣaduq nni ɣa dd-iqarrben ɣar SIDI zeg ayt n Lawi, maḥend ad as sexxaren.”  
\v 47 Iɛbar řemraḥ: tuzzeggart \add nnes\add* mya n iɣaǧen u tiru nnes mya n iɣaǧen, ijj n ukwadrun. Aɛaltar tuɣa-t zzat n Taddart.   
\b  
\m
\v 48 \add Xenni\add* yiwi ayi ɣar \bd wesqif n Taddart\bd* uca iɛbar řeḍruf n řḥiḍ n wesqif, xemsa n iɣaǧen ɣar \add ijj n\add* uɣezdis u xemsa n iɣaǧen ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*, uřa d tiru n tewwart, třata n iɣaǧen ɣar \add ijj n\add* uɣezdis u třata n iɣaǧen ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*.  
\v 49 Tuzzuggart n wesqif tuɣa-tt ɛicrin n iɣaǧen u tiru nnes ḥiṭac n iɣaǧen, d man aya ɣar \add uɣezdis n\add* treffidin \add n ddruj\add* i zi zemmaren ad geɛɛden. \add Tuɣa din\add* ɛawed ipilaren ɣar řeḍruf n řḥiḍ, ijj ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* u ijj ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*. *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 41
\s1 Taddart n Zzawect Tameqqrant n jdid  
\m
\v 1 Netta yiwi ayi ɣar \add Wexxam\add* n Zzawect Tameqqrant uca iɛbar řeḍruf n řḥiḍ. Tuɣa-ten setta n iɣaǧen ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* u setta n iɣaǧen ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*, x tiru n Uqiḍun. *   
\b  
\m
\v 2 Tiru n wadaf tuɣa-tt ɛecra n iɣaǧen uca udmawen n řeḥyuḍ ɣar uɣezdis n wadaf \add tuɣa aten\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* u xemsa n iɣaǧen ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*. Iɛbar tuzzeggart nnes: arebɛin n iɣaǧen, uca tiru nnes: ɛicrin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 3 Yudef-dd ɣar daxeř uca iɛbar řḥiḍ nni ɣar ṭṭarf n wadaf \add n Wexxam n Daxeř\add*: tnayen n iɣaǧen uca tewwart \add tuɣa-tt\add* setta n iɣaǧen uca tiru n wadaf sebɛa n iɣaǧen.  
\v 4 Iɛbar tuzzeggart \add n Wexxam n Daxeř\add*: ɛicrin n iɣaǧen, uca tiru \add nnes\add*: ɛicrin n iɣaǧen ɣar zzat \add n Wexxam\add* n Zzawect Tameqqrant. \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Wa d Aqdas x Uqeddas!”   
\m
\v 5 Iɛbar řḥiḍ n Taddart: setta n iɣaǧen, uca tiru n kuř axxam n uɣezdis \add tuɣa-t\add* di arebɛa n iɣaǧen deg wenneḍ n Taddart marra.  
\v 6 tixxamin n uɣezdis \add tuɣa atent\add* taxxamt zzat i texxamt \add nneɣni\add*, třata \add di řuɛřa\add*, uca \add amenni\add* třatin n twařawin ict n texxamt. Uca \add tixxamin nni\add* iwḍent ař řḥiḍ n Taddart nni \add din iǧan\add* i texxamin i d as dd-innḍen, maḥend ad iqeddem asenned \add i tḥenya n texxamin\add*. War iɛeddeř ad awḍent \add tḥenya\add* ař daxeř di řḥiḍ n Taddart.  
\v 7 Ɣar sennej deg wenneḍ immarni di ttasiɛ nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar ixxamen n uɣezdis x kuř ṭṭebqet Maɣar x kuř ṭṭebqet n taddart inneḍ-dd ijj n ukulwar i Taddart marra. X uya tedweř Taddart dayes ttasiɛ ktar sennej u ammu i izemmar \add bnadem\add* ad dd-igeɛɛed zeg wadday ɣar ṭṭebqet sennej s ṭṭebqet n řwesṭ.   
\m
\v 8 Ẓriɣ \bd ict n řgeɛɛdet i d as dd-innḍen i Taddart marra\bd*, aqa-tt d dsusa n ixxamen n uɣezdis: ijj n uɣanim \add n řeɛbar\add* ikemmřen, setta n iɣaǧen ař mani iwḍen \add ɣar tisi\add*.  
\v 9 Tiru n řḥiḍ nni \add igga\add* aɣezdis n barra n řebni ak-d ixxamen n uɣezdis, \add tuɣa-tt\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen, uca \add ammu uřa d\add* ttasiɛ yarezmen i iqqimen ɣar Taddart \add ak-d\add* ixxamen n uɣezdis, \add ttasiɛ\add* i dd-yusin-dd ak-d Taddart.  
\v 10 Uca \add min iqqimen ɛad\add* aqa d ijj n ttasiɛ jar ixxamen \add di řemřaḥ ɣar ccamal d yinni ɣar ljanub\add* n ɛicrin n iɣaǧen, deg wenneḍ n Taddart, deg wenneḍ nnes marra.  
\v 11 \add Teffeɣ\add* tewwart n řebni n ixxamen n uɣezdis ɣar ttasiɛ yarezmen i iqqimen, ict n tewwart \add teffeɣ\add* ɣar ccamal uca tawwart nneɣni \add teffeɣ\add* ɣar ljanub. Tiru n ttasiɛ iqqimen \add tuɣa-tt\add* di xemsa n iɣaǧen deg wenneḍ nnes marra.   
\m
\v 12 \bd Řebni ɣar wudem n řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen ɣar řɣarb\bd* tuɣa ɣares ict n tiru n sebɛin n iɣaǧen uca řḥiḍ n řebni tuɣa-t di xemsa n iɣaǧen deg wenneḍ nnes marra, uca tuzzeggart nnes \add tuɣa-tt\add* di tesɛin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 13 Netta iɛbar tuzzeggart n Taddart: mya n iɣaǧen. Řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen d řebni \add i dayes iǧan\add* ak-d řeḥyuḍ nnes, aqa \add ɣarsen\add* tuzzeggart d ict: mya n iɣaǧen.  
\v 14 \add Am\add* tiru n wudem n Taddart ɣar uɣezdis \add nnes n ḍeffar\add* \add am\add* řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen ɣar uɣezdis nnes n ccarq \add tuɣa\add* mya n iɣaǧen.  
\v 15 Iɛbar \add uřa d\add* tuzzeggart n řebni nni tuɣa ɣar zzat n řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen ař ḍeffar nnes. Ikulwaren nnes ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* u ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add* tuɣa aten di mya n uɣiř.  
\m Daxeř n Zzawect Tameqqrant, isqifen ɣar řemraḥ n zzat,  
\v 16 tinebdatin d řekwazi iḥṣaren d řebniyyat s ikulwaren i d as dd-innḍen i třata \add n řefwaqi nsent\add* zzat i tnebdatin \add n tewwura\add*, \add marra\add* aya tuɣa ittwassduri \add s teřwiḥin n\add* ukeccud, \add zi\add* temmurt ař řekwazi uca řekwazi \add simant nsen\add* tuɣa ttwassduryen.  
\v 17 X \add wudem i iǧan\add* sennej i wadaf, \add am\add* x wudem n daxeř \add am\add* x wudem n barra n Taddart u x marra řḥiḍ ɣar daxeř u ɣar barra \add tuɣa din\add* tiřwiḥin \add n ukeccuḍ\add*.  
\v 18 Tuɣa ttwaggen xasen ikiruben d tcejjura n tini. Aqa din ict n tcejjart n tini jar ijj n ukirub d ijj n ukirub \add nneɣni\add* uca kuř akirub ɣares tnayen n wudmawen: \f ◼ \fr 41:18 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  
\v 19 udem n bnadem nni ixezzaren ɣar tcejjart n tini ɣar ijj n uɣezdis d wudem n wayrad ameẓyan ixezzaren ɣar tcejjart n tini ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*. \add Ammu i\add* ten ggin deg wenneḍ n marra Taddart.  
\v 20 Zi temmurt ař sennej n tewwart ttwaggen ikiruben d tcejjura n tini uca ɛawed x řḥiḍ n Zzawect Tameqqrant.  
\v 21 Řeḍruf ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart n Zzawect Tameqqrant ggin ijj n ukwadrun uca ccuf n Uqeddas iḍhar-dd am ccuf \add n Zzawect\add*.   
\m
\v 22 \bd Aɛalṭar\bd* tuɣa-t n ukeccuḍ u řuɛřa nnes tuɣa-t třata n iɣaǧen u řebni sadu nnes tnayen n iɣaǧen di řuɛřa nnes. Ɣares tiɣemmura uca řebni sadu nnes d iɣezdisen nnes \add tuɣa aten\add* zeg ukeccuḍ. Netta issiweř akidi: “Ta d tazewḍa nni \add iǧan\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI.”  
\v 23 Zzawect Tameqqrant d Weqdas ɣarsen tnayen n tewwura.  
\v 24 Tuɣa ɣar tiwwura, \add ɣar kuř icten zzaysent,\add* tnayen n teřwiḥin am wafriwen, tnayen n teřwiḥin nni zemmaren ad nuqqaren, tnayen i yict n tewwart u tnayen i \add tewwart\add* nneɣni.  
\v 25 Di tewwura n Zzawect Tameqqrant ttwaggen ikiruben d tcejjura n tini nni ittwaggen am yinni x řeḥyuḍ. Tuɣa din tasqift n ukeccuḍ ɣar wudem n wesqif ɣar barra.  
\v 26 \add Tuɣa din\add* řekwazi ḥsaren d tcejjura n tini ɣar uɣezdis\add -a\add* u ɣar uɣezdis \add nneɣni\add*, ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n wesqif, \add ɣar\add* ixxamen i iǧan ɣar uɣezdis n Taddart u ɣar tesqifin. *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 42
\s1 Ixxamen n ikehhanen  
\m
\v 1 Netta issuffeɣ ayi-dd barra ɣar řemraḥ n barra nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar ccamal. Netta indeh ayi ɣar \add řebni n\add* ixxam\add en\add* nni iǧan ɣar uɣezdis n řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen u ɣar uɣezdis n řebni \add n Zzawect Tameqqrant\add*, ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal,  
\v 2 ɣar uɣezdis \add nnes\add* d azirar n mya n iɣaǧen, \add ɣar\add* wadaf n ccamal, \add maca\add* tiru \add nnes tuɣa\add* di xemsin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 3 Tuɣa řebni zzat i \add ttasiɛ yarezmen n\add* ɛicrin \add n iɣaǧen\add* n řemraḥ n daxeř u zzat i zzellij n řemraḥ n barra. Ijj n ukulwar \add ak-d ixxamen nnes\add* tuɣa \add isenned\add* x ukulwar nneɣni, uca aqa din třata n ṭṭebqat.   
\m
\v 4 Zzat n ixxamen \add tuɣa din\add* ijj n ukulwar ɣar daxeř s ict n tiru n ɛecra n iɣaǧen, ict n tebridt \add n mya\add* n iɣaǧen, uca tiwwura n wadaf nsen \add tuɣa atent\add* ɣar ccamal.  
\v 5 Ixxamen n sennej \add tuɣa aten\add* ḥṣaren, maɣar ikulwaren kksen \add ktar ttasiɛ\add* zzaysen x \add yexxamen n\add* wadday u \add x yexxamen\add* ɣar řwest n řebni.  
\v 6 Minzi \add tuɣa aten\add* di třata \add n řefwaqi\add*, maca war ɣarsen ipilaren am yipilaren n řemraḥat. X uya tuɣa aten ixammen nni ḥsaren ktar x yinni n wadday d yinni di řwesṭ \add am ɣarsen txezzared\add* zi temmurt.   
\m
\v 7 Řḥiḍ nni tuɣa ɣar barra qibač i yexxamen, \add řḥiḍ\add* nni iǧan ɣar uɣezdis n řemraḥ n barra, i dd-ittekken zzat i yexxamen, \add tuɣa ɣares\add* tuzzeggart n xemsin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 8 Minzi tuzzeggart n \add marra\add* ixxamen nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar řemraḥ n barra, tuɣa-tt di xemsin n iɣaǧen. \add Maca\add* xzar, ɣar uɣezdis n Zzawect Tameqqrant tuɣa-tt di mya n iɣaǧen.  
\v 9 Swadday n ixxamen-a \add teggur\add* tebridt zi ccarq xmi dd ɣarsen tiwḍed zi řemraḥ n barra.   
\m
\v 10 Ɣar tiru n řḥiḍ n řemraḥ ɣar ccarq, \add řḥiḍ\add* zzat i řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen u ɣar uɣezdis n řebni, \add tuɣa din ɛawed řebniyyat n\add* ixxamen,  
\v 11 uca akulwar i dd-ittekken zzatsen \add tuɣa\add* am tenni n ixxamen nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal, anect tuzzeggart anect tiru u marra uffuɣen nnes tuɣa aten am ṣṣenɛat d wadafen nnes \add ɣar uɣezdis n ixammen ɣar ccamal\add*.  
\v 12 Am mammec \add din\add* adafen ɣar texxamin tinni iwejjhen ɣar ljanub, \add amenni i din\add* iǧa uřa d ijj n wadaf ɣar beddu n tebridt, tabridt nni itteffɣen zi zzat i řḥid n řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen uca tᵉttakkwaḍ ɣar webrid i x dd ɣa yas bnadem zi ccarq ɣar řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen.   
\m
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Ixxamen nni iǧan ɣar ccamal u ixxamen nni iǧan ɣar ljanub, inni iǧan ɣar zzat n řemraḥ ittwaɛezřen, aqa aten d ixxamen iqeddsen mani ikehhanen, inni i ɣa dd-iqarrben ɣar SIDI, ad ccen tiwhibin iqeddsen aṭṭas. Din ittxeṣṣa ad sarsen nitni tiwhibin iqeddsen aṭṭas: tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tewhibt n ddenb d tewhibt n umarwas, minzi amcan iqeddes qaɛ.  
\v 14 Xmi ɣa udfen ikehhanen, war iɛeddeř ad uyuren zi Zzawect Iqeddsen ɣar řemraḥ n barra. Ad ssarsen arruḍ nsen n tsexxart, maɣar wanita d amqeddes. Ad arḍen arruḍ nneɣni uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-qarrben ɣar \add řemraḥ\add* nni iǧan i řgens.” *   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Zzawect Tameqqrant n jdid - Jjihet Iqeddsen  
\m
\v 15 Umi ikemmeř netta řeɛbar n min iǧan daxeř n Taddart, issuffuɣ ayi-dd zeg webrid n tewwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq uca iksi řeɛbar n jjihet iqeddsen deg wenneḍ marra.  
\v 16 Iɛbar aɣezdis n ccarq s uɣanim n řeɛbar: xemsa-mya n iɣunam s uɣanim n řeɛbar deg wenneḍ.  
\v 17 Iɛbar aɣezdis n ccamal, xemsa-mya n iɣunam s uɣanim n řeɛbar deg wenneḍ.  
\v 18 Iɛbar aɣezdis n ljanub, xemsa-mya n iɣunam s uɣanim n řeɛbar.  
\v 19 Inuqqar ɣar uɣezdis n lɣarb uca iɛbar xemsa-mya n iɣunam s uɣanim n řeɛbar.  
\v 20 Netta iɛbar \add řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant\add* ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura \add nnes\add*. \add Tuɣa\add* ɣares deg wenneḍ nnes ijj n řḥiḍ s ict n tuzzeggart n xemsa-mya \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* d ict n tiru n xemsa-mya \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* maḥend ad ifarz jar min \add iǧan\add* iqeddsen d min war \add iǧin\add* iqeddsen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 43
\s1 Aɛuǧi n SIDI idweř-dd ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* indeh ayi ɣar tewwart, \add ɣar\add* tewwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq.  
\v 2 Xzar, yusa-dd uɛuǧi n AREBBI n Israil zi jjihet n ccarq uca tmijja nnes tuɣa-tt am řhess n waman aṭṭas uca tammurt tceɛceɛ s uɛuǧi nnes.  
\v 3 Udem n řewḥiy i ẓriɣ tuɣa am řewḥiy i ẓriɣ umi dd-usiɣ ḥima ad areddǧeɣ tandint. Aqa d iweḥḥan am řewḥiy i ẓriɣ ɣar yeɣzar n Xabur, uca wḍiɣ s wudem inu \add ɣar temmurt\add*. \x ◘ \xo 43:3 \xt Ḥiz. 1:4; 8:4\x*  
\v 4 Aɛuǧi n SIDI yudef ɣar Taddart s tewwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq.  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed ayi-dd Arruḥ uca issidef ayi ɣar řemraḥ n daxeř, uca xzar, aɛuǧi n SIDI iccur Taddart. \x ◘ \xo 43:5 \xt Ḥiz. 3:14, Ḥiz. 11:24\x*  
\v 6 Uca sřiɣ \add ict n tmijja\add* tessawař akidi zi daxeř n Taddart uca aryaz ibedd ɣar uɣezdis inu.  
\v 7 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, wa d amcan n řɛarc inu u amcan n třeqqa n iḍaren inu, mani ɣa zedɣeɣ di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil i řebda. Uca nitni, taddart n Israil, nitni uřa d ijeǧiden nsen, war ssxemmajen ɛad Isem inu iqeddsen s farq-ccɣeř nsen u s řxecbat n \add l’aṣnam n\add* ijeǧiden nsen x řegɛudi nsen \add mani ttqeddamen tiwhibin nsen\add* \x ◘ \xo 43:7 \xt Irm. 16:18\x*  
\v 8 am ggin tanebdat nsen zzat i tnebdat inu, d ṭṭarf n tewwart nsen ɣar ṭṭarf \add n tewwart\add* inu, \add iqqim\add* mɣir ijj n weɣbar jar ayi-dd d nitni. \add Ammu i\add* ssexmejen Isem inu iqeddsen s jjɛayef nsen nni ggin, ařami cciɣ ten deg weɣḍab inu.  
\v 9 Nitni ad xafi ssiggʷejen farq-ccɣeř nsen d řxecbat n \add l’aṣnam n\add* ijeǧiden nsen, maḥend ad zemmareɣ ad zedɣeɣ di řwest nsen i řebda.  
\v 10 Cek, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem, barreḥ s Taddart-a i taddart n Israil ḥima ad seḍḥan zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyat nsen uca ejj i-ten ad ɛbaren ccekl nnes.  
\v 11 Mařa seḍḥan zi marra min ggin, scen asen \add xenni\add* ccekl n Taddart d tisars nnes, uffuɣen nnes d adafen nnes d marra ccekl nnes d marra lfarayiḍ nnes, \add wah,\add* marra ickalen nnes d marra tiweṣṣa nnes uca ari \add marra\add* man aya zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, ḥima xenni ad ḥḍan marra ccekl nnes d marra lfarayiḍ nnes, uca ad zzaysen ggen.”   
\m  
\s1 Aɛalṭar d udeccen nnes  
\m
\v 12 “Ta d ccariɛa n Taddart: x tqiccat n wedrar ad yiři wemcan nnes deg wenneḍ nnes iqeddsen qaɛ. Ta d ccariɛa n Taddart.” \x ◘ \xo 43:12 \xt Ḥiz. 20:40; Ḥiz. 40:2\x*   
\m
\v 13 “Ina d řeɛburat n \bd uɛalṭar\bd* s iɣaǧen: \bd ijj n uɣiř aqa-t d ijj n uɣiř d ijj cbar n ufus.\bd* Tarya nnes d ijj n uɣiř u tiru nnes d ijj n uɣiř. Tma nnes ɣar ṭṭarf nnes i d as dd-innḍen aqa d ijj n wezyen n uɣiř. Wa d dsas n uɛalṭar. \f ◼ \fr 43:13 \ft \+fk aḥsin\ft  - niɣ ‘abeḥrur’.\f*  
\v 14 Zi tarya di temmurt ař tareffidet n wadday \add n uɛalṭar\add*: tnayen n iɣaǧen, u tiru \add nnes\add*: ijj n uɣiř, u zi treffidet n wadday \add n uɛalṭar\add* ař tareffidet n sennej \add n uɛalṭar\add*: arebɛa n iɣaǧen u tiru \add nnes\add* ijj n uɣiř.  
\v 15 Řebni ɣar sennej, \add adrar n Arebbi’,\add* \add igga\add* arebɛa n iɣaǧen \add di řuɛřa\add* u zeg ufurnu n uɛalṭar \add geɛɛden-dd zzayes\add* arebɛa n waccawen sennej nnes.  
\v 16 Afurnu n uɛalṭar ɣares ict n tuzzeggart n tenɛac \add n iɣaǧen\add* d ict n tiru n tenɛac \add n iɣaǧen\add*, ijj n ukwadrun s arebɛa n iɣezdisen \add nnes\add*.  
\v 17 Tareffidet nnes \add sennej\add* ɣares ict n tuzzeggart n arbeɛṭac \add n iɣaǧen\add* d ict n tiru n arbeɛṭac \add n iɣaǧen\add* ɣar arebɛa n iɣezdisen nnes, u tma nnes i d as dd-innḍen aqa d azyen n uɣiř, uca tarya nnes d ijj n uɣiř deg wenneḍ nnes uca tareffidin n ddruj nnes xezzaren ɣar ccarq.” *   
\b  
\m
\v 18 Netta inna ayi: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Tina d lfarayiḍ inu i uɛalṭar deg wass i di t ɣa ggen, maḥend ad xas ssgeɛɛden taɣarṣt n tmessi u maḥend ad xas zeǧɛen idammen.’  
\v 19 \add Ammu\add* i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Ad tewced ijj n ufunas, ameẓyan n ict n tfunast, d tawhibt n tɣarṣt n ddenb i ikehhanen zeg Ilawiyyen, i yinni dd-iqqarṣen zi Ṣaduq, inni ɣari dd-iqarrben maḥend ad ayi sexxaren.  
\v 20 Ad teksid zeg idammen nnes uca ad ten tegged ɣar arebɛa n waccawen \add n uɛalṭar\add* u ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura n treffidet u x tma nnes i d as dd-innḍen ɣar ṭṭarf nnes. Ittxeṣṣa ad zzayes tekksed ddenb nnes u ad t tṣeřḥed.  
\v 21 \add Awarni as\add* ad teksid afunas nni ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb. Ittxeṣṣa asen ad t sscemḍen deg wemcan ittwaggen n Taddart barra i Zzawect Iqeddsen.  
\v 22 Deg wass wiss tnayen ad dd-tessqarrbed ijj n umyan zeg iɣayḍen icnan aṭṭas d taɣarṣt n ddenb. Ad zzayes kksen ddenb zeg uɛalṭar am mammec zzayes kksen ddenb s ufunas ameẓyan.  
\v 23 Xmi ɣa tkemmřed takessit n ddenb, ad dd-tessqarrbed ijj n ufunas, ameẓyan n tfunast icnan qaɛ, uřa d ijj n icarri icnan aṭṭas zeg wuǧi.  
\v 24 Ad ten dd-tessqarrbed zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ikehhanen ad xas ssuyusen tameǧaḥt u ad ten ssgeɛɛden am tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI.  
\v 25 Sebɛa n wussan ad tesswejded di kuř ass ijj n umyan d taɣarṣt n ddenb. Ad sswejden \add ɛawed\add* ijj n ufunas, ameẓyan n tfunast, uřa d ijj n icarri n wuǧi, ittxeṣṣa ad iřin cnan aṭṭas.  
\v 26 Sebɛa n wussan ad tegged aṣřaḥ i uɛalṭar uca ad t ssizedgen u ad t ssqeddsen.  
\v 27 Mařa kemmřen nitni ussan-a, \add xenni\add* ad yiři deg wass wiss tmenya, belli ikehhanen ad sswejden tɣarṣa nwem n wecmaḍ d tewhibin nwem n uqadi x uɛalṭar u Necc ad xawem arḍiɣ!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 44
\s1 Řḥakem d ikehhanen  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra ayi ɛawed ɣar tewwart n barra n Zzawect Iqeddsen nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq. Tuɣa tbelleɛ.  
\v 2 \bd Inna ayi SIDI:\bd* “Tawwart-a ad teqqim tbelleɛ, war tarzem ca uca uřa d ijj ad zzayes yadef. Minzi SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, yudef zzayes, x uya ad teqqim tbelleɛ.  
\v 3 Řḥakem \add waha\add* i yeǧan d řḥakem, ad din iqqim ḥima ad yecc aɣrum zzat i wudem n SIDI. Ad yadef s ukulwar n wesqif \add n řebni\add* n tewwart uca ad iffeɣ s ukulwar nnes.”   
\m
\v 4 \add Awarni as\add* indeh ayi \add s\add* tewwart n ccamal ɣar zzat n Taddart. Xezzareɣ, uca xzar, aɛuǧi n SIDI iccur Taddart n SIDI. \add Xenni\add* wḍiɣ s uɣembub inu \add ɣar temmurt\add*.  
\v 5 Inna ayi SIDI: “\add A\add* mmis n bnadem, egg uř nnec, xzar s tiṭṭawin nnec uca seř s imezzuɣen nnec marra min d ac ɣa ssiwřeɣ x marra tiweṣṣa n Taddart n SIDI u x marra izerfan nnes. Egg uř nnec x \add kuř ijjen\add* i ittadfen Taddart s marra uffuɣen n Zzawect Iqeddsen  
\v 6 uca ini i yinni ittɣewwɣen, i taddart n Israil: ‘Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Cfa marra jjɛayef nwem, \add a\add* taddart n Israil,  
\v 7 maɣar kenniw tessidfem ibarraniyyen, inni war ittwaxetnen n wuř u inni war ittwaxetnen n arrimet, maḥend ad iřin di Zzawect inu Iqeddsen u ad ssɛiǧten \add ammu\add* Taddart inu, řami kenniw tiwyem aɣrum inu, \add ixs ad yini\add* tadunt d idammen, u arẓin nitni Řɛahd inu sennej i marra jjɛayef \add i teggim s yixef\add* nwem.  
\v 8 Kenniw war teḥḍim aḥeṭṭu x min \add iǧan\add* iqeddsen i Necc uca teggim imeḥḍayen i yixef nwem maḥend ad ḥḍan x Zzawect inu Iqeddsen.”   
\m
\v 9 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Uřa d ijj n řbarrani nni war ittwaxetnen uř nnes u war ittwaxetnen aysum nnes ad yadef ɣar Zzawect inu Iqeddsen. Ammu i ɣa yiři i kuř řbarrani nni iǧan di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil.  
\v 10 Ilawiyyen nni yaggʷejen xafi aṭṭas umi zzayi iweddar Israil, ffɣen zeg webrid, \add uyuren\add* awarni imeyḍa nsen n l’aṣnam. Aqa nitni ad arbun řmuɛṣiyyet nsen.  
\v 11 Ad ḥḍan di Zzawect inu Iqeddsen ɣar \add řebniyyat n\add* tewwart n Taddart uca ad sexxaren \add ɛawed\add* di Taddart. Nitni ad ɣarṣen taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣt i řgens uca ad bedden zzat i wudem n řgens maḥend ad asen sexxaren.  
\v 12 Umi tuɣa ttsexxaren zzat i wudem n imeyḍa nsen n l’aṣnam u umi ten tuɣa d ict n ssibbet i dd-yiwyen řmuɛṣiyyet i taddart n Israil, x uya aqa ssgeɛɛdeɣ Necc afus inu xasen u nitni ad arbun řmuɛṣiyyet nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 13 War iɛeddeř ad ɣari dd-qarrben maḥend ad ayi iřin d ikehhanen u maḥend ad dd-qarrben ɣar marra timesřayin iqeddsen inu, ɣar tmesřayin iqeddsen qaɛ. Nitni ad arbun řefdiḥet nsen d jjɛayef i ggin.  
\v 14 Ad ten ggeɣ maḥend ad ḥḍan x tsexxart di Taddart, x marra řxedmet nnes u x marra min ittxeṣṣa ad dayes ittwagg.’”   
\m
\v 15 “\add Maca\add* ikehhanen ilawiyyen, ayt n Ṣaduq, inni iḥḍan aḥeṭṭu n Zzawect inu Iqeddsen xmi xafi iggʷejen ayt n Israil, ad ɣari dd-qarrben maḥend ad ayi sexxaren. Nitni ad bedden zzat i wudem inu maḥend ad ɣari dd-awyen tadunt d idammen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 16 Nitni ad adfen ɣar Zzawect inu Iqeddsen uca ad dd-qarrben ɣar ṭṭabřa inu maḥend ad ayi sexxaren u ad ḥḍan tasexxart inu.  
\v 17 Ad yiři xmi ɣa yadfen ɣar \add řebniyyat n\add* tewwart n řemraḥ n daxeř, ad arḍen arruḍ n řeqṭen. War iɛeddeř ad arḍen ca n taḍuft xmi ɣa sexxaren di \add řebniyyat n\add* tewwart n řemraḥ n daxeř u ɣar daxeř nnes.  
\v 18 Areẓẓat n řeqṭen ad iřin x izeǧifen nsen u ssraweř n řeqṭen ad iřin x tejɛinnatin nsen, war beysen ca min zi ɣa ssuffɣen tidi.  
\v 19 Xmi ɣa ffɣen ɣar řemraḥ n barra, ɣar řemraḥ n barra ɣar řgens, \add xenni\add* ad kksen arruḍ nsen i di sexxaren uca ad t ssarsen deg ixxamen iqeddsen. \add Awarni as\add* ad arḍen arruḍ nneɣni, ḥima war ssqeddasen řgens s warrud nsen.  
\v 20 War ssquccaren azeǧif nsen u war ttejjin tijeṭṭayin \add nsen\add* ad ayřent amenni \add waha\add*. Nitni ad qessen \add acuwwaf n\add* uzeǧif nsen mliḥ.  
\v 21 War iɛeddeř uřa i yijj n ukehhan ad isu binu, xmi ɣa yadef ɣar řemraḥ n daxeř.  
\v 22 War d asen iɛeddeř \add i ikehhanen\add* maḥend ad awyen ict n tajjač niɣ ict n tnuřuft d tamɣart i yixef nsen. Iɛeddeř maḥend ad awyen mɣir tiɛzuray zi zzariɛet n taddart n Israil ict n tajjač tenni d tajjač n ijj n ukehhan. \x ◘ \xo 44:22 \xt Lawi 21:13, 14\x*  
\v 23 Ad ssřemden řgens inu řfarq jar min \add iǧan\add* iqeddsen d min war \add iǧin\add* iqeddsen uca ad ten ssaregben řfarz jar min ixemjen d min izdigen.  
\v 24 Deg umcubbec ad kkaren ḥima ad carrɛen. Ad ten ḥakmen ɛlaḥsab lfarayiḍ inu. Nitni ad ḥḍan tiweṣṣa inu d lfarayiḍ inu di marra řeɛyudat inu ittwaggen uca ad ssqeddsen ussan inu n ssebt.  
\v 25 War iɛeddeř ad ireḥḥeg \add ukehhan\add* ɣar ijj n bnadem immuten ařami ɣa issexmej ixef nnes. Iɛeddeř \add waha\add* ad ssxemjen ixef nsen mɣir i babatsen niɣ i yemmatsen niɣ i mmitsen niɣ i yeǧitsen niɣ i umatsen niɣ i učmatsen nni war imřicen ɛemmarṣ.  
\v 26 Awarni usizdeg nnes ittxeṣṣa asen ad ḥessben sebɛa n wussan i netta.  
\v 27 Deg wass nni i ɣa yadef ɣar Uqeddas, ɣar řemraḥ n daxeř, maḥend ad isexxar deg Uqeddas, ittxeṣṣa as ad dd-issqarreb taɣarṣt n ddenb, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\m
\v 28 “Wa ad yiři d řwart nsen: Necc d Řwart nsen. War d asen tᵉtticim uřa d ijj n wagřa \add n temmurt\add* di Israil: Necc d Agřa nsen. \x ◘ \xo 44:28 \xt Řxř. 18:20; Aɛwd. 18:1\x*  
\v 29 Iɛeddeř ad ccen tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tɣarṣt n ddenb d tɣarṣt n umarwas. Marra min ittwaḥarrmen di Israil ad asen yiři.  
\v 30 Mummu n tmenzut n marra u marra tawhibt n usgeɛɛed, zi marra tiwhibin nwem n usgeɛɛed, ad yiři i ikehhanen. Tamezwarut n warecti nwem ad tt tewced i ukehhan, ḥima ad tarsa lbaraka x taddart nnec. \x ◘ \xo 44:30 \xt Uf. 13:2; 22:29,30; Řxř. 18:11\x*  
\v 31 Uřa d ict n řxecbet niɣ min ittwacarrgen n ijḍaḍ niɣ n řebḥayem, war iɛeddeř ad t ccen ikehhanen.” \x ◘ \xo 44:31 \xt Lawi 22:8\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 45
\s1 Tasɣart n temmurt i iǧan i SIDI  
\m
\v 1 “Xmi ɣa tebḍam tammurt d řwart \add s tqedduḥt\add*, ad twehhbem ict n tewhibt n usgeɛɛed i SIDI, ict n tesɣart iqeddsen zi temmurt: tuzzeggart nnes \add ad tiři\add* xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* d tiru nnes ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*. Marra tammurt i d as dd-innḍen ad tiři tqeddes.  
\v 2 Xemsa-mya di xemsa-mya \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* ɣar arebɛa iɣezdisen nnes ad zzayes iřin i Zzawect Iqeddsen. Uca deg wenneḍ nnes xemsin n iɣaǧen ad iřin d ddmani n tarewsa.  
\v 3 S řeɛbar-a ad teɛbared di tuzzeggart xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef u di tiru ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* u Zzawect Iqeddsen ad dayes tiři, \add ixs ad yini\add* Aqdas x Uqeddas.  
\v 4 Ad tiři d ict n temmurt iqeddsen. Ad tiři i ikehhanen nni ittsexxaren di Zzawect Iqeddsen, inni dd-iqarrben maḥend ad sexxaren i SIDI. Ad tiři i nitni d amcan n tzeddiɣin \add nsen\add* d ijj n wemcan iqeddsen i Zzawect Iqeddsen.   
\m
\v 5 \add Ict n temmurt\add* s ict n tuzzeggart n xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef u s ict n tiru n ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* ad tiři i Ilawiyyen nni ittsexxaren di Taddart, \add ad tiři\add* d řmulk i nitni, \add s\add* ɛicrin n řebniyyat n ixxamen.   
\m
\v 6 Ad tewcem \add ict n temmurt\add* s ict n tiru n xemsa-ařaf u s ict n tuzzeggart n xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* d tammurt i tendint, zzat i \add temmurt n\add* tewhibt iqeddsen n usgeɛɛed. Ad tiři i marra taddart n Israil.  
\v 7 Tasɣart \add n temmurt\add* n řḥakem ad tiři ɣar ijj n uɣezdis uřa ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni n \add temmurt n\add* tewhibt iqeddsen n usgeɛɛed u n tesɣart \add n temmurt\add* n tendint, zzat i tewhibt iqeddsen n usgeɛɛed u zzat i tesɣart \add n temmurt\add* n tendint, zeg uɣezdis n řɣarb ɣar řɣarb u zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ɣar ccarq. Tuzzuggart ad tiři nican zzat i uɣezdis n icten zi tseqqař n řwart, zeg weymir i iǧan ɣar řɣarb ař weymir i iǧan ɣar ccarq.  
\v 8 Tammurt ad tiři nnes, tasɣart nnes di Israil. U řḥukkam inu war ḥessaren ɛad řgens inu, \add maca\add* ad wcen tammurt i taddart n Israil, i tqebbař nsen.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řḥeqq n řḥakem d min xas iǧan  
\m
\v 9 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Cfa awem, \add a kenniw,\add* řḥukkam n Israyil! Sbeɛɛed xawem lɛunf u ggem řḥeqq d tsegda uca kksem ibeɛɛaj nwem x řgens inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 10 Ittxeṣṣa ad ɣarwem yiři ijj n řmizan nican d ijj n ifa nican d ijj n ubatu nican. \f ◼ \fr 45:10 \ft \+fk abatu\ft  - ijj n ‘ubatu’ ɛraḥař 20 niɣ 40 litru.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 45:10 \xt Lawi 19:35, 36; Aɛwd. 25:13-16.\x*  
\v 11 Ittxeṣṣa ad yiři \add řeɛbar n\add* ifa d \add řeɛbar n\add* ubatu d řeɛbar d ijj, ḥima ad yiři ubatu d ict zi tɛeccart n uḥumir, uca ict n tɛeccart n uḥumir \add ad teswa\add* ifa. Řeqyas n řeɛbar nsen ad yiři zeg uḥumir.  
\v 12 Aciql aqa-t ɛicrin jira. Ɛicrin ciqlu, xemsa u-ɛecrin ciqlu, xemmesṭac ciqlu, ad awem yiři ijjen mina.’” \x ◘ \xo 45:12 \xt Uf. 30:13; Lawi 27:25; Řxř. 3:47\x*   
\m
\v 13 “Ta d tewhibt n usgeɛɛed nni i ɣa tessgeɛɛdem: ict n tsittut n ijj n ifa zeg ijj n uḥumir n yirden uca ad tewcem uřa d ict n tsittut n ijj n uḥumir n imendi.  
\v 14 X tewṣeyyet n zzect, \add tawṣiyyet n\add* \add řqedd n\add* ubatu n zzect: aqa ict n teɛcart n ubatu n ijj n ukuru, \add akuru nni isekkwin\add* ijj n uḥumir n ɛecra ibatuten, minzi ɛecra ibatuten d ijj n uḥumir.  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* ijj \add zeg wuǧi\add* x mitayen n wuǧi zi \add ddmani n tarewsa n\add* temmurt n Israil i ifeyyḍen s waman, am tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* u am tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ u am tewhibt n řehna, maḥend ad tegged aṣřaḥ i nitni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.  
\v 16 Marra řgens n temmurt, \add marra\add* nitni ad carcen di tewhibt n usgeɛɛed i řḥakem di Israil.  
\v 17 Ad yiři x řḥakem maḥend \add ad yegg\add* tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tɣarṣt \add n useyyeb\add* di řeɛyudat u deg wussan n uyur n jdid u x wussan n ssebt, \add wah,\add* x marra ussan n řeɛyudat n taddart n Israil. Netta ad issewjed taɣarṣt n ddenb d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tewhibt n wecmaḍ d tewhibin n řehna, maḥend ad igg aṣřaḥ i taddart n Israil.” \f ◼ \fr 45:17 \ft \+fk ad igg asřaḥ\ft  - niɣ ‘ad ifdi’. Xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řeɛyudat d tewhibin  
\m
\v 18 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Deg uyur amezwaru, deg wass amezwar n uyur, ad teksid ijj n ufunas icnan aṭṭas, ameẓyan n tfunast, uca ad zzayes tekksed ddenb zi Zzawect Iqeddsen.  
\v 19 Akehhan ad iksi zeg idammen n tɣarṣa n ddenb uca ad ten yegg x řeḍruf i iǧan ɣar uɣezdis n tewwura n Taddart, ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura n treffidet n uɛalṭar u x řeḍruf n tewwart n řemraḥ n daxeř.  
\v 20 Ammu i ɣa tegged deg wass wiss sebɛa n uyur, di ṭṭweɛ n wenni iweddaren \add deg webrid\add* u di ṭṭweɛ n uqubbani, ammu i ɣa teggem aṣřaḥ i Taddart.’”   
\m
\v 21 “Deg \add uyur\add* amezwaru, deg wass wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur ad tiři \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i kenniw, ad yiři řɛid i yijj n řmijař n sebɛa n wussan, ad ccen aɣrum břa antun. \x ◘ \xo 45:21 \xt Uf. 12:3; 23:15; Lawi 23:5; Řxř. 9:3; 28:16, 17; Aɛwd. 16:1\x*  
\v 22 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad issewjed řḥakem ijj n ufunas ameẓyan \add am\add* tɣarṣṭ n ddenb i yixef nnes u i marra řgens n temmurt.  
\v 23 \add Di\add* sebɛa n wussan n řɛid ad issewjed ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI: sebɛa n ifunasen imeẓyanen d sebɛa n icarriyyen icnan, \add marra\add* sebɛa n wussan nni, uřa d ict n tɣarṣt n ddenb n ijj n umyan zeg iɣayḍen kuř ass.  
\v 24 Ad issewjed \add ɛawed\add* tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*: ijj n ifa i yijj n ufunas ameẓyan u ijj n ifa i yijj n icarri u ijj n uhinu n zzect i yijj n ifa.  
\v 25 Deg \add yuyur\add* wiss sebɛa, deg wass wiss xemmesṭac n uyur ittxeṣṣa as ad yegg \add ammu\add* \add marra\add* man aya di řɛid, sebɛa n wussan: am tɣarṣt n ddenb am tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, am tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* am zzect.” \x ◘ \xo 45:25 \xt Lawi 23:33; Řxř. 29:12; Aɛwd. 16:13\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 46
\m
\v 1 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Tawwart n řemraḥ n daxeř nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq ad tiři tbelleɛ di setta n wussan n řxedmet. Deg wass n ssebt ad tennurzem uřa x wass n uyur n jdid ad tennurzem.  
\v 2 Ad dd-yadef řḥakem zi barra s ukulwar n wesqif \add n řebni\add* n tewwart uca ad ibedd ɣar ṭṭarf \add n řebni\add* n tewwart. Ikehhanen ad sswejden tiɣarṣa nnes n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣa nnes n tmessi u netta ad isjed x tnebdat n tewwart uca ad \add zzayes\add* iffeɣ \add ɛawed\add*. War ttbelliɛen tawwart ař tameddit.  
\v 3 Řgens n temmurt ad isjed zzat i wadaf \add n řebni\add* n tewwart x wussan n ssebt u x wussan n uyur n jdid zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 4 Taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ nni i ɣa dd-issqarreb řḥakem i SIDI deg wass n ssebt, ad tiři setta n izmaren icnan d ijj n icarri icna.  
\v 5 Tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* \add ad tiři\add* ijj n ifa i yijj n icarri, u i izmaren \add ad tiři\add* tewhibt \add n rɣiǧet\add* min izemmar ufus nnes ad t yawi uca \add xenni arni\add* ijj n uhinu n zzect i kuř ifa.  
\v 6 Deg wass n uyur n jdid: ijj n ufunas icnan aṭṭas, ameẓyan n tfunast, u setta n izmaren d ijj n icarri. Ittxeṣṣa ad iřin cnan aṭṭas.  
\v 7 Ad issewjed ijj n ifa i kuř afunas ameẓyan u ijj n ifa i kuř icarri d tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* u i izmaren anect izemmar ufus nnes ad t yawi, u \add zi\add* zzect ittxeṣṣa ad issewjed ijj n uhinu i kuř ifa.’”   
\m
\v 8 “Xmi ɣa yadef řḥakem, ad yadef zeg ukulwar n wesqif \add n řebni\add* n tewwart uca ad iffeɣ zeg ukulwar nnes \add ɛawed\add*.  
\v 9 Xmi dd ɣa yas řgens n temmurt zzat i wudem n SIDI deg wussan ittwaggen n řeɛyudat, ittxeṣṣa wi ɣa yadfen zeg ukulwar \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ccamal maḥend ad \add as\add* ibendeq, ad iffeɣ s ukulwar \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ljanub, u wi ɣa yadfen s ukulwar \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ljanub, ad iffeɣ s ukulwar \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ccamal. War iddikkwiř zi řebni n tewwart mani dd-yudef, maca ad dd-iffeɣ zi tenni yeǧan arendad nnes.  
\v 10 Řḥakem ad yadef di řwest nsen. Xmi ɣa yadfen u xmi dd ɣa ffɣen, ad dd-ffɣen \add jmiɛ\add*.”   
\m
\v 11 “Di řeɛyudat u deg wussan ittwaggen n řɛid ad tiři tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d ijj n ifa i kuř afunas ameẓyan u ijj n ifa i kuř icarri u i izmaren anect izemmar ufus nnes ad t yawi, uca \add xenni arni\add* ijj n uhinu n zzect i kuř ifa.”   
\m
\v 12 “Xmi ɣa issewjed řḥakem ict n tewhibt n řxaḍar, ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ tiwhibin n řehna am tewhibt n řxaḍar i SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad as arzmen tawwart nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq. Netta ad issewjed taɣarṣt nnes n wecmaḍ d tewhibin nnes n řehna, am mammec tent issewjed deg wass n ssebt, u xmi ɣa iffeɣ ad bellɛen tawwart awarni řami iffeɣ netta.”   
\m
\v 13 “Kuř ṣṣbeḥ ad tesswejded ijj n izmar n ijj n useggʷas icnan qaɛ am tewhibt n wecmaḍ i SIDI.  
\v 14 Ittxeṣṣa ad kides tesswejded di kuř ṣṣbeḥ ict n tsittut n ijj n ifa d ict n ttuřut n ijj n uhinu n zzect maḥend ad zzayes tessuffed aren azdad am tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i SIDI. \add Aqa\add* d tiweṣṣa ittduman, i řebda.  
\v 15 Nitni ad sswejden izmar d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d zzect di kuř tiwecca am tɣarṣt n tmessi n řebda.”   
\m
\v 16 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xmi ɣa iwc řḥakem ict n tarzeft i yijj zeg iḥenjiren nnes, \add xenni\add* man aya ad tiři d řwart nnes. Ad tiři i iḥenjiren nnes, aqa-t d agřa nnes di řwart.  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* mařa iwca zi řwart nnes ict n tarzeft i yijjen zeg imsexxaren nnes, \add xenni\add* ad tiři nnes ař aseggʷas n třelli. \add Xenni\add* ad dd-tedweř \add tesɣart\add* ɣar řḥakem, minzi aqa-tt d řwart nnes, ad tiři i iḥenjiren nnes. \f ◼ \fr 46:17 \ft \+fk ad tiři nnes\ft  - ixs ad yini aqa tasɣart ad tiři i umsexxar nnes.\f*  
\v 18 War iɛeddeř i řḥakem ad ikkes ca zi tesɣart n řgens ařami ɣa ikecceḍ agřa nsen. Netta ad isswart tasɣart i iḥenjiren nnes zeg wagřa nnes, ḥima war ittwazuzzar řgens inu, \add umi\add* i ɣa ittwaqřeɛ kuř ijj zeg wagřa nnes.’”   
\m
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* indeh ayi am dd-ikka x tebridt nni ɣar uɣezdis \add n řebni\add* n tewwart ař ixxamen iqeddsen n ikehhanen nni tuɣa iwařan ccamal. U xzar, aqa din ijj n wemcan ɣar ḍeffar n tnayen n iɣezdisen \add nnes\add*, ɣar řɣarb.  
\v 20 Netta inna ayi: “Wa d amcan mani ɣa ssenwen ikehhanen taɣarṣt n \add tikkest n\add* umarwas d tɣarṣt n ddenb u mani ɣa ssenggwen tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, ḥima war tt ssuffɣen ca barra ɣar řemraḥ n barra, ařami i ɣa ssqeddsen řgens \add ammu\add*.”   
\m
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* issuffeɣ ayi barra ɣar řemraḥ n barra uca indeh ayi ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura n řemraḥ. U xzar, di kuř taɣmart n řemraḥ aqa din ijj n řemraḥ \add nneɣni\add*, ijj n \add wemcan ifarzen di\add* řemraḥ di \add kuř\add* taɣmart n řemraḥ.  
\v 22 Di arebɛa n tɣemmura n řemraḥ n zzat \add tuɣa din ixxamen am\add* řemraḥat iseqqfen s ict n tuzzeggart n arebɛin \add n iɣaǧen\add* d ict n tiru n třatin \add n iɣaǧen\add*. \add Ixxamen deg\add* arebɛa n tɣemmura ɣarsen řeɛbar d ijj.  
\v 23 Deg wenneḍ n arebɛa \add n ixammen\add* nni tuɣa din ict n tseddiyt i d asen-dd innḍen. Aqa ggin řmejmarat sadu i tseddyin i d as dd-innḍen.  
\v 24 Netta inna ayi: “Tina d kuzinat mani ɣa ssenggʷen imsexxaren n Taddart taɣarṣt n řgens.” *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 47
\s1 Iɣzar i dd-iffɣen zi Zzawect Tameqqrant  
\m
\v 1 \add Awarni aya\add* yiwi ayi ɛawed ɣar wadaf n Taddart, u xzar, zi sadu tanebdat n Taddart tteffɣen waman ɣar ccarq, minzi aɣezdis n zzat n Taddart tuɣa-t ɣar ccarq u tuɣa ttazzřen hekkwan aman zi swadday n uɣezdis azeřmaḍ n Taddart, ɣar \add uɣezdis n\add* ljanub n uɛalṭar.  
\v 2 Issuffeɣ ayi-dd zeg ukulwar \add n řebni\add* n tewwart n ccamal uca indeh ayi ɣar tebridt nni ɣar barra, jjihet n tewwart n barra, \add ɣar\add* ukulwar nni ixezzaren ɣar ccarq, u xzar, aman ttazzřen zi teɣmart n zzat afusi.   
\m
\v 3 \add Umi\add* dd-iffeɣ weryaz ɣar ccarq, tuɣa ɣares afiřu n řeɛbar deg ufus nnes uca iɛbar ařef n iɣaǧen. Isseẓwa ayi x waman uca aman \add iwḍen\add* ař ticeɛbin.  
\v 4 Iɛbar \add ɛawed\add* ařef \add n iɣaǧen\add* uca isseẓwa ayi x waman uca aman iwḍen ař ifadden. \add Ɛawed\add* iɛbar ařef \add n iɣaǧen\add* uca isseẓwa ayi ɛad ktar uca aman iwḍen ař tijɛinnatin.  
\v 5 Iɛbar \add twařat nneɣni\add* ařef \add n iɣaǧen\add* uca \add aman\add* dewřen d ijj n iɣzar war zmireɣ ad t ẓwiɣ \add x iḍaren\add*, maɣar aman geɛɛden ařami tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad iɛumm bnadem, aqa-t d ijj n iɣzar i war izemmar ḥed ad t iẓwa \add x iḍaren\add*.   
\m
\v 6 Netta inna ayi: “Ma teẓrid tt, \add a\add* mmis n bnadem?” \add Xenni\add* indeh ayi am ggureɣ nnec uca yarra ayi ɣar tma n iɣzar.  
\v 7 \add Umi\add* dd-dewřeɣ necc, xzar, \add beddent din\add* aṭṭas n tcejjura x tma n iɣzar, am ɣar tma-ya am ɣar tma nni. \x ◘ \xo 47:7 \xt Asa. 22:2\x*  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Aman-a ttazzřen ɣar jjihet n ccarq uca hekkwan ɣar Řewḍa uca ttakkwaḍen ɣar Řebḥar \add Immuten\add*. \add Xenni\add* ttazzřen di řebḥar uca ad ttwassggenfan aman \add ɛawed\add*.  
\v 9 Ad imsar, belli kuř řeɛmar i din ittenhezzan ad iddar, mani ma i dd ɣa \add y\add*awḍen tnayen n iɣezran. Ad \add din\add* iřin iseřman aṭṭas, minzi aman-a ttazzřen dinni uca ad ttwassgenfan \add waman n řebḥar\add*. Mani ma i dd ɣa yas yeɣzar-a, ad din tiři tudart.  
\v 10 Ad imsar belli ad iřin iyemmaren n iseřman zi Ɛayn-Jadyi ař Ɛayn-Ɛiglayim. Ad din iřin imucan i ujeffaf n traccawin. Asřem nsen ad yiři ɛlaḥsab marka nnes, am wesřem n Řebḥar Ameqqran, aṭṭas s waṭṭas,  
\v 11 \add maca\add* tindat nnes d iyeřmamen nnes war ttwaggenfan, ad qqimen meǧḥen.  
\v 12 Ɣar yeɣzar, x tma nnes, x tma-ya u x tma nni, ad iřin ɛřam kuř ticejjura, maḥend ad zzaysent ccen, tinni umi tafart nsent war tᵉttisřaw u řɣiǧet nsent war t qeṭṭi ca. Kuř ayur ad wcent řɣiǧet d ṭṭri, maɣar aman n \add yeɣzar\add* ffɣen-dd zi Zzawect Iqeddsen. Řɣiǧet nsent ad tiři i macca d tafart nsent i ugenfu.” \x ◘ \xo 47:12 \xt Asa. 22:2\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iymiren d ubeṭṭu n temmurt  
\m
\v 13 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Wa \add ad yiři\add* d aymir i x i ɣa tewcim tammurt d řwart i tenɛac n tqebbař n Israil. Yusuf ad iksi tnayen n tseqqar.  
\v 14 Kenniw ad tt twartem, ijj am wenneɣni, i uya ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu \add uca jjuǧeɣ\add* ad tt wceɣ i řejdud nwem. Tammurt-a ad tiři d tasɣart nwem. \x ◘ \xo 47:14 \xt Amz. 12:7; 17:8; 26:3; 28:13\x*  
\v 15 Wa \add ad yiři\add* d aymir n temmurt: ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal, zi Řebḥar Ameqqran x webrid ɣar Ḥitlun ař dd-tusid ɣar Ṣadad,  
\v 16 \add xenni ɣar\add* Ḥamat, Bayruta, Sibrayim nni yeǧa jar weymir \add n temmurt n\add* Dimacq d weymir \add n temmurt n\add* Ḥamat, \add xenni ɣar\add* Ḥaṣr-Hatixun nni yeǧa ɣar weymir n Ḥawran.  
\v 17 Zi řebḥar ad dd-iffeɣ weymir ɣar Ḥasr-Ɛaynun, \add x uɣezdis n\add* weymir n Dimacq uca \add xenni\add* ɣar ccamal, ɣar ccamal u \add x uɣezdis n\add* weymir n Ḥamat. Wa ad yiři d aɣezdis n ccamal.   
\m
\v 18 Aɣezdis n ccarq \add ittekk\add* zi jar Ḥawran d Dimacq u zi jar Jilɛad d temmurt n Israil \add x\add* L’Urdun. Kenniw ad t tɛebbarem zeg weymir ař řebḥar n ccarq. Wa \add ad yiři\add* d aɣezdis n ccarq.   
\m
\v 19 Aɣezdis n ljanub, aqa-t ɣar ljanub zi Tamar ař aman n Maribut-Qadac \add uca ittekk x\add* Teɣzurt n Teɣzart \add n Miṣra\add* ař Řebḥar Ameqqran. Wa ad yiři d aɣezdis n ljanub ɣar ljanub.   
\m
\v 20 Aɣezdis n řɣarb d Řebḥar Ameqqran, zeg weymir \add nni iǧan ɣar ljanub\add* ař arendad n webrid ɣar Ḥamat, wa ad yiři d aɣezdis n lɣarb.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 21 “Ad tebḍam tammurt-a jar awem ɛlaḥsab tiqebbař n Israil.  
\v 22 Kenniw ad tt jjen d řwart i kenniw u i ibarraniyyen di řwesṭ nwem, inni urwen iḥenjiren di řwesṭ nwem. Nitni ad awem iřin am yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen di temmurt jar ayt n Israil. Ad asen tiři tasɣart akidwem di řwesṭ n tqebbař n Israil.  
\v 23 Ɣar teqbič i ɣar ɣa izdeɣ am ubarrani, din ad as tewcem tasɣart nnes! \add Ammu i\add* ɣa tiři, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 48
\m
\v 1 “Ina d ismawen n tqebbař.  
\b  
\m Zi ṭṭarf n ccamal qaɛ, x webrid n Ḥitlun ařami ɣa tawḍed ɣar Ḥamat, Ḥaṣar-Ɛinan, tammurt n weymir n Dimacq, x uɣezdis n ccamal n Ḥamat umi xas tᵉttekked: ad as yiři am uɣezdis n ccarq am uɣezdis n řebḥar, ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Dan.   
\m
\v 2 X weymir n Dan, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Acir.   
\m
\v 3 X weymir n Acir, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Naftali.   
\m
\v 4 X weymir n Naftali, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Manassa.   
\m
\v 5 X weymir n Manassa, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Ifrayim.   
\m
\v 6 X weymir n Ifrayim, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Rubin.   
\m
\v 7 X weymir n Rubin, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Yahuda.   
\b  
\m
\v 8 X weymir n Yahuda, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař tma n řebḥar, \add ad tiři\add* \bd tewhibt n usgeɛɛed\bd*, tenni i ɣa twehhbem, s ict n tiru n xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* u s ict n tuzzeggart am \add tuzzeggart n\add* icten zi tseqqar \add inneɣni\add* zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař tma n řebḥar. Zzawect Iqeddsen ad tiři di řwest nnes.   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Tawhibt n usgeɛɛed i SIDI nni i ɣa tessgeɛɛdem, \add ad tiři\add* s ict n tuzzeggart n xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* u s ict n tiru n ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 10 Tawhibt iqeddsen n usgeɛɛed ad tiři i ina:  
\b  
\m I ikehhanen: ɣar ccamal xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, u ɣar řɣarb tiru \add nnes\add* ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, u ɣar ccarq tiru \add nnes\add* ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, u ɣar ljanub tuzzeggart \add nnes\add* xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*. Zzawect Iqeddsen n SIDI ad tiři di řwest nnes.   
\m
\v 11 \add Ad tiři\add* temmurt-a iqeddsen i ikehhanen zeg ayt n Ṣaduq, inni iḥḍan aḥeṭṭu inu, inni war dd-iffɣen ca zeg webrid zi ssibbet n uweddar n ayt n Israil, am ffɣen uřa d ayt n Lawi.  
\v 12 Ad tiři d ict n tewhibt n usgeɛɛed i nitni zi tewhibt n temmurt, ad tiři tqeddes qaɛ, \add ad tiři\add* x weymir n Ilawiyyen.   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Ɣar weymir ak-d ikehhanen \add ad ɣarsen tiři\add* i Ilawiyyen \add ict n temmurt\add* s ict n tuzzeggart n xemsa u-ɛicrin ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, s ict n tiru n ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*. Marra tuzzeggart \add ad tiři\add* xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, u tiru nnes \add ad tiři ɛawed\add* ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*.  
\v 14 War iɛeddeř ad zzenzen uřa d ca zzayes, war iɛeddeř ad \add tt\add* beddřen niɣ ad \add tt\add* sseɛdun, \add aqa-tt\add* d řemxeyyer n temmurt, minzi aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ.   
\b  
\m
\v 15 Xemsa-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* nni i ɣa iqqimen ɣar tiru, ɣar zzat n xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, ad iřin i tudart n kuř ass di tendint, i tzeddiɣt u i ddmani n tarewsa. Ad tiři tendint di řwesṭ nnes.   
\m
\v 16 Ina ad iřin d řeɛburat nnes: ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal xemsa u-rebɛin-mya \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub xemsa u-rebɛin-mya \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq xemsa u-rebɛin-mya \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, ɣar uɣezdis n řebḥar xemsa u-rebɛin-mya \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*. \f ◼ \fr 48:16 \ft \+fk ɣar uɣezdis n řebḥar\ft  - niɣ ‘ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb’.\f*   
\m
\v 17 Ddmani n tarewsa n tendint: ɣar ccamal ad iřint mitayen u-xemsin \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, ɣar ljanub mitayen u-xemsin \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, ɣar ccarq mitayen u-xemsin \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*, ɣar řɣarb mitayen u-xemsin \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*.   
\m
\v 18 Min iqqimen zi tuzzeggart ɣar zzat n tewhibt iqeddsen n usgeɛɛed, ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* ɣar ccarq d ɛecra-ařaf \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb, ad yiři zzat \add n temmurt\add* n tewhibt iqeddsen n usgeɛɛed. Ṣṣabet nnes ad tiři d macca i imsexxaren n tendint.  
\v 19 Imsexxaren n tendint, aqa ad tt sexxaren zi marra tiqebbař n Israil.   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Marra tawhibt n usgeɛɛed \add ad tiři\add* xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef x xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add*. Ad ssgeɛɛden tawhibt n usgeɛɛed d ijj n ukwadrun ak-d tesɣart n tendint \add i dayes\add*.   
\b  
\m
\v 21 Min iqqimen ad yiři i řḥakem, ɣar ijj n uɣezdis u ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni n tewhibt iqeddsen n usgeɛɛed u n tesɣart n tendint. \add Min iǧan\add* ɣar uɣezdis n zzat n xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* n tewhibt n usgeɛɛed ař aymir n ccarq, u ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb ɣar zzat n xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n iɣunam n řeɛbar\add* ař aymir n řɣarb ɣar řebḥar, zzat i tseqqar nneɣni \add n temmurt\add*, \add d man aya ad yiři\add* i řḥakem.  
\b  
\m Ad tiři d ict n tewhibt iqeddsen \add n temmurt\add* nni i ɣa ssgeɛɛden, u Zzawect Iqeddsen n Taddart ad tiři di řwest nnes.  
\v 22 Zi \add min iǧan d\add* tasɣart n Ilawiyyen u \add zi min iǧan d\add* tasɣart n tendint nni \add iǧan\add* di řwesṭ n min ɣa yiři i řḥakem, ad yiři \add marra\add* min iǧan jar temmurt n Yahuda d temmurt n Binyamin, i řḥakem.   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Min iqqimen n tqebbař zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart\add* i Binyamin.   
\m
\v 24 X weymir n Binyamin, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Cimɛun.   
\m
\v 25 X weymir n Cimɛun, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Issakar.   
\m
\v 26 X weymir n Issakar, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Zabulun.   
\m
\v 27 X weymir n Zabulun, zeg uɣezdis n ccarq ař řebḥar:  
\m ict \add n tesɣart i\add* Jad.   
\m
\v 28 X weymir n Jad, ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub di jjihet n ljanub, ad yiři weymir zi Tamar ař aman n Mariba-Qadac, \add xenni ad yekk\add* x Teɣzart \add n Miṣra\add* ař Řebḥar Ameqqran.   
\b  
\m
\v 29 Ta d temmurt nni ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad tt tebḍam d tasɣart n řwart i tqebbař n Israil u tina d tiseqqar nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.” *   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tandint iqeddsen  
\m
\v 30 “D yina i ɣa yiřin d \bd uffuɣen n tendint\bd*:  
\b  
\m \bd Ɣar ccamal\bd* \add aqa din\add* xemsa u-rebɛin-mya n řeɛburat.  
\v 31 Tiwwura n tendint \add ad ttwařaɣant\add* ɛlaḥsab ismawen n tqebbař n Israil: třata n tewwura \add ad iřint\add* ɣar ccamal: icten n Rubin, icten n Yahuda, icten n Lawi.   
\m
\v 32 \bd Ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq\bd* \add aqa din\add* xemsa u-rebɛin-mya n řeɛburat, \add ak-d\add* třata n tewwura: icten n Yusuf, icten n Binyamin, icten n Dan.   
\m
\v 33 \bd Ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub\bd* \add aqa din\add* xemsa u-rebɛin-mya n řeɛburat, \add ak-d\add* třata n tewwura: icten n Cimɛun, icten n Issakar, icten n Zabulun.   
\m
\v 34 \bd Ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb\bd* \add aqa din\add* xemsa u-rebɛin-mya \add n řeɛburat\add*, \add ak-d\add* třata n tewwura nsen: icten n Jad, icten n Acir, icten n Naftali.   
\b  
\m
\v 35 \add Řeɛbar\add* deg wenneḍ \add n tendint\add* \add aqa-t\add* di tmenṭac-ařef \add n řeɛburat\add* u zeg wass \add nni\add* ad yiři yisem n tendint d wa:  
\b  
\m \bd ‘SIDI \+bdit AQA-T\+bdit* DIN!’\bd* ”   